__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
QDialog
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setupUi(this);

  QRegExp exp(glb::name);
  typEdit->setValidator(new QRegExpValidator(exp, typEdit));

  exp.setPattern(glb::exp_par);
  field1Edit->setValidator(new QRegExpValidator(exp, field1Edit));
  field2Edit->setValidator(new QRegExpValidator(exp, field2Edit));
  field3Edit->setValidator(new QRegExpValidator(exp, field3Edit));
  exp.setPattern("^[vi]{ 4 }");
  field4Edit->setValidator(new QRegExpValidator(exp, field4Edit));
  refresh();

  connect(typEdit, SIGNAL(activated(int)), this, SLOT(refresh()));
  connect(typEdit, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString&)), this, SLOT(refresh()));
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
setType
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QString &type)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  typEdit->clear();

  if ( type == "bSignalPar" )
  { 
    typEdit->insertItem("acs_bSignalInfoA429");
    typEdit->insertItem("acs_bSignalInfoAscb");
   }
  else if ( type == "iSignalPar" )
  { 
    typEdit->insertItem("acs_iSignalInfoA429");
    typEdit->insertItem("acs_iSignalInfoAscb");
   }
  else if ( type == "fSignalPar" )
  { 
    typEdit->insertItem("acs_fSignalInfoA429");
    typEdit->insertItem("acs_fSignalInfoAscb");
   }

  refresh();
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

{ 
  QString type = typEdit->currentText();

  if ( type == "acs_bSignalInfoA429" ||
       type == "acs_iSignalInfoA429" ||
       type == "acs_fSignalInfoA429" )
  { 
    field1Label->show();
    field1Label->setText("Value:");
    field1Edit->show();

    field2Label->show();
    field2Label->setText("SSM:");
    field2Edit->show();

    field3Label->show();
    field3Label->setText("Bus:");
    field3Edit->show();

    field4Label->show();
    field4Label->setText("SSM type:");
    field4Edit->show();
   }
  else if ( type == "acs_bSignalInfoAscb" ||
            type == "acs_iSignalInfoAscb" ||
            type == "acs_fSignalInfoAscb" )
  { 
    field1Label->show();
    field1Label->setText("Value:");
    field1Edit->show();

    field2Label->show();
    field2Label->setText("Validity:");
    field2Edit->show();

    field3Label->show();
    field3Label->setText("User:");
    field3Edit->show();

    field4Label->hide();
    field4Edit->hide();
    field4Edit->setCurrentText("");
   }
  else if ( type == "acs_bSignalInfoRsb" ||
            type == "acs_iSignalInfoRsb" ||
            type == "acs_fSignalInfoRsb" )
  { 
    field1Label->show();
    field1Label->setText("Value:");
    field1Edit->show();

    field2Label->show();
    field2Label->setText("Validity:");
    field2Edit->show();

    field3Label->show();
    field3Label->setText("Message:");
    field3Edit->show();

    field4Label->hide();
    field4Edit->hide();
    field4Edit->setCurrentText("");
   }
  else if ( type == "acs_bSignalInfoCustom" ||
            type == "acs_iSignalInfoCustom" ||
            type == "acs_fSignalInfoCustom" )
  { 
    field1Label->hide();
    field1Edit->hide();

    field2Label->hide();
    field2Edit->hide();

    field3Label->hide();
    field3Edit->hide();

    field4Label->hide();
    field4Edit->hide();
    field4Edit->setCurrentText("");
   }
  else 

  { 
    field1Label->show();
    field1Label->setText("Param 1:");
    field1Edit->show();

    field2Label->show();
    field2Label->setText("Param 2:");
    field2Edit->show();

    field3Label->show();
    field3Label->setText("Param 3:");
    field3Edit->show();

    field4Label->hide();
    field4Edit->hide();
    field4Edit->setCurrentText("");
   }

  adjustSize();
 }

(parent)

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setObjectName("theCParam");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_table_16.png").pixmap());

  mMainWindow = mw;




  setColumnCount(5);
  QStringList headers;
  headers << tr("Parameter") << tr("Type") << tr("Comment") << tr("Value") << tr("Status");
  setHeaderLabels(headers);
  header()->resizeSection(0, 200);
  header()->resizeSection(1, 100);
  header()->setResizeMode(2, QHeaderView::Stretch);
  hideColumn(3);
  hideColumn(4);

  setSortingEnabled(false);
  setRootIsDecorated(true);
  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);





  mProperties = new CProperties(this);

  QMap<QString, QVariant> extra;

  extra["helptext"] = QString("Specifies paramerer table type name");
  mProperties->setProperty("type_name", "MyParam", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Specifies compagnie namespace name");
  mProperties->setProperty("cie_namespace", "com_cae", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Specifies project namespace name");
  mProperties->setProperty("pro_namespace", "", extra);

  extra["helptext"] = QString("Enter the LRU name list using semicolon as separator");
  mProperties->setProperty("lru_list", "<ACSLRUTYPE>", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Enter parameter table document comment");
  mProperties->setProperty("comment", "", extra);





  mAddParamAct = new QAction(tr("&Add Parameter"), this);
  mAddParamAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage lement_add_24.png"));
  mAddParamAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddParamAct->setStatusTip(tr("Add paramete item"));
  connect(mAddParamAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddParam()));

  mAddGroupAct = new QAction(tr("&Add Section"), this);
  mAddGroupAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage older_add_24.png"));
  mAddGroupAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+S"));
  mAddGroupAct->setStatusTip(tr("Add paramete section"));
  connect(mAddGroupAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddGroup()));

  mAddRefAct = new QAction(tr("&Add Reference"), this);
  mAddRefAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage ink_add_24.png"));
  mAddRefAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+R"));
  mAddRefAct->setStatusTip(tr("Add custom reference section"));
  connect(mAddRefAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddRef()));

  mEditParamAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditParamAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditParamAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditParamAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edit parameter item"));
  connect(mEditParamAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditParam()));

  mEditGroupAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditGroupAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditGroupAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditGroupAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edit parameter section"));
  connect(mEditGroupAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditGroup()));

  mEditGroupAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit Reference"), this);
  mEditGroupAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditGroupAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditGroupAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edit custom reference section"));
  connect(mEditGroupAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditRef()));

  mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
  mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
  mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
  mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
  connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDelete()));





  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemDoubleClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotDoubleClick()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemExpanded(QTreeWidgetItem *)), this, SLOT(expandItem(QTreeWidgetItem *)));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemCollapsed(QTreeWidgetItem *)), this, SLOT(collapseItem(QTreeWidgetItem *)));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mMainWindow, SLOT(slotUpdateModIndicator()));





  CParamRoot *input = new CParamRoot(this, 0);
  input->setText(0, "Input");
  CParamRoot *local = new CParamRoot(this, input);
  local->setText(0, "Local");
  CParamRoot *output = new CParamRoot(this, local);
  output->setText(0, "Output");
  CParamRoot *custom = new CParamRoot(this, output);
  custom->setText(0, "Custom");
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:1 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:1 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:1 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/param/param.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:234 L_END:236 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:isModified NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:1 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
menu
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const Menu &item)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  switch ( item )
  { 
    case EditUndo :
      return mCmdStack.canUndo();
    case EditRedo :
      return mCmdStack.canRedo();
    case FileGenerate :
      return true;
    case EditCut :
      return true;
    case EditCopy :
      return true;
    case EditPaste :
      return true;
    case EditDelete :
      return true;
    case EditFind :
      return true;
    default:
      return false;
   }
 }

{ 
  CFindDialog dialog;
  dialog.caseCheck->hide();
  dialog.startCheck->hide();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString text = dialog.findEdit->text();

    Qt::MatchFlags flags = Qt::MatchRecursive;
    if ( dialog.exactCheck->isChecked() )
      flags |= Qt::MatchCaseSensitive;

    QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> found = findItems(text, flags, 0);
    if ( found.count() )
      scrollToItem(found[0]);
   }
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:4 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:8 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:6 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:11 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/param/param.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:3 IN:0 INDR:5 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:18 LOCALS:32 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:396 L_END:413 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:editFind NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:4 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:8 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



  CMarkup xml;
  if ( !xml.load(fn) )
  { 
   QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "XML document error.");
    return false;
   }



  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));




  clear();

  xml.findElem();
  xml.intoElem();

  xml.findElem("Input");
  CParamRoot *input = new CParamRoot(this, 0);
  input->load(xml);
 

 

  xml.findElem("Local");
  CParamRoot *local = new CParamRoot(this, input);
  local->load(xml);

  

  xml.findElem("Output");
  CParamRoot *output = new CParamRoot(this, local);
  output->load(xml);

  

  xml.findElem("Custom");
  CParamRoot *custom = new CParamRoot(this, output);
  custom->load(xml);







  xml.findElem("properties");
  while ( xml.findChildElem() )
  { 
    QString name = xml.getChildTagName().c_str();
    QString value = xml.getChildData().c_str();
    mProperties->setProperty(name, value);
   }
  xml.outOfElem();


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:6 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:31 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:16 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:33 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/param/param.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:6 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:69 LOCALS:65 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:427 L_END:495 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:readFile NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:4 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:29 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:1 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
writeFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( fn.isEmpty() )
  { 
    fn = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(".", filter(), 0);

    if ( fn.isEmpty() )
      return false;
    else if ( QFileInfo(fn).extension(false).isEmpty() )
      fn += ".par";
   }

  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  CMarkup xml;
  xml.setDoc("<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n");
  xml.addElem("ACS");
  xml.addAttrib("type", "param");
  xml.addAttrib("version", glb::version);

  xml.intoElem();

  



  for ( int i = 0; i < topLevelItemCount(); ++i )
    static_cast<CBaseParamItem *>(topLevelItem(i))->save(xml);





  xml.addElem("properties");
  QStringList list = mProperties->names();
  for ( int i = 0; i < list.count(); ++i )
  { 
    xml.addChildElem(list[i].toAscii().data());
    xml.setChildData(mProperties->value(list[i]).toString().toAscii().data());
   }

  xml.outOfElem();





  if ( !xml.save(fn) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(fn);
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "FMS Editor", message);

    QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
    return false;
   }


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

  CParamEditDialog dialog(this);
  dialog.setWindowTitle("Add Parameter");
  dialog.setTab(QStringList::split(";", mProperties->value("lru_list").toString()));
  dialog.nameEdit->setFocus();
  dialog.refresh();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
    QString type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
    QString comment = dialog.cmtEdit->text();
    QString value = dialog.valueEdit->text();
    QString status = QString::number(dialog.status());
    QStringList io = dialog.io();
    CSignalTable sig = dialog.signal();

    CParamItem *item = 0;
    QTreeWidgetItem *select = selectedItems().value(0);
    if ( select->type() == ParamItem )
      item = new CParamItem(select->parent(), select);
    else
      item = new CParamItem(select, 0);

    item->setText(0, name);
    item->setText(1, type);
    item->setText(2, comment);
    item->setText(3, value);
    item->setText(4, status);
    item->mIo = io;
    item->mSignal = sig;

    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdAdd("add parameter", item));
    emit modified();
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

slotAddRef
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CParamSecEditDialog dialog(this);
  dialog.setWindowTitle("Add Reference");
  dialog.adjustSize();

  QStringList ref;
  QTreeWidgetItem *custom = findItems("Custom", Qt::MatchExactly, 0).at(0);
  if ( custom )
    for ( int i = 0; i <  custom->childCount(); ++i )
      ref << custom->child(i)->text(0);

  ref.sort();
  dialog.refEdit->insertStringList(ref);

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
    QString ref = dialog.refEdit->currentText();

    CParamRef *item = 0;
    QTreeWidgetItem *select = selectedItems().value(0);
    if ( select->type() == ParamItem )
      item = new CParamRef(select->parent(), select);
    else
      item = new CParamRef(select, 0);
    item->setText(0, name);
    item->setText(1, ref);

    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdAdd("add reference", item));
    emit modified();
   }
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotEditParam
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CParamItem *item = (CParamItem *)currentItem();

  CParamEditDialog dialog(this);
  dialog.setWindowTitle("Edit Parameter");
  dialog.setTab(QStringList::split(";", mProperties->value("lru_list").toString()));
  dialog.nameEdit->setText(item->text(0));
  dialog.typeEdit->setCurrentText(item->text(1));
  dialog.cmtEdit->setText(item->text(2));
  dialog.valueEdit->setText(item->text(3));
  dialog.setStatus(item->text(4).toInt());
  dialog.setIO(item->mIo);
  dialog.setSignal(item->mSignal);
  dialog.refresh();
  dialog.refresh();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
    QString comment = dialog.cmtEdit->text();
    QString value = dialog.valueEdit->text();
    QString status = QString::number(dialog.status());
    QStringList io = dialog.io();
    CSignalTable sig = dialog.signal();

    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "edit parameter"));
    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdEdit("", item, 0, name));
    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdEdit("", item, 1, type));
    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdEdit("", item, 2, comment));
    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdEdit("", item, 3, value));
    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdEdit("", item, 4, status));
    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdEditIO("", item, io));
    mCmdStack.push(new CParamCmdEditSig("", item, sig));
    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "edit parameter"));
    emit modified();
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenuEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QContextMenuEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

  if ( !item )
    return;

  if ( item->type() == ParamRoot )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    if ( item->text(0) != "Custom" ) menu.addAction(mAddParamAct);
    menu.addAction(mAddGroupAct);
    if ( item->text(0) != "Custom" ) menu.addAction(mAddRefAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ParamGroup )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddParamAct);
    menu.addAction(mAddGroupAct);
    menu.addAction(mAddRefAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditGroupAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ParamRef )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddParamAct);
    menu.addAction(mAddRefAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditRefAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ParamItem )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddParamAct);
    menu.addAction(mAddRefAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditParamAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
contextMenuEvent::QTreeWidgetItem::item::currentItem::item::item::type::ParamRoot::QMenu::menu::item::text::Custom::menu::addAction::mAddParamAct::menu::addAction::mAddGroupAct::item::text::Custom::menu::addAction::mAddRefAct::menu::exec::event::globalPos::item::type::ParamGroup::QMenu::menu::menu::addAction::mAddParamAct::menu::addAction::mAddGroupAct::menu::addAction::mAddRefAct::menu::addAction::mEditGroupAct::menu::addAction::mDeleteAct::menu::exec::event::globalPos::item::type::ParamRef::QMenu::menu::menu::addAction::mAddParamAct::menu::addAction::mAddRefAct::menu::addAction::mEditRefAct::menu::addAction::mDeleteAct::menu::exec::event::globalPos::item::type::ParamItem::QMenu::menu::menu::addAction::mAddParamAct::menu::addAction::mAddRefAct::menu::addAction::mEditParamAct::menu::addAction::mDeleteAct::menu::exec::event::globalPos

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
maybeSave
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( isModified() )
  { 
    QString fn = QFileInfo(filename()).fileName();
    int ret = QMessageBox::warning( 0,
                                    "Editor",
                                    QString("File %1 has been modified.\n"
                                            "Do you want to save your changes?").arg(fn),
                                    QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::Default,
                                    QMessageBox::No,
                                    QMessageBox::Cancel | QMessageBox::Escape );
    if ( ret == QMessageBox::Yes )
      return writeFile(filename());
    else if ( ret == QMessageBox::Cancel )
      return false;
   }
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setText(0, xml.getTagName().c_str());

  xml.intoElem();
  CBaseParamItem *previous = 0;
  while ( xml.findElem() )
  { 
    CBaseParamItem *item = 0;

    if ( xml.getTagName() == "param" )
      item = new CParamItem(this, previous);
    else if ( !xml.getAttrib("ref").empty() )
      item = new CParamRef(this, previous);
    else
      item = new CParamGroup(this, previous);

    item->load(xml);
    previous = item;
   }
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/param/paramitem.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:8 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:272 L_END:274 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:CBaseParamItem NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:1 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setText(0, xml.getAttrib("name").c_str());
  setText(1, xml.getAttrib("type").c_str());

  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT);
  setText(2, xml.getData().c_str());

  xml.findElem();
  if ( text(1).contains("io") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();
    while ( xml.findElem() )
      mIo << xml.getAttrib("lbl").c_str();
    xml.outOfElem();
   }
  else if ( text(1).contains("Signal") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();
    for ( int i = 0; xml.findElem(); ++i )
    { 
      mSignal.push_back(CSignalList());

      xml.intoElem();
      for ( int j = 0; xml.findElem(); ++j )
      { 
        CSignalData data;


        xml.intoElem();
        xml.findNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT);
        data.mSrc = xml.getData().c_str();


        xml.findElem("object");
        xml.intoElem();
        xml.findElem("class");
        data.mTyp = xml.getElemContent().c_str();


        xml.findElem("content");
        xml.intoElem();
        xml.findElem("value");

        xml.findChildElem();
        data.mField1 = xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str();

        xml.findChildElem();
        data.mField2 = xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str();

        xml.findChildElem();
        data.mField3 = xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str();

        xml.findChildElem();
        data.mField4 = xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str();

        mSignal[i].push_back(data);

        xml.outOfElem();
        xml.outOfElem();
        xml.outOfElem();
       }
      xml.outOfElem();
     }
    xml.outOfElem();
   }
  else
  { 
    setText(3, xml.getAttrib("value").c_str());
    setText(4, xml.getAttrib("status").c_str());
   }

  xml.outOfElem();

__BEGIN_NAME__
save
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.addElem("param");
  xml.addAttrib("name", text(0).toAscii().data());
  xml.addAttrib("type", text(1).toAscii().data());

  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, text(2).toAscii().data());

  if ( text(1).contains("io") )
  { 
    xml.addElem("lru");
    xml.addAttrib("size", mIo.count());

    for ( int i = 0; i < mIo.count(); ++i ) 
    { 
      xml.intoElem();
      xml.addElem("cdb");
      xml.addAttrib("lbl", mIo[i].toAscii().data());
      xml.outOfElem();
     }
   }
  else if ( text(1).contains("Signal") )
  { 
    xml.addElem("lru");
    xml.addAttrib("size", mSignal.count());

    for ( int i = 0; i < mSignal.count(); ++i ) 
    { 
      xml.intoElem();
      xml.addElem("channel");
      xml.addAttrib("size", mSignal[i].count());

      for ( int j = 0; j < mSignal[i].count(); ++j )
      { 
        xml.intoElem();
        xml.addElem("data");


        xml.intoElem();
        xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, mSignal[i][j].mSrc.toAscii().data());

        xml.addElem("object");
        xml.intoElem();


        xml.addElem("class");
        xml.addAttrib("schema", 0);
        xml.setElemContent(mSignal[i][j].mTyp.toAscii().data());

        xml.addElem("content");
        xml.intoElem();


        xml.addElem("value");
        xml.addChildElem("string");
        xml.addChildAttrib("val", mSignal[i][j].mField1.toAscii().data());


        xml.addElem("value");
        xml.addChildElem("string");
        xml.addChildAttrib("val", mSignal[i][j].mField2.toAscii().data());


        xml.addElem("value");
        xml.addChildElem("string");
        xml.addChildAttrib("val", mSignal[i][j].mField3.toAscii().data());


        xml.addElem("value");
        xml.addChildElem("string");
        xml.addChildAttrib("val", mSignal[i][j].mField4.toAscii().data());

        xml.outOfElem();
        xml.outOfElem();
        xml.outOfElem();
       }

      xml.outOfElem();
     }
   }
  else
  { 
    xml.addElem("default");
    xml.addAttrib("value", text(3).toAscii().data());
    xml.addAttrib("status", text(4).toAscii().data());
   }

  xml.outOfElem();
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
setTab
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QStringList &list)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

  for ( int i = 0; i < ioTab->count(); ++i )
    ioTab->removeTab(i);


  for ( int i = 0; i < sigTab->count(); ++i )
    sigTab->removeTab(i);


  while ( mIO.size() < list.count() )
    mIO.push_back("");

  while ( mSig.size() < list.count() )
    mSig.push_back(CSignalList());

  for ( int i = 0; i < list.count(); i++ )
  { 
    QString name = list[i].stripWhiteSpace();
    ioTab->insertTab(i, name);
    sigTab->insertTab(i, name);
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
refresh
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QString type = typeEdit->currentText();

  if ( type == "bPar" )
  { 
    line->show();
    valueLabel->show();
    valueEdit->show();
    statusGroup->show();
    ioGroup->hide();
    sigGroup->hide();

    valueEdit->setValidator(new QIntValidator(0, 1, valueEdit));
   }
  else if ( type == "iPar" )
  { 
    line->show();
    valueLabel->show();
    valueEdit->show();
    statusGroup->show();
    ioGroup->hide();
    sigGroup->hide();

    valueEdit->setValidator(new QIntValidator(valueEdit));
   }
  else if ( type == "fPar" )
  { 
    line->show();
    valueLabel->show();
    valueEdit->show();
    statusGroup->show();
    ioGroup->hide();
    sigGroup->hide();

    valueEdit->setValidator(new QDoubleValidator(valueEdit));
   }
  else if ( type == "aPar" )
  { 
    line->show();
    valueLabel->show();
    valueEdit->show();
    statusGroup->show();
    ioGroup->hide();
    sigGroup->hide();

    valueEdit->setValidator(new QDoubleValidator(valueEdit));
   }
  else if ( type == "sPar" )
  { 
    line->show();
    valueLabel->show();
    valueEdit->show();
    statusGroup->show();
    ioGroup->hide();
    sigGroup->hide();

    valueEdit->setValidator(0);
   }
  else if ( (type == "iobPar") || (type == "iohPar") || (type == "ioiPar") ||
            (type == "iofPar") || (type == "iodPar") || (type == "iosPar") )
  { 
    line->hide();
    valueLabel->hide();
    valueEdit->hide();
    statusGroup->hide();
    ioGroup->show();
    sigGroup->hide();
   }
  else if ( (type == "bSignalPar") || (type == "iSignalPar") || (type == "fSignalPar") )
  { 
    line->hide();
    valueLabel->hide();
    valueEdit->hide();
    statusGroup->hide();
    ioGroup->hide();
    sigGroup->show();
   }

  adjustSize();
 }
__END_BODY__

on_sigList_itemDoubleClicked
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QListWidgetItem *item)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int index = sigTab->currentIndex();
  int ch = item->text().section('-', 0, 0).toInt() - 1;


  CSignalEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.setType(typeEdit->currentText());
  dialog.setSignal(mSig[index][ch]);
  dialog.refresh();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    CSignalData data = dialog.signal();


    mSig[index][ch] = data;


    item->setText(QString("%1 - %2").arg(ch + 1).arg(data.mSrc));
   }
 }

{ 
  int index = sigTab->currentIndex();


  CSignalEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.setType(typeEdit->currentText());
  dialog.srcEdit->setText("undef");

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    CSignalData data = dialog.signal();


    mSig[index].push_back(data);


    QListWidgetItem *item = new QListWidgetItem(sigList);
    item->setText(QString("%1 - %2").arg(sigList->count()).arg(data.mSrc));
    sigList->setCurrentItem(item);
   }
 }

()

{ 
  int row = sigList->currentRow();

  if ( row >= 0 )
  { 
    QListWidgetItem *item = sigList->takeItem(row);

generate

(const QTreeWidget *list)

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( list == 0 )
    return false;

  mList = list;

  getSection();

  if ( !generateTableFile() )
  { 
	  return false; }

  if ( !generateTableFileImp() )
  { 
  return false; }

  if ( !generateSectionFiles() )
    { 
  return false; }
  if ( !generateCustomFile() )
    { 
  return false; }
  return true;
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
getSection
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



  QStringList local;

  QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> found = mList->findItems("Local", Qt::MatchExactly, 0);
  if ( found.count() )
    for ( int i = 0; i <  found.at(0)->childCount(); ++i )
	{ 
		
      local << found.at(0)->child(i)->text(0);
	 }




  QStringList output;

  found = mList->findItems("Output", Qt::MatchExactly, 0);
  if ( found.count() )
    for ( int i = 0; i <  found.at(0)->childCount(); ++i )
      local << found.at(0)->child(i)->text(0);





  mSection = local + output;
  QString prev;
  for ( QStringList::iterator it = mSection.begin(); it != mSection.end(); it++ )
  { 
    if ( *it == prev )
      it = mSection.remove(it);
    prev = *it;
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
generateTableFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


  QFile file(source());

    
  if ( !file.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(file.name());

    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", message);
    return false;
   }

    stream << "

  stream << "\n";

    stream << "namespace " << cieNamespace() << " { \n";
  if ( !proNamespace().isEmpty() )
    stream << "namespace " << proNamespace() << " { \n";
  if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() || !proNamespace().isEmpty() )
    stream << "\n\n";





  stream << "
\n";
  stream << "struct " << cname() << "_Input\n";
  stream << "{ \n";
  stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_BeginPar begin;\n";

  QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> found = mList->findItems("Input", Qt::MatchExactly, 0);
  if ( found.count() )
    for ( int i = 0; i <  found.at(0)->childCount(); ++i )
      writeParam(stream, "  ", QString(cname() + "_Input"), found.at(0)->child(i), true);

  stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_EndPar end;\n";
  stream << " };\n";
  stream << "\n";
  stream << "\n";





  stream << "
\n";
  stream << "struct " << cname() << "_Local\n";
  stream << "{ \n";
  stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_BeginPar begin;\n";

  found = mList->findItems("Local", Qt::MatchExactly, 0);
  if ( found.count() )
    for ( int i = 0; i <  found.at(0)->childCount(); ++i )
      writeParam(stream, "  ", QString(cname() + "_Local"), found.at(0)->child(i), false);

  stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_EndPar end;\n";
  stream << " };\n";
  stream << "\n";
  stream << "\n";

  stream << "struct " << cname() << "_Output\n";
  stream << "{ \n";
  stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_BeginPar begin;\n";

  found = mList->findItems("Output", Qt::MatchExactly, 0);

      writeParam(stream, "  ", QString(cname() + "_Output"), found.at(0)->child(i), false);

  stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_EndPar end;\n";
  stream << " };\n";
  stream << "\n";
  stream << "\n";





  stream << "
\n";
  stream << "class " << cname() << " : public _CAE::_ACS::acs_ParTbl\n";
  stream << "{ \n";
  stream << "private:\n";
  stream << "  ACS_DECLARE_CLASS(" << cname() << ")\n";
  stream << "\n";

  stream << "\n";

  stream << " };\n";

  stream << "\n";
  stream << "
  stream << "
  stream << "
  stream << "\n";

  if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() )
    stream << " };

  if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() || !proNamespace().isEmpty() )
    stream << "\n\n";
  writeFooter();


  mStream = 0;
  return true;

generateSectionFiles
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  for ( int i = 0; i < mSection.size(); i++ )
  { 



    QFile file(source().insert(source().lastIndexOf("."), "_" + mSection[i].lower()));
    if ( !file.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text) )
    { 
      QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(file.name());
      QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", message);
      return false;
     }
    QTextStream stream(&file);
    mStream = &stream;





    writeHeader();
    stream << "
\n";
    stream << "\n";
    stream << "
    stream << "\n";
    stream << "\n";
    if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() )
      stream << "namespace " << cieNamespace() << " { \n";
    if ( !proNamespace().isEmpty() )
      stream << "namespace " << proNamespace() << " { \n";
    if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() || !proNamespace().isEmpty() )
      stream << "\n\n";





    QTreeWidgetItem *item = 0;
    QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> found = mList->findItems("Local", Qt::MatchExactly, 0);
    if ( found.count() )
      for ( int j = 0; j <  found.at(0)->childCount(); ++j )
        if ( found.at(0)->child(j)->text(0) == mSection[i] )
        { 
          item = found.at(0)->child(j);
          break;
         }

    if ( item )
    { 
      stream << "
\n";
      stream << "struct " << cname() << "_Local_" << mSection[i] << "\n";
      stream << "{ \n";
      stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_BeginPar begin;\n";

      for ( int j = 0; j <  item->childCount(); ++j )
        writeParam(stream, "  ", QString(cname() + "_Local"), item->child(j), true);


      stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_EndPar end;\n";
      stream << " };\n";
      stream << "\n";
      stream << "\n";
     }





    found = mList->findItems("Output", Qt::MatchExactly, 0);
    if ( found.count() )
      for ( int j = 0; j <  found.at(0)->childCount(); ++j )
        if ( found.at(0)->child(j)->text(0) == mSection[i] )
        { 
          item = found.at(0)->child(j);
          break;
         }

    if ( item )
    { 
      stream << "
\n";
      stream << "struct " << cname() << "_Output_" << mSection[i] << "\n";
      stream << "{ \n";
      stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_BeginPar begin;\n";

      for ( int j = 0; j <  item->childCount(); ++j )
        writeParam(stream, "  ", QString(cname() + "_Output"), item->child(j), true);

      stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_EndPar end;\n";
      stream << " };\n";
      stream << "\n";
      stream << "\n";
     }





    if ( !proNamespace().isEmpty() )
      stream << " };  
\n";
    if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() )
      stream << " };  
\n";
    if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() || !proNamespace().isEmpty() )
      stream << "\n\n";
    writeFooter();
   }

  mStream = 0;
  return true;
 }

    QMessageBox::warning(0, "FMS Editor", message);

      stream << "

      stream << "{ \n";

      for ( int j = 0; j <  item->childCount(); ++j )

      stream << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_EndPar end;\n";
      stream << " };\n";
      stream << "\n";
      stream << "\n";
   }

    stream << " };

  if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() )
    stream << " };

  if ( !cieNamespace().isEmpty() || !proNamespace().isEmpty() )

  writeFooter();


  mStream = 0;
  return true;

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
writeParam
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( QTextStream &stream,
                            QString indent,
                            QString basename,
                            const QTreeWidgetItem *item,
                            bool rec )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QString name = item->text(0);
  QString type = item->text(1);
  QString comment = item->text(2);


  if ( item->type() == ParamItem )
  { 
    if ( comment.isEmpty() )
      stream << indent << "_CAE::_ACS::acs_" << type << " " << name << ";\n";
    else
    { 
      stream << QString(indent + "_CAE::_ACS::acs_" + type + " " + name + ";").leftJustify(48, ' ');
      stream << "
     }
   }


  else if ( item->type() == ParamRef )
  { 

   }


  else
  { 
    if ( rec )
    { 
      basename += "_" + name;

      stream << "\n";
      stream << indent << "struct " << basename << "\n";
      stream << indent << "{ \n";
      stream << indent << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_BeginPar begin;\n";

      for ( int i = 0; i <  item->childCount(); ++i )
        writeParam(stream, indent + "  ", basename, item->child(i), true);

      stream << indent << "  _CAE::_ACS::acs_EndPar end;\n";
      stream << indent << " } " + name + ";\n";
      stream << "\n";
     }
    else
    { 
      basename += "_" + name;
      stream << indent << basename << " " << name << ";\n";
     }
   }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
main
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(int argc, char *argv[])
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

  QApplication app(argc, argv);

  CSplashScreen *splash = new CSplashScreen;
  splash->show();

  splash->setMessage("Loading application...");
  qApp->processEvents();
  Sleep(1000);
  CMainWindow *mainWin = new CMainWindow;

  if ( argc == 2 )
  { 
    splash->setMessage(QString("Opening %1 document...").arg(argv[1]));
    qApp->processEvents();
    mainWin->slotOpen(argv[1]);
   }



  mainWin->show();
  splash->finish(mainWin);
  delete splash;

  return app.exec();
 }
__END_BODY__

menu

__BEGIN_SIG__
(const Menu &item)

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  switch ( item )
  { 
    case EditUndo :
      return isUndoAvailable();
    case EditRedo :
      return isRedoAvailable();
    case EditCut :
      return true;
    case EditCopy :
      return true;
    case EditPaste :
      return true;
    case EditDelete :
      return true;
    case EditFind :
      return true;
    default:
      return false;
   }
 }

{ 
  CFindDialog dialog;
  dialog.startCheck->hide();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  {

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



  QFile file(fn);
  if ( !file.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to open <B>%1< > file.").arg(fn);
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", message);
    return false;
   }





  QTextStream stream(&file);
  setText(stream.read());
  file.close();



  setUndoRedoEnabled(false);
  setUndoRedoEnabled(true);

  setCaption(fn);
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:12 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:5 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:13 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/text/text.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:1 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:28 LOCALS:35 LONG:0 LT:2 L_BEGIN:282 L_END:309 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:readFile NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:2 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:11 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
writeFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( fn.isEmpty() )
  { 
    fn = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(".", filter(), 0);

    if ( fn.isEmpty() )
      return false;
    else if ( QFileInfo(fn).extension(false).isEmpty() )
      fn += ".txt";

    if ( QFile::exists(fn) )
    { 
      int ret = QMessageBox::warning( 0,
                                      "ACS Editor",
                                      QString("File %1 already exists.\n"
                                              "Do you want to overwrite it?").arg(QDir::convertSeparators(fn)),
                                      QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::Default,
                                      QMessageBox::No | QMessageBox::Escape );

      if ( ret == QMessageBox::No )
       return false;
     }
   }





  QFile file(fn);
  if ( !file.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(file.name());
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "FMS Editor", message);
    return false;
   }
  QTextStream stream(&file);
  stream << text();
  setModified(false);



  setUndoRedoEnabled(false);
  setUndoRedoEnabled(true);

  setCaption(fn);
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
writeFile::fn::isEmpty::fn::QFileDialog::getSaveFileName::filter::fn::isEmpty::false::QFileInfo::fn::extension::false::isEmpty::fn::txt::QFile::exists::fn::ret::QMessageBox::warning::ACS::Editor::QString::File::already::exists::n::Do::you::want::to::overwrite::it::arg::QDir::convertSeparators::fn::QMessageBox::Yes::QMessageBox::Default::QMessageBox::No::QMessageBox::Escape::ret::QMessageBox::No::false::QFile::file::fn::file::open::QIODevice::WriteOnly::QIODevice::Text::QString::message::QString::Unable::to::write::the::B::file::arg::file::name::QMessageBox::warning::FMS::Editor::message::false::QTextStream::stream::file::stream::text::setModified::false::setUndoRedoEnabled::false::setUndoRedoEnabled::true::setCaption::fn::true
__END_IDS__

__BEGIN_NAME__
maybeSave
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( isModified() )
  { 
    QString fn = QFileInfo(filename()).fileName();
    int ret = QMessageBox::warning( 0,
                                    "Editor",
                                    QString("File %1 has been modified.\n"
                                            "Do you want to save your changes?").arg(fn),
                                    QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::Default,
                                    QMessageBox::No,
                                    QMessageBox::Cancel | QMessageBox::Escape );
    if ( ret == QMessageBox::Yes )
      return writeFile(filename());
    else if ( ret == QMessageBox::Cancel )
      return false;
   }
  return true;
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:5 LOCALS:10 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:108 L_END:112 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:Load NONLCALS:1 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
ReadTextFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szFileName, string& strDoc, string* pstrError, int* pnFlags )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	FILE* fp = fopen( szFileName, "rb" );
	if ( ! fp )
	{ 
		if ( pstrError )
			*pstrError = strerror(errno);
		return false;
	 }


	int nFlags = pnFlags?*pnFlags:0;
	char szDescBOM[20] = { 0 };
	char szResult[100];
	strDoc.erase();


	fseek( fp, 0, SEEK_END );
	int nFileByteLen = ftell(fp);
	fseek( fp, 0, SEEK_SET );



	if ( nFileByteLen )
	{ 
		char* pszBuffer = new char[nFileByteLen];
		fread( pszBuffer, nFileByteLen, 1, fp );
		strDoc.assign( pszBuffer, nFileByteLen );
		delete [] pszBuffer;
	 }
	sprintf( szResult, "%s%d bytes", szDescBOM, nFileByteLen );
	if ( pstrError )
		*pstrError = szResult;

	fclose( fp );
	if ( pnFlags )
		*pnFlags = nFlags;
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
WriteTextFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szFileName, string& strDoc, string* pstrError, int* pnFlags )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	bool bSuccess = true;
	FILE* fp = fopen( szFileName, "wb" );
	if ( ! fp )
	{ 
		if ( pstrError )
			*pstrError = strerror(errno);
		return false;
	 }


	int nFlags = pnFlags?*pnFlags:0;
	char szDescBOM[20] = { 0 };
	char szResult[100];


	int nDocLength = (int)strDoc.size();


	if ( nDocLength )
		bSuccess = ( fwrite( strDoc.c_str(), nDocLength, 1, fp ) == 1 );
	sprintf( szResult, "%s%d bytes", szDescBOM, nDocLength );
	if ( pstrError )
		*pstrError = szResult;
	
	if ( ! bSuccess && pstrError )
		*pstrError = strerror(errno);
	fclose(fp);
	if ( pnFlags )
		*pnFlags = nFlags;
	return bSuccess;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:2 ASM:0 ASS:2 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:2 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:19 LOCALS:24 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:217 L_END:235 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:FindChildElem NONLCALS:1 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:6 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
EscapeText
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szText, int nFlags )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 













	static const char* szaReplace[] = {  "&lt;","&amp;","&gt;","&apos;","&quot;"  };
	const char* pFind = (nFlags&MNF_ESCAPEQUOTES)?"<&>\'\"":"<&>";
	string strText;
	const char* pSource = szText;
	int nDestSize = (int)strlen(pSource);
	nDestSize += nDestSize / 10 + 7;
	strText.reserve( nDestSize );
	char cSource = *pSource;
	const char* pFound;
	while ( cSource )
	{ 
		if ( (pFound=strchr(pFind,cSource)) != NULL )
		{ 
			bool bIgnoreAmpersand = false;
			if ( (nFlags&MNF_WITHREFS) && *pFound == '&' )
			{ 


				const char* pCheckEntity = pSource;
				++pCheckEntity;
				char c = *pCheckEntity;
				if ( (c>='A'&&c<='Z') || (c>='a'&&c<='z')
						|| c=='
				{ 
					while ( 1 )
					{ 
						++pCheckEntity;
						c = *pCheckEntity;
						if ( c == ';' )
						{ 
							int nEntityLen = (int)(pCheckEntity - pSource) + 1;
							strText.append( pSource, nEntityLen );
							pSource = pCheckEntity;
							bIgnoreAmpersand = true;
						 }
						else if ( (c>='A'&&c<='Z') || (c>='a'&&c<='z') || (c>='0'&&c<='9')
								|| c=='_' || c==':' || c=='-' || c=='.' || c>0x7f )
							continue;
						break;
					 }
				 }
			 }
			if ( ! bIgnoreAmpersand )
			{ 
				pFound = szaReplace[pFound-pFind];
				strText.append( pFound );
			 }
		 }
		else
		{ 
			strText += cSource;
		 }
		++pSource;
		cSource = *pSource;
	 }
	return strText;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
EscapeText::szaReplace::lt::amp::gt::apos::quot::pFind::nFlags::MNF_ESCAPEQUOTES::string::strText::pSource::szText::nDestSize::strlen::pSource::nDestSize::nDestSize::strText::reserve::nDestSize::cSource::pSource::pFound::cSource::pFound::strchr::pFind::cSource::NULL::bIgnoreAmpersand::false::nFlags::MNF_WITHREFS::pFound::pCheckEntity::pSource::pCheckEntity::c::pCheckEntity::c::A::c::Z::c::a::c::z::c::pCheckEntity::c::pCheckEntity::c::nEntityLen::pCheckEntity::pSource::strText::append::pSource::nEntityLen::pSource::pCheckEntity::bIgnoreAmpersand::true::c::A::c::Z::c::a::c::z::c::c::c::_::c::c::c::c::bIgnoreAmpersand::pFound::szaReplace::pFound::pFind::strText::append::pFound::strText::cSource::pSource::cSource::pSource::strText
__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
#METRICS ARRAYOP:2 ASM:0 ASS:28 AUTO:0 BREAK:1 CALLS:5 CASE:0 CHAR:7 CLASS:0 CONST:5 CONTINUE:1 CYCLO:9 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:4 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:2 ENUM:0 EQTEST:7 EXPRORCALL:24 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:5 GOTO:0 GT:7 IF:6 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:4 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:5 LOC:71 LOCALS:145 LONG:0 LT:7 L_BEGIN:238 L_END:308 MAXNEST:6 MMINUS:0 NAME:EscapeText NONLCALS:1 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:3 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:1 STMNT:33 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:1 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:2 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
UnescapeText
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szText, int nTextLength
 )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 





	static const char* szaCode[] = {  "lt;","amp;","gt;","apos;","quot;"  };
	static int anCodeLen[] = {  3,4,3,5,5  };
	static const char* szSymbol = "<&>\'\"";
	string strText;
	const char* pSource = szText;
	if ( nTextLength == -1 )
		nTextLength = (int)strlen(szText);
	strText.reserve( nTextLength );
	int nChar = 0;
	while ( nChar < nTextLength )
	{ 
		if ( pSource[nChar] == '&' )
		{ 
			bool bCodeConverted = false;


			if ( pSource[nChar+1] == '
			{ 

				int nBase = 10;
				int nNumericChar = nChar + 2;
				char cChar = pSource[nNumericChar];
				if ( cChar == 'x' )
				{ 
					++nNumericChar;
					cChar = pSource[nNumericChar];
					nBase = 16;
				 }


				int nCodeLen = 0;
				while ( nCodeLen < 7 && cChar && cChar != ';' )
				{ 

					++nCodeLen;
					cChar = pSource[nNumericChar + nCodeLen];
				 }


				if ( cChar == ';' )
				{ 
					int nUnicode = strtol( &pSource[nNumericChar], NULL, nBase );
					

					if ( nUnicode < 0x80 )
						strText += (char)nUnicode;
					else if ( nUnicode < 0x800 )
					{ 

						strText += (char)(((nUnicode&0x7c0)>>6) | 0xc0);
						strText += (char)((nUnicode&0x3f) | 0x80);
					 }
					else
					{ 

						strText += (char)(((nUnicode&0xf000)>>12) | 0xe0);
						strText += (char)(((nUnicode&0xfc0)>>6) | 0x80);
						strText += (char)((nUnicode&0x3f) | 0x80);
					 }
					if ( nUnicode )
					{ 

						nChar = nNumericChar + nCodeLen + 1;
						bCodeConverted = true;
					 }
				 }
			 }
			else
			{ 

				for ( int nMatch = 0; nMatch < 5; ++nMatch )
				{ 
					if ( nChar < nTextLength - anCodeLen[nMatch]
						&& strncmp(szaCode[nMatch],&pSource[nChar+1],anCodeLen[nMatch]) == 0 )
					{ 

						strText += szSymbol[nMatch];
						nChar += anCodeLen[nMatch] + 1;
						bCodeConverted = true;
						break;
					 }
				 }
			 }


			if ( ! bCodeConverted )
			{ 
				strText += '&';
				++nChar;
			 }
		 }
		else
		{ 
			strText += pSource[nChar];
			++nChar;
		 }
	 }
	return strText;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
FindNode
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int nType )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 






	int nTypeFound = 0;
	int nNodeOffset = m_nNodeOffset;
	if ( m_nNodeType > 1 )
	{ 

		nNodeOffset += m_nNodeLength;
	 }
	else
	{ 

		nNodeOffset = 0;
		if ( m_iPos )
		{ 

			nNodeOffset = m_aPos[m_iPos].StartAfter();
		 }
		else if ( m_iPosParent )
		{ 

			if ( m_aPos[m_iPosParent].IsEmptyElement() )
				return 0;
			else
				nNodeOffset = m_aPos[m_iPosParent].StartContent();
		 }
	 }


	int iPosNew = m_iPos;
	TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
	NodePos node;
	token.nNext = nNodeOffset;
	do
	{ 
		nNodeOffset = token.nNext;
		nTypeFound = x_ParseNode( token, node );
		if ( nTypeFound == 0 )
		{ 


			if ( m_iPosParent && nNodeOffset == m_aPos[m_iPosParent].StartContent()
					+ m_aPos[m_iPosParent].ContentLen() )
				return 0;
			nTypeFound = MNT_LONE_END_TAG;
		 }
		else if ( nTypeFound < 0 )
		{ 
			if ( nTypeFound == -2 )
				return 0;

			nTypeFound = MNT_NODE_ERROR;
		 }
		else if ( nTypeFound == MNT_ELEMENT )
		{ 
			if ( iPosNew )
				iPosNew = m_aPos[iPosNew].iElemNext;
			else
				iPosNew = m_aPos[m_iPosParent].iElemChild;
			if ( ! iPosNew )
				return 0;
			if ( ! nType || (nType & nTypeFound) )
			{ 

				x_SetPos( m_iPosParent, iPosNew, 0 );
				return m_nNodeType;
			 }
			token.nNext = m_aPos[iPosNew].StartAfter();
		 }
	 }
	while ( nType && ! (nType & nTypeFound) );

	m_iPos = iPosNew;
	m_iPosChild = 0;
	m_nNodeOffset = nNodeOffset;
	m_nNodeLength = token.nNext - nNodeOffset;
	m_nNodeType = nTypeFound;
	MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE;
	return m_nNodeType;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
GetTagName
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	string strTagName;



	if ( m_nNodeLength )
	{ 
		switch ( m_nNodeType )
		{ 
		case MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION:
		case MNT_LONE_END_TAG:
			{ 

				TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
				token.nNext = m_nNodeOffset + 2;
				if ( x_FindName(token) )
					strTagName = x_GetToken( token );
			 }
			break;
		case MNT_COMMENT:
			strTagName = "
			break;
		case MNT_CDATA_SECTION:
			strTagName = "
			break;
		case MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE:
			{ 

				TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
				token.nNext = m_nNodeOffset + 2;
				if ( x_FindName(token) && x_FindName(token) )
					strTagName = x_GetToken( token );
			 }
			break;
		case MNT_TEXT:
		case MNT_WHITESPACE:
			strTagName = "
			break;
		 }
		return strTagName;
	 }

	if ( m_iPos )
		strTagName = x_GetTagName( m_iPos );
	return strTagName;
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
GetAttribName
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int n )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
	if ( m_iPos && m_nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
		token.nNext = m_aPos[m_iPos].nStart + 1;
	else if ( m_nNodeLength && m_nNodeType == MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION )
		token.nNext = m_nNodeOffset + 2;
	else
		return "";
	if ( x_FindAttrib(token,NULL,n) )
		return x_GetToken( token );
	return "";
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:2 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:3 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:2 ENUM:0 EQTEST:2 EXPRORCALL:6 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:3 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:13 LOCALS:23 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:601 L_END:613 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:GetAttribName NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:3 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:6 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
SavePos
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szPosName )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	if ( szPosName )
	{ 
		SavedPos savedpos;
		if ( szPosName )
			savedpos.strName = szPosName;
		if ( m_iPosChild )
		{ 
			savedpos.iPos = m_iPosChild;
			savedpos.nSavedPosFlags |= SavedPosMap::SPM_CHILD;
		 }
		else if ( m_iPos )
		{ 
			savedpos.iPos = m_iPos;
			savedpos.nSavedPosFlags |= SavedPosMap::SPM_MAIN;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			savedpos.iPos = m_iPosParent;
		 }
		savedpos.nSavedPosFlags |= SavedPosMap::SPM_USED;

		if ( ! m_mapSavedPos.pTable )
			m_mapSavedPos.AllocMapTable();
		int nSlot = m_mapSavedPos.Hash( szPosName );
		SavedPos* pSavedPos = m_mapSavedPos.pTable[nSlot];
		int nOffset = 0;
		if ( ! pSavedPos )
		{ 
			pSavedPos = new SavedPos[2];
			pSavedPos[1].nSavedPosFlags = SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST;
			m_mapSavedPos.pTable[nSlot] = pSavedPos;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			while ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_USED )
			{ 
				if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].strName == szPosName )
					break;
				if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST )
				{ 
					int nNewSize = (nOffset + 6) * 2;
					SavedPos* pNewSavedPos = new SavedPos[nNewSize];
					for ( int nCopy=0; nCopy<=nOffset; ++nCopy )
						pNewSavedPos[nCopy] = pSavedPos[nCopy];
					pNewSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags ^= SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST;
					pNewSavedPos[nNewSize-1].nSavedPosFlags = SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST;
					delete [] pSavedPos;
					pSavedPos = pNewSavedPos;
					m_mapSavedPos.pTable[nSlot] = pSavedPos;
					++nOffset;
					break;
				 }
				++nOffset;
			 }
		 }
		if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST )
			savedpos.nSavedPosFlags |= SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST;
		pSavedPos[nOffset] = savedpos;

		


		return true;
	 }
	return false;
 }
__END_BODY__

SavePos::szPosName::SavedPos::savedpos::szPosName::savedpos::strName::szPosName::m_iPosChild::savedpos::iPos::m_iPosChild::savedpos::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_CHILD::m_iPos::savedpos::iPos::m_iPos::savedpos::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_MAIN::savedpos::iPos::m_iPosParent::savedpos::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_USED::m_mapSavedPos::pTable::m_mapSavedPos::AllocMapTable::nSlot::m_mapSavedPos::Hash::szPosName::SavedPos::pSavedPos::m_mapSavedPos::pTable::nSlot::nOffset::pSavedPos::pSavedPos::new::SavedPos::pSavedPos::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::m_mapSavedPos::pTable::nSlot::pSavedPos::pSavedPos::nOffset::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_USED::pSavedPos::nOffset::strName::szPosName::pSavedPos::nOffset::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::nNewSize::nOffset::SavedPos::pNewSavedPos::new::SavedPos::nNewSize::nCopy::nCopy::nOffset::nCopy::pNewSavedPos::nCopy::pSavedPos::nCopy::pNewSavedPos::nOffset::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::pNewSavedPos::nNewSize::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::delete::pSavedPos::pSavedPos::pNewSavedPos::m_mapSavedPos::pTable::nSlot::pSavedPos::nOffset::nOffset::pSavedPos::nOffset::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::savedpos::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::pSavedPos::nOffset::savedpos::true::false

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
RestorePos
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szPosName )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	if ( szPosName && m_mapSavedPos.pTable )
	{ 
		int nSlot = m_mapSavedPos.Hash( szPosName );
		SavedPos* pSavedPos = m_mapSavedPos.pTable[nSlot];
		if ( pSavedPos )
		{ 
			int nOffset = 0;
			while ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_USED )
			{ 
				if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].strName == szPosName )
				{ 
					int i = pSavedPos[nOffset].iPos;
					if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_CHILD )
						x_SetPos( m_aPos[m_aPos[i].iElemParent].iElemParent, m_aPos[i].iElemParent, i );
					else if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_MAIN )
						x_SetPos( m_aPos[i].iElemParent, i, 0 );
					else
						x_SetPos( i, 0, 0 );
					return true;
				 }
				if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST )
					break;
				++nOffset;
			 }
		 }
	 }
	return false;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

()

{ 

	if ( m_iPos && m_nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
	{ 
		int iPos = x_RemoveElem( m_iPos );
		x_SetPos( m_iPosParent, iPos, 0 );
		return true;
	 }
	return false;
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:10 LOCALS:20 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:747 L_END:756 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:RemoveChildElem NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:4 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_AllocPosArray
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int nNewSize
 )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 





	if ( ! nNewSize )
		nNewSize = m_iPosFree + (m_iPosFree>>1);
	if ( m_aPos.GetSize() < nNewSize )
	{ 

		int nSeg = (m_aPos.GetSize()?m_aPos.GetSize()-1:0) >> m_aPos.PA_SEGBITS;
		int nNewSeg = (nNewSize-1) >> m_aPos.PA_SEGBITS;
		if ( nNewSeg > nSeg + 1 )
		{ 
			nNewSeg = nSeg + 1;
			nNewSize = (nNewSeg+1) << m_aPos.PA_SEGBITS;
		 }


		if ( m_aPos.nSegs <= nNewSeg )
		{ 
			int nNewSegments = 4 + nNewSeg * 2;
			char* pNewSegments = new char[nNewSegments*sizeof(char*)];
			if ( m_aPos.SegsUsed() )
				memcpy( pNewSegments, m_aPos.pSegs, m_aPos.SegsUsed()*sizeof(char*) );
			if ( m_aPos.pSegs )
				delete[] (char*)m_aPos.pSegs;
			m_aPos.pSegs = (ElemPos**)pNewSegments;
			m_aPos.nSegs = nNewSegments;
		 }


		int nSegSize = m_aPos.GetSize() - (nSeg << m_aPos.PA_SEGBITS);
		int nNewSegSize = nNewSize - (nNewSeg << m_aPos.PA_SEGBITS);


		int nFullSegSize = 1 << m_aPos.PA_SEGBITS;
		if ( nSeg < nNewSeg && nSegSize < nFullSegSize )
		{ 
			char* pNewFirstSeg = new char[ nFullSegSize * sizeof(ElemPos) ];
			if ( nSegSize )
			{ 

				memcpy( pNewFirstSeg, m_aPos.pSegs[nSeg], nSegSize * sizeof(ElemPos) );
				delete[] (char*)m_aPos.pSegs[nSeg];
			 }
			m_aPos.pSegs[nSeg] = (ElemPos*)pNewFirstSeg;
		 }


		char* pNewSeg = new char[ nNewSegSize * sizeof(ElemPos) ];
		if ( nNewSeg == nSeg && nSegSize )
		{ 

			memcpy( pNewSeg, m_aPos.pSegs[nSeg], nSegSize * sizeof(ElemPos) );
			delete[] (char*)m_aPos.pSegs[nSeg];
		 }
		m_aPos.pSegs[nNewSeg] = (ElemPos*)pNewSeg;
		m_aPos.nSize = nNewSize;
	 }
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_AllocPosArray::nNewSize::nNewSize::m_iPosFree::m_iPosFree::m_aPos::GetSize::nNewSize::nSeg::m_aPos::GetSize::m_aPos::GetSize::m_aPos::PA_SEGBITS::nNewSeg::nNewSize::m_aPos::PA_SEGBITS::nNewSeg::nSeg::nNewSeg::nSeg::nNewSize::nNewSeg::m_aPos::PA_SEGBITS::m_aPos::nSegs::nNewSeg::nNewSegments::nNewSeg::pNewSegments::new::nNewSegments::m_aPos::SegsUsed::memcpy::pNewSegments::m_aPos::pSegs::m_aPos::SegsUsed::m_aPos::pSegs::delete::m_aPos::pSegs::m_aPos::pSegs::ElemPos::pNewSegments::m_aPos::nSegs::nNewSegments::nSegSize::m_aPos::GetSize::nSeg::m_aPos::PA_SEGBITS::nNewSegSize::nNewSize::nNewSeg::m_aPos::PA_SEGBITS::nFullSegSize::m_aPos::PA_SEGBITS::nSeg::nNewSeg::nSegSize::nFullSegSize::pNewFirstSeg::new::nFullSegSize::ElemPos::nSegSize::memcpy::pNewFirstSeg::m_aPos::pSegs::nSeg::nSegSize::ElemPos::delete::m_aPos::pSegs::nSeg::m_aPos::pSegs::nSeg::ElemPos::pNewFirstSeg::pNewSeg::new::nNewSegSize::ElemPos::nNewSeg::nSeg::nSegSize::memcpy::pNewSeg::m_aPos::pSegs::nSeg::nSegSize::ElemPos::delete::m_aPos::pSegs::nSeg::m_aPos::pSegs::nNewSeg::ElemPos::pNewSeg::m_aPos::nSize::nNewSize::true

#METRICS ARRAYOP:12 ASM:0 ASS:18 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:9 CASE:0 CHAR:11 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:10 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:25 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:36 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:6 IF:9 IN:3 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:6 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:1 LOC:63 LOCALS:128 LONG:0 LT:12 L_BEGIN:764 L_END:826 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_AllocPosArray NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:4 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:6 STATIC:0 STMNT:24 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:1 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_ParseDoc
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	string strResult = m_strError;


	ResetPos();
	m_mapSavedPos.RemoveAll();




	m_iPosFree = 1;
	x_AllocPosArray( (int)m_strDoc.size() / 64 + 8 );
	m_iPosDeleted = 0;


	m_aPos[0].ClearVirtualParent();
	if ( m_strDoc.size() )
	{ 
		TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
		int iPos = x_ParseElem( 0, token );
		m_aPos[0].nLength = (int)m_strDoc.size();
		if ( iPos > 0 )
		{ 
			m_aPos[0].iElemChild = iPos;
			if ( m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext )
				m_strError = "Root element has sibling";
		 }
		else
			m_strError = "No root element";
	 }
	else
		m_strError = "Empty document";

	ResetPos();


	if ( ! strResult.empty() )
	{ 
		if ( m_strError.empty() )
			m_strError = strResult;
		else
			m_strError = strResult + ", " + m_strError;
	 }

	return IsWellFormed();
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_ParseDoc::string::strResult::m_strError::ResetPos::m_mapSavedPos::RemoveAll::m_iPosFree::x_AllocPosArray::m_strDoc::size::m_iPosDeleted::m_aPos::ClearVirtualParent::m_strDoc::size::TokenPos::token::m_strDoc::m_nFlags::iPos::x_ParseElem::token::m_aPos::nLength::m_strDoc::size::iPos::m_aPos::iElemChild::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemNext::m_strError::Root::element::has::sibling::m_strError::No::root::element::m_strError::Empty::document::ResetPos::strResult::empty::m_strError::empty::m_strError::strResult::m_strError::strResult::m_strError::IsWellFormed
__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
#METRICS ARRAYOP:4 ASM:0 ASS:11 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:13 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:6 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:10 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:3 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:20 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:5 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:3 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:47 LOCALS:56 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:829 L_END:875 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_ParseDoc NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:18 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_ParseElem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPosParent, TokenPos& token )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	int iElemRoot = 0;
	int iPos = iPosParent;
	int iVirtualParent = iPosParent;
	int nRootDepth = m_aPos[iPos].Level();
	token.nNext = 0;
	m_strError.erase();


	NodeStack aNodes;
	aNodes.Add();
	int nDepth = 0;
	int nMatchDepth;
	int iPosChild;
	int iPosMatch;
	int nTypeFound = 0;
	ElemPos* pElem;
	int iElemFirst, iElemLast;
	while ( 1 )
	{ 
		nTypeFound = x_ParseNode( token, aNodes.Top() );
		nMatchDepth = 0;
		if ( nTypeFound == MNT_ELEMENT )
		{ 
			iPos = x_GetFreePos();
			if ( ! iElemRoot )
				iElemRoot = iPos;
			pElem = &m_aPos[iPos];
			pElem->iElemParent = iPosParent;
			pElem->iElemNext = 0;
			if ( m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild )
			{ 
				iElemFirst = m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild;
				iElemLast = m_aPos[iElemFirst].iElemPrev;
				m_aPos[iElemLast].iElemNext = iPos;
				pElem->iElemPrev = iElemLast;
				m_aPos[iElemFirst].iElemPrev = iPos;
				pElem->nFlags = 0;
			 }
			else
			{ 
				m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild = iPos;
				pElem->iElemPrev = iPos;
				pElem->nFlags = MNF_FIRST;
			 }
			pElem->SetLevel( nRootDepth + nDepth );
			pElem->iElemChild = 0;
			pElem->nStart = aNodes.Top().nStart;
			pElem->SetStartTagLen( aNodes.Top().nLength );
			if ( aNodes.Top().nFlags & MNF_EMPTY )
			{ 
				iPos = iPosParent;
				pElem->SetEndTagLen( 0 );
				pElem->nLength = aNodes.Top().nLength;
			 }
			else
			{ 
				iPosParent = iPos;
				++nDepth;
				aNodes.Add();
			 }
		 }
		else if ( nTypeFound == 0 )
		{ 
			nMatchDepth = nDepth;
			iPosMatch = iPos;
			while ( nMatchDepth && ! token.Match(aNodes.At(nMatchDepth-1).strMeta) )
			{ 
				

				--nMatchDepth;
				iPosMatch = m_aPos[iPosMatch].iElemParent;
			 }
			if ( nMatchDepth == 0 )
			{ 

				m_aPos[iVirtualParent].nFlags |= MNF_ILLFORMED;
				m_aPos[iPos].nFlags |= MNF_ILLDATA;
				if ( m_strError.empty() )
				{ 
					char* szError = new char[token.Length()+100];
					sprintf( szError, "No start tag for end tag '%s' at offset %d",
						x_GetToken(token).c_str(), aNodes.Top().nStart );
					m_strError = szError;
					delete [] szError;
				 }
			 }
			else
			{ 
				pElem = &m_aPos[iPosMatch];
				pElem->nLength = aNodes.Top().nStart - pElem->nStart + aNodes.Top().nLength;
				pElem->SetEndTagLen( aNodes.Top().nLength );
			 }
		 }
		else if ( nTypeFound == -1 )
		{ 
			m_aPos[iVirtualParent].nFlags |= MNF_ILLFORMED;
			m_aPos[iPos].nFlags |= MNF_ILLDATA;
			if ( m_strError.empty() )
				m_strError = aNodes.Top().strMeta;
		 }


		if ( nMatchDepth || nTypeFound == -2 )
		{ 
			if ( nDepth > nMatchDepth )
				m_aPos[iVirtualParent].nFlags |= MNF_ILLFORMED;


			while ( nDepth > nMatchDepth )
			{ 

				pElem = &m_aPos[iPos];
				iPosChild = pElem->iElemChild;
				iPosParent = pElem->iElemParent;
				pElem->SetEndTagLen( 0 );
				pElem->nFlags |= MNF_NONENDED;
				pElem->iElemChild = 0;
				pElem->nLength = pElem->StartTagLen();
				if ( pElem->nFlags & MNF_ILLDATA )
				{ 
					pElem->nFlags ^= MNF_ILLDATA;
					m_aPos[iPosParent].nFlags |= MNF_ILLDATA;
				 }
				while ( iPosChild )
				{ 
					m_aPos[iPosChild].iElemParent = iPosParent;
					m_aPos[iPosChild].iElemPrev = iPos;
					m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext = iPosChild;
					iPos = iPosChild;
					iPosChild = m_aPos[iPosChild].iElemNext;
				 }
				iPos = iPosParent;
				aNodes.Remove();
				--nDepth;




				if ( m_strError.empty() )
				{ 
					if ( nTypeFound == 0 )
					{ 
						char* szError = new char[aNodes.Top().strMeta.size()+token.Length()+100];
						sprintf( szError, "End tag '%s' at offset %d does not match start tag '%s' at offset %d",
							x_GetToken(token).c_str(), token.nL-1, aNodes.Top().strMeta.c_str(), pElem->nStart );
						m_strError = szError;
						delete [] szError;
					 }
					else
					{ 
						char* szError = new char[aNodes.Top().strMeta.size()+100];
						sprintf( szError, "Element '%s' at offset %d not ended",
							aNodes.Top().strMeta.c_str(), aNodes.Top().nStart );
						m_strError = szError;
						delete [] szError;
					 }
				 }
			 }
			if ( nTypeFound == -2 )
				break;
			iPosParent = m_aPos[iPos].iElemParent;
			iPos = iPosParent;
			aNodes.Remove();
			--nDepth;
		 }
	 }
	return iElemRoot;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:28 ASM:0 ASS:61 AUTO:0 BREAK:1 CALLS:47 CASE:0 CHAR:6 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:21 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:69 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:6 ENUM:0 EQTEST:7 EXPRORCALL:66 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:1 IF:15 IN:0 INDR:26 INLINE:0 INT:10 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:172 LOCALS:322 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:878 L_END:1057 MAXNEST:4 MMINUS:3 NAME:x_ParseElem NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:89 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:4 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_FindAny
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szDoc, int& nChar )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	while ( szDoc[nChar] && strchr(" \t\n\r",szDoc[nChar]) )
		++nChar;
	return szDoc[nChar] != '\0';
 }

__END_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:3 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:1 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:2 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:8 LOCALS:13 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1060 L_END:1067 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_FindAny NONLCALS:3 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:1 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_FindName
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( CMarkupSTL::TokenPos& token )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	const char* szDoc = token.szDoc;
	int nChar = token.nNext;


	if ( ! x_FindAny(szDoc,nChar) )
	{ 

		token.nL = nChar;
		token.nR = nChar - 1;
		token.nNext = nChar;
		return false;
	 }


	token.nL = nChar;
	while ( szDoc[nChar] && ! strchr(" \t\n\r<>=\\/?!",szDoc[nChar]) )
		++nChar;


	if ( nChar == token.nL )
		++nChar;
	token.nR = nChar - 1;


	token.nNext = nChar;
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__END_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:2 ASM:0 ASS:9 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:1 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:9 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:1 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:31 LOCALS:43 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:1070 L_END:1100 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_FindName NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:2 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:12 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:1 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:1 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_GetToken
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const CMarkupSTL::TokenPos& token )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	if ( token.nL > token.nR )
		return "";
	string strToken( &token.szDoc[token.nL], token.Length() );
	return strToken;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_GetToken::token::nL::token::nR::string::strToken::token::szDoc::token::nL::token::Length::strToken
__END_IDS__
