#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:5 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:8 LOCALS:12 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1103 L_END:1110 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_GetToken NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:3 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_FindElem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPosParent, int iPos, const char* szPath )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	if ( iPos )
		iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext;
	else
		iPos = m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild;


	if ( szPath == NULL || !szPath[0] )
		return iPos;


	TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
	while ( iPos )
	{ 

		token.nNext = m_aPos[iPos].nStart + 1;
		x_FindName( token );
		if ( token.Match(szPath) )
			return iPos;
		iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext;
	 }
	return 0;

 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_FindElem::iPos::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemNext::iPos::m_aPos::iPosParent::iElemChild::szPath::NULL::szPath::iPos::TokenPos::token::m_strDoc::m_nFlags::iPos::token::nNext::m_aPos::iPos::nStart::x_FindName::token::token::Match::szPath::iPos::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemNext
__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
#METRICS ARRAYOP:5 ASM:0 ASS:4 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:5 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:6 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:1 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:7 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:3 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:27 LOCALS:29 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1113 L_END:1139 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_FindElem NONLCALS:3 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:3 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:9 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:1 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_ParseNode
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( CMarkupSTL::TokenPos& token, CMarkupSTL::NodePos& node )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 















	enum ParseBits
	{ 
		PD_OPENTAG = 1,
		PD_BANG = 2,
		PD_DASH = 4,
		PD_BRACKET = 8,
		PD_TEXTORWS = 16,
		PD_DOCTYPE = 32,
		PD_INQUOTE_S = 64,
		PD_INQUOTE_D = 128,
	 };
	int nParseFlags = 0;

	const char* szFindEnd = NULL;
	int nNodeType = -1;
	int nEndLen = 0;
	int nName = 0;
	unsigned int cDminus1 = 0, cDminus2 = 0;



	node.nStart = token.nNext;
	node.nFlags = 0;

	int nR = token.nNext;
	const char* pDoc = &token.szDoc[nR];
	register unsigned int cD = (unsigned int)*pDoc;
	if ( ! cD )
	{ 
		node.nLength = 0;
		node.nNodeType = 0;
		return -2;
	 }

	while ( 1 )
	{ 
		cD = (unsigned int)*pDoc;
		if ( ! cD )
		{ 
			nR = (int)(pDoc - token.szDoc) - 1;
			if ( nNodeType != MNT_WHITESPACE && nNodeType != MNT_TEXT )
			{ 
				const char* szType = "tag";
				if ( (nParseFlags & PD_DOCTYPE) || nNodeType == MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE )
					szType = "Doctype";
				else if ( nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
					szType = "Element tag";
				else if ( nNodeType == 0 )
					szType = "Element end tag";
				else if ( nNodeType == MNT_CDATA_SECTION )
					szType = "CDATA Section";
				else if ( nNodeType == MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION )
					szType = "Processing instruction";
				else if ( nNodeType == MNT_COMMENT )
					szType = "Comment";
				nNodeType = -1;
				char szError[100];
				sprintf( szError, "%s at offset %d unterminated", szType, node.nStart );
				node.strMeta = szError;
			 }
			break;
		 }

		if ( nName )
		{ 
			if ( strchr(" \t\n\r/>",(char)cD) )
			{ 
				int nNameLen = (int)(pDoc - token.szDoc) - nName;
				if ( nNodeType == 0 )
				{ 
					token.nL = nName;
					token.nR = nName + nNameLen - 1;
				 }
				else
				{ 
					node.strMeta.assign( &token.szDoc[nName], nNameLen );
				 }
				nName = 0;
				cDminus2 = 0;
				cDminus1 = 0;
			 }
			else
			{ 
				++pDoc;
				continue;
			 }
		 }

		if ( szFindEnd )
		{ 
			if ( cD == '>' && ! (nParseFlags & (PD_INQUOTE_S|PD_INQUOTE_D)) )
			{ 
				nR = (int)(pDoc - token.szDoc);
				if ( nEndLen == 1 )
				{ 
					szFindEnd = NULL;
					if ( nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT && cDminus1 == '/' )
					{ 
						if ( (! cDminus2) || strchr(" \t\n\r\'\"",(char)cDminus2) )
							node.nFlags |= MNF_EMPTY;
					 }
				 }
				else if ( nR > nEndLen )
				{ 

					const char* pEnd = pDoc - nEndLen + 1;
					const char* pFindEnd = szFindEnd;
					int nLen = nEndLen;
					while ( --nLen && *pEnd++ == *pFindEnd++ );
					if ( nLen == 0 )
						szFindEnd = NULL;
				 }
				if ( ! szFindEnd && ! (nParseFlags & PD_DOCTYPE) )
					break;
			 }
			else if ( cD == '<' && (nNodeType == MNT_TEXT || nNodeType == -1) )
			{ 
				nR = (int)(pDoc - token.szDoc) - 1;
				break;
			 }
			else if ( nNodeType & (MNT_ELEMENT|MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE) )
			{ 
				if ( cD == '\"' && ! (nParseFlags&PD_INQUOTE_S) )
					nParseFlags ^= PD_INQUOTE_D;
				else if ( cD == '\'' && ! (nParseFlags&PD_INQUOTE_D) )
					nParseFlags ^= PD_INQUOTE_S;
				if ( nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
				{ 
					cDminus2 = cDminus1;
					cDminus1 = cD;
				 }
			 }
		 }
		else if ( nParseFlags )
		{ 
			if ( nParseFlags & PD_TEXTORWS )
			{ 
				if ( cD == '<' )
				{ 
					nR = (int)(pDoc - token.szDoc) - 1;
					nNodeType = MNT_WHITESPACE;
					break;
				 }
				else if ( ! strchr(" \t\n\r",(char)cD) )
				{ 
					nParseFlags ^= PD_TEXTORWS;
					FINDNODETYPE( "<", MNT_TEXT, 0 )
				 }
			 }
			else if ( nParseFlags & PD_OPENTAG )
			{ 
				nParseFlags ^= PD_OPENTAG;
				if ( cD > 0x60 || ( cD > 0x40 && cD < 0x5b ) || cD == 0x5f || cD == 0x3a )
					FINDNODETYPE( ">", MNT_ELEMENT, 1 )
				else if ( cD == '/' )
					FINDNODETYPE( ">", 0, 2 )
				else if ( cD == '!' )
					nParseFlags |= PD_BANG;
				else if ( cD == '?' )
					FINDNODETYPE( "?>", MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION, 2 )
				else
					FINDNODEBAD( "tag name character" )
			 }
			else if ( nParseFlags & PD_BANG )
			{ 
				nParseFlags ^= PD_BANG;
				if ( cD == '-' )
					nParseFlags |= PD_DASH;
				else if ( cD == '[' && !(nParseFlags & PD_DOCTYPE) )
					nParseFlags |= PD_BRACKET;
				else if ( cD == 'D' && !(nParseFlags & PD_DOCTYPE) )
					nParseFlags |= PD_DOCTYPE;
				else if ( strchr("EAN",(char)cD) )
					FINDNODETYPE( ">", MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE, 0 )
				else
					FINDNODEBAD( "! tag" )
			 }
			else if ( nParseFlags & PD_DASH )
			{ 
				nParseFlags ^= PD_DASH;
				if ( cD == '-' )
					FINDNODETYPE( "-->", MNT_COMMENT, 0 )
				else
					FINDNODEBAD( "comment tag" )
			 }
			else if ( nParseFlags & PD_BRACKET )
			{ 
				nParseFlags ^= PD_BRACKET;
				if ( cD == 'C' )
					FINDNODETYPE( "]]>", MNT_CDATA_SECTION, 0 )
				else
					FINDNODEBAD( "tag" )
			 }
			else if ( nParseFlags & PD_DOCTYPE )
			{ 
				if ( cD == '<' )
					nParseFlags |= PD_OPENTAG;
				else if ( cD == '>' )
				{ 
					nR = (int)(pDoc - token.szDoc);
					nNodeType = MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE;
					break;
				 }
			 }
		 }
		else if ( cD == '<' )
		{ 
			nParseFlags |= PD_OPENTAG;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			nNodeType = MNT_WHITESPACE;
			if ( strchr(" \t\n\r",(char)cD) )
				nParseFlags |= PD_TEXTORWS;
			else
				FINDNODETYPE( "<", MNT_TEXT, 0 )
		 }
		++pDoc;
	 }
	token.nNext = nR + 1;
	node.nLength = token.nNext - node.nStart;
	node.nNodeType = nNodeType;
	return nNodeType;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_ParseNode::enum::ParseBits::PD_OPENTAG::PD_BANG::PD_DASH::PD_BRACKET::PD_TEXTORWS::PD_DOCTYPE::PD_INQUOTE_S::PD_INQUOTE_D::nParseFlags::szFindEnd::NULL::nNodeType::nEndLen::nName::cDminus1::cDminus2::node::nStart::token::nNext::node::nFlags::nR::token::nNext::pDoc::token::szDoc::nR::cD::pDoc::cD::node::nLength::node::nNodeType::cD::pDoc::cD::nR::pDoc::token::szDoc::nNodeType::MNT_WHITESPACE::nNodeType::MNT_TEXT::szType::tag::nParseFlags::PD_DOCTYPE::nNodeType::MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE::szType::Doctype::nNodeType::MNT_ELEMENT::szType::Element::tag::nNodeType::szType::Element::end::tag::nNodeType::MNT_CDATA_SECTION::szType::CDATA::Section::nNodeType::MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION::szType::Processing::instruction::nNodeType::MNT_COMMENT::szType::Comment::nNodeType::szError::sprintf::szError::s::at::offset::d::unterminated::szType::node::nStart::node::strMeta::szError::nName::strchr::t::n::r::cD::nNameLen::pDoc::token::szDoc::nName::nNodeType::token::nL::nName::token::nR::nName::nNameLen::node::strMeta::assign::token::szDoc::nName::nNameLen::nName::cDminus2::cDminus1::pDoc::szFindEnd::cD::nParseFlags::PD_INQUOTE_S::PD_INQUOTE_D::nR::pDoc::token::szDoc::nEndLen::szFindEnd::NULL::nNodeType::MNT_ELEMENT::cDminus1::cDminus2::strchr::t::n::r::cDminus2::node::nFlags::MNF_EMPTY::nR::nEndLen::pEnd::pDoc::nEndLen::pFindEnd::szFindEnd::nLen::nEndLen::nLen::pEnd::pFindEnd::nLen::szFindEnd::NULL::szFindEnd::nParseFlags::PD_DOCTYPE::cD::nNodeType::MNT_TEXT::nNodeType::nR::pDoc::token::szDoc::nNodeType::MNT_ELEMENT::MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE::cD::nParseFlags::PD_INQUOTE_S::nParseFlags::PD_INQUOTE_D::cD::nParseFlags::PD_INQUOTE_D::nParseFlags::PD_INQUOTE_S::nNodeType::MNT_ELEMENT::cDminus2::cDminus1::cDminus1::cD::nParseFlags::nParseFlags::PD_TEXTORWS::cD::nR::pDoc::token::szDoc::nNodeType::MNT_WHITESPACE::strchr::t::n::r::cD::nParseFlags::PD_TEXTORWS::FINDNODETYPE::MNT_TEXT::nParseFlags::PD_OPENTAG::nParseFlags::PD_OPENTAG::cD::cD::cD::cD::cD::FINDNODETYPE::MNT_ELEMENT::cD::FINDNODETYPE::cD::nParseFlags::PD_BANG::cD::FINDNODETYPE::MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION::FINDNODEBAD::tag::name::character::nParseFlags::PD_BANG::nParseFlags::PD_BANG::cD::nParseFlags::PD_DASH::cD::nParseFlags::PD_DOCTYPE::nParseFlags::PD_BRACKET::cD::D::nParseFlags::PD_DOCTYPE::nParseFlags::PD_DOCTYPE::strchr::EAN::cD::FINDNODETYPE::MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE::FINDNODEBAD::tag::nParseFlags::PD_DASH::nParseFlags::PD_DASH::cD::FINDNODETYPE::MNT_COMMENT::FINDNODEBAD::comment::tag::nParseFlags::PD_BRACKET::nParseFlags::PD_BRACKET::cD::C::FINDNODETYPE::MNT_CDATA_SECTION::FINDNODEBAD::tag::nParseFlags::PD_DOCTYPE::cD::nParseFlags::PD_OPENTAG::cD::nR::pDoc::token::szDoc::nNodeType::MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE::cD::nParseFlags::PD_OPENTAG::nNodeType::MNT_WHITESPACE::strchr::t::n::r::cD::nParseFlags::PD_TEXTORWS::FINDNODETYPE::MNT_TEXT::pDoc::token::nNext::nR::node::nLength::token::nNext::node::nStart::node::nNodeType::nNodeType::nNodeType

#METRICS ARRAYOP:4 ASM:0 ASS:73 AUTO:0 BREAK:5 CALLS:19 CASE:0 CHAR:11 CLASS:0 CONST:5 CONTINUE:1 CYCLO:51 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:26 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:32 ENUM:1 EQTEST:33 EXPRORCALL:100 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:10 IF:48 IN:0 INDR:2 INLINE:0 INT:17 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:240 LOCALS:463 LONG:0 LT:7 L_BEGIN:1142 L_END:1381 MAXNEST:4 MMINUS:2 NAME:x_ParseNode NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:4 REGISTER:1 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:77 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:2 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:4 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:2 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_GetPath
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	string strPath;
	while ( iPos )
	{ 
		string strTagName = x_GetTagName( iPos );
		int iPosParent = m_aPos[iPos].iElemParent;
		int iPosSib = 0;
		int nCount = 0;
		while ( iPosSib != iPos )
		{ 
			iPosSib = x_FindElem( iPosParent, iPosSib, strTagName.c_str() );
			++nCount;
		 }
		if ( nCount > 1 )
		{ 
			char szPred[25];
			sprintf( szPred, "[%d]", nCount );
			strPath = "/" + strTagName + szPred + strPath;
		 }
		else
			strPath = "/" + strTagName + strPath;
		iPos = iPosParent;
	 }
	return strPath;
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:3 ASM:0 ASS:9 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:4 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:1 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:7 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:3 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:25 LOCALS:55 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1384 L_END:1408 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_GetPath NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:13 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:2 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__

x_GetTagName
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
	token.nNext = m_aPos[iPos].nStart + 1;
	if ( ! iPos || ! x_FindName( token ) )
		return "";


	return x_GetToken( token );
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:4 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:10 LOCALS:14 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1411 L_END:1420 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_GetTagName NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:4 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_FindAttrib
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( CMarkupSTL::TokenPos& token, const char* szAttrib, int n
 )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 






	int nPreSpaceStart;
	int nPreSpaceLength;
	int nChar;
	char cFirstChar;
	const char* szDoc = token.szDoc;
	int nAttrib = -1;
	int nFoundAttribNameR = 0;
	bool bAfterEqual = false;
	while ( 1 )
	{ 

		nChar = token.nNext;
		nPreSpaceStart = nChar;
		if ( ! x_FindAny(szDoc,nChar) )
			break;
		nPreSpaceLength = nChar - nPreSpaceStart;


		cFirstChar = szDoc[nChar];
		if ( cFirstChar == '\"' || cFirstChar == '\'' )
		{ 
			token.nTokenFlags |= MNF_QUOTED;


			++nChar;
			token.nL = nChar;


			while ( szDoc[nChar] && szDoc[nChar] != cFirstChar )
				++nChar;


			token.nR = nChar - 1;


			if ( szDoc[nChar] )
				++nChar;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			token.nTokenFlags &= ~MNF_QUOTED;


			token.nL = nChar;
			if ( bAfterEqual )
			{ 
				while ( szDoc[nChar] && ! strchr(" \t\n\r>",szDoc[nChar]) )
					++nChar;
			 }
			else
			{ 
				while ( szDoc[nChar] && ! strchr("= \t\n\r>/?",szDoc[nChar]) )
					++nChar;
			 }


			if ( nChar == token.nL )
				++nChar;
			token.nR = nChar - 1;
		 }


		token.nNext = nChar;

		if ( ! bAfterEqual && ! (token.nTokenFlags&MNF_QUOTED) )
		{ 

			char cChar = szDoc[token.nL];
			if ( cChar == '=' )
			{ 
				bAfterEqual = true;
				continue;
			 }


			if ( cChar == '>' || cChar == '/' || cChar == '?' )
			{ 
				token.nNext = nPreSpaceStart;
				break;
			 }

			if ( nFoundAttribNameR )
				break;


			if ( nAttrib != -1 )
			{ 
				if ( ! szAttrib )
				{ 
					if ( nAttrib == n )
						return true;
				 }
				else if ( token.Match(szAttrib) )
				{ 

					nFoundAttribNameR = token.nR;
					token.nPreSpaceStart = nPreSpaceStart;
					token.nPreSpaceLength = nPreSpaceLength;
				 }
			 }
			++nAttrib;
		 }
		else if ( nFoundAttribNameR )
			break;
		bAfterEqual = false;
	 }

	if ( nFoundAttribNameR )
	{ 
		if ( ! bAfterEqual )
		{ 

			token.nL = token.nPreSpaceStart + token.nPreSpaceLength;
			token.nR = nFoundAttribNameR;
			token.nNext = nFoundAttribNameR + 1;
		 }
		return true;
	 }
	return false;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_NAME__
x_GetAttrib
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos, const char* szAttrib )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
	if ( iPos && m_nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
		token.nNext = m_aPos[iPos].nStart + 1;
	else if ( iPos == m_iPos && m_nNodeLength && m_nNodeType == MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION )
		token.nNext = m_nNodeOffset + 2;
	else
		return "";

	if ( szAttrib && x_FindAttrib( token, szAttrib ) )
		return UnescapeText( &token.szDoc[token.nL], token.Length() );
	return "";
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:2 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:12 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1568 L_END:1573 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_SetAttrib NONLCALS:1 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:3 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_SetAttrib
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos, const char* szAttrib, const char* szValue )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
	if ( iPos && m_nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
		token.nNext = m_aPos[iPos].nStart + 1;
	else if ( iPos == m_iPos && m_nNodeLength && m_nNodeType == MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION )
		token.nNext = m_nNodeOffset + 2;
	else
		return false;



	int nReplace = 0;
	int nInsertAt;
	string strInsert;
	strInsert += x_ATTRIBQUOTE;
	strInsert += EscapeText( szValue, MNF_ESCAPEQUOTES );
	strInsert += x_ATTRIBQUOTE;
	if ( x_FindAttrib( token, szAttrib ) )
	{ 

		nInsertAt = token.nL - ((token.nTokenFlags&MNF_QUOTED)?1:0);
		nReplace = token.Length() + ((token.nTokenFlags&MNF_QUOTED)?2:0);
	 }
	else
	{ 

		string strFormat;
		strFormat = " ";
		strFormat += szAttrib;
		strFormat += "=";
		strFormat += strInsert;
		strInsert = strFormat;
		nInsertAt = token.nNext;
	 }

	x_DocChange( nInsertAt, nReplace, strInsert );
	int nAdjust = (int)strInsert.size() - nReplace;
	if ( m_nNodeType == MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION )
	{ 
		x_AdjustForNode( m_iPosParent, m_iPos, nAdjust );
		m_nNodeLength += nAdjust;
		MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE;
		return true;
	 }
	m_aPos[iPos].AdjustStartTagLen( nAdjust );
	m_aPos[iPos].nLength += nAdjust;
	x_Adjust( iPos, nAdjust );
	MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE;
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:3 ASM:0 ASS:18 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:9 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:5 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:11 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:3 ENUM:0 EQTEST:4 EXPRORCALL:18 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:4 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:4 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:51 LOCALS:90 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1576 L_END:1626 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_SetAttrib NONLCALS:3 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:3 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:30 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:2 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_CreateNode
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( string& strNode, int nNodeType, const char* szText )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	switch ( nNodeType )
	{ 
	case MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION:
		strNode = "<?";
		strNode += szText;
		strNode += "?>";
		break;
	case MNT_COMMENT:
		strNode = "<!--";
		strNode += szText;
		strNode += "-->";
		break;
	case MNT_ELEMENT:
		strNode = "<";
		strNode += szText;
		strNode += "/>";
		break;
	case MNT_TEXT:
	case MNT_WHITESPACE:
		strNode = EscapeText( szText );
		break;
	case MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE:
		strNode = szText;
		break;
	case MNT_LONE_END_TAG:
		return false;
	case MNT_CDATA_SECTION:
		if ( strstr(szText,"]]>") != NULL )
			return false;
		strNode = "<![CDATA[";
		strNode += szText;
		strNode += "]]>";
		break;
	 }
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:2 ASM:0 ASS:15 AUTO:0 BREAK:6 CALLS:2 CASE:8 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:11 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:4 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:3 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:2 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:40 LOCALS:40 LONG:0 LT:4 L_BEGIN:1630 L_END:1669 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:2 NAME:x_CreateNode NONLCALS:7 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:3 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:23 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:1 TERNINSTR:2 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_EncodeCDATASection
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szData )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	string strData = "<![CDATA[";
	const char* pszNextStart = szData;
	const char* pszEnd = strstr( szData, "]]>" );
	while ( pszEnd )
	{ 
		strData += string( pszNextStart, (int)(pszEnd - pszNextStart) );
		strData += "]]]]><![CDATA[>";
		pszNextStart = pszEnd + 3;
		pszEnd = strstr( pszNextStart, "]]>" );
	 }
	strData += pszNextStart;
	strData += "]]>";
	return strData;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:2 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:12 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1690 L_END:1695 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_SetData NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:3 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_SetData
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos, const char* szData, int nFlags )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	string strInsert;

	if ( iPos == m_iPos && m_nNodeLength )
	{ 

		if ( ! x_CreateNode(strInsert, m_nNodeType, szData) )
			return false;
		x_DocChange( m_nNodeOffset, m_nNodeLength, strInsert );
		x_AdjustForNode( m_iPosParent, iPos, (int)strInsert.size() - m_nNodeLength );
		m_nNodeLength = (int)strInsert.size();
		MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE;
		return true;
	 }


	if ( ! iPos || m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild )
		return false;


	if ( nFlags & MNF_WITHCDATA )
		strInsert = x_EncodeCDATASection( szData );
	else
		strInsert = EscapeText( szData, nFlags );


	NodePos node( MNF_WITHNOLINES|MNF_REPLACE );
	node.strMeta = strInsert;
	int iPosBefore = 0;
	int nReplace = x_InsertNew( iPos, iPosBefore, node );
	int nAdjust = (int)node.strMeta.size() - nReplace;
	x_Adjust( iPos, nAdjust );
	m_aPos[iPos].nLength += nAdjust;
	if ( m_aPos[iPos].nFlags & MNF_ILLDATA )
		m_aPos[iPos].nFlags &= ~MNF_ILLDATA;
	MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE;
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_SetData::string::strInsert::iPos::m_iPos::m_nNodeLength::x_CreateNode::strInsert::m_nNodeType::szData::false::x_DocChange::m_nNodeOffset::m_nNodeLength::strInsert::x_AdjustForNode::m_iPosParent::iPos::strInsert::size::m_nNodeLength::m_nNodeLength::strInsert::size::MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE::true::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemChild::false::nFlags::MNF_WITHCDATA::strInsert::x_EncodeCDATASection::szData::strInsert::EscapeText::szData::nFlags::NodePos::node::MNF_WITHNOLINES::MNF_REPLACE::node::strMeta::strInsert::iPosBefore::nReplace::x_InsertNew::iPos::iPosBefore::node::nAdjust::node::strMeta::size::nReplace::x_Adjust::iPos::nAdjust::m_aPos::iPos::nLength::nAdjust::m_aPos::iPos::nFlags::MNF_ILLDATA::m_aPos::iPos::nFlags::MNF_ILLDATA::MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE::true

#METRICS ARRAYOP:4 ASM:0 ASS:9 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:11 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:6 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:9 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:1 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:19 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:5 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:6 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:40 LOCALS:59 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1698 L_END:1737 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_SetData NONLCALS:3 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:4 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:20 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_GetData
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	if ( iPos == m_iPos && m_nNodeLength )
	{ 
		if ( m_nNodeType == MNT_COMMENT )
			return m_strDoc.substr( m_nNodeOffset+4, m_nNodeLength-7 );
		else if ( m_nNodeType == MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION )
			return m_strDoc.substr( m_nNodeOffset+2, m_nNodeLength-4 );
		else if ( m_nNodeType == MNT_CDATA_SECTION )
			return m_strDoc.substr( m_nNodeOffset+9, m_nNodeLength-12 );
		else if ( m_nNodeType == MNT_TEXT )
			return UnescapeText( &(m_strDoc.c_str())[m_nNodeOffset], m_nNodeLength );
		else if ( m_nNodeType == MNT_LONE_END_TAG )
			return m_strDoc.substr( m_nNodeOffset+2, m_nNodeLength-3 );
		else
			return m_strDoc.substr( m_nNodeOffset, m_nNodeLength );
	 }



	string strData;
	if ( ! m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild && ! m_aPos[iPos].IsEmptyElement() )
	{ 

		int nContentLen = m_aPos[iPos].ContentLen();
		int nStartContent = m_aPos[iPos].StartContent();
		const char* pszContent = &(m_strDoc.c_str())[nStartContent];
		const char* pszTag = strchr( pszContent, '<' );
		if ( pszTag && ((int)(pszTag-pszContent) < nContentLen) )
		{ 

			TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
			token.nNext = nStartContent;
			NodePos node;
			while ( token.nNext < nStartContent + nContentLen )
			{ 
				x_ParseNode( token, node );
				if ( node.nNodeType == MNT_TEXT )
					strData += UnescapeText( &token.szDoc[node.nStart], node.nLength );
				else if ( node.nNodeType == MNT_CDATA_SECTION )
					strData += m_strDoc.substr( node.nStart+9, node.nLength-12 );
			 }
		 }
		else
			strData = UnescapeText( &(m_strDoc.c_str())[nStartContent], nContentLen );
	 }
	return strData;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:3 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:4 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:4 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:5 LOCALS:7 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1789 L_END:1793 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_GetElemContent NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_SetElemContent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szContent )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	if ( ! m_iPos )
		return false;

	if ( m_nNodeLength )
		return false;


	int iPos = m_iPos;
	int iPosChild = m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild;
	bool bHadChild = (iPosChild != 0);
	while ( iPosChild )
		iPosChild = x_ReleaseSubDoc( iPosChild );
	if ( bHadChild )
		x_CheckSavedPos();


	bool bWellFormed = true;
	TokenPos token( szContent, m_nFlags );
	int iPosVirtual = x_GetFreePos();
	m_aPos[iPosVirtual].ClearVirtualParent();
	m_aPos[iPosVirtual].SetLevel( m_aPos[iPos].Level() + 1 );
	iPosChild = x_ParseElem( iPosVirtual, token );
	if ( m_aPos[iPosVirtual].nFlags & MNF_ILLFORMED )
		bWellFormed = false;
	m_aPos[iPos].nFlags = (m_aPos[iPos].nFlags & ~MNF_ILLDATA) | (m_aPos[iPosVirtual].nFlags & MNF_ILLDATA);


	NodePos node( MNF_WITHNOLINES|MNF_REPLACE );
	node.strMeta = szContent;
	int iPosBefore = 0;
	int nReplace = x_InsertNew( iPos, iPosBefore, node );
	

	x_Adjust( iPosChild, node.nStart );
	m_aPos[iPosChild].nStart += node.nStart;
	m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild = iPosChild;
	while ( iPosChild )
	{ 
		m_aPos[iPosChild].iElemParent = iPos;
		iPosChild = m_aPos[iPosChild].iElemNext;
	 }
	x_ReleasePos( iPosVirtual );

	int nAdjust = (int)node.strMeta.size() - nReplace;
	x_Adjust( iPos, nAdjust, true );
	m_aPos[iPos].nLength += nAdjust;

	x_SetPos( m_iPosParent, m_iPos, 0 );
	return bWellFormed;
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:13 ASM:0 ASS:19 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:15 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:7 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:18 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:25 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:4 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:7 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:52 LOCALS:74 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1796 L_END:1847 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_SetElemContent NONLCALS:2 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:3 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:30 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:2 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_DocChange
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int nLeft, int nReplace, const string& strInsert )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	int nDocLength = (int)m_strDoc.size();
	int nInsLength = (int)strInsert.size();
	int nNewLength = nInsLength + nDocLength - nReplace;



	int nBufferLen = nNewLength;
	int nAllocLen = (int)m_strDoc.capacity();
	if ( nNewLength > nAllocLen )
	{ 
		nBufferLen += nBufferLe  + 128;
		if ( nBufferLen < nNewLength )
			nBufferLen = nNewLength;
		m_strDoc.reserve( nBufferLen );
	 }

	m_strDoc.replace( nLeft, nReplace, strInsert );

 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_DocChange::nDocLength::m_strDoc::size::nInsLength::strInsert::size::nNewLength::nInsLength::nDocLength::nReplace::nBufferLen::nNewLength::nAllocLen::m_strDoc::capacity::nNewLength::nAllocLen::nBufferLen::nBufferLe::nBufferLen::nNewLength::nBufferLen::nNewLength::m_strDoc::reserve::nBufferLen::m_strDoc::replace::nLeft::nReplace::strInsert
__END_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:7 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:5 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:5 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:10 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:8 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:23 LOCALS:33 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:1850 L_END:1872 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_DocChange NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:9 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_Adjust
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos, int nShift, bool bAfterPos
 )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 







	int iPosTop = m_aPos[iPos].iElemParent;
	bool bPosFirst = bAfterPos;


	while ( m_aPos[iPos].StartTagLen() )
	{ 

		bool bPosTop = false;
		if ( iPos == iPosTop )
		{ 

			iPosTop = m_aPos[iPos].iElemParent;
			bPosTop = true;
		 }


		if ( ! bPosTop && ! bPosFirst && m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild )
		{ 

			iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild;
		 }
		else if ( m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext )
		{ 
			iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext;
		 }
		else
		{ 


			while ( 1 )
			{ 
				iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemParent;
				if ( iPos == iPosTop )
					break;
				if ( m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext )
				{ 
					iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext;
					break;
				 }
			 }
		 }
		bPosFirst = false;


		if ( iPos != iPosTop )
			m_aPos[iPos].nStart += nShift;
		else
			m_aPos[iPos].nLength += nShift;
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_Adjust::iPosTop::m_aPos::iPos::iElemParent::bPosFirst::bAfterPos::m_aPos::iPos::StartTagLen::bPosTop::false::iPos::iPosTop::iPosTop::m_aPos::iPos::iElemParent::bPosTop::true::bPosTop::bPosFirst::m_aPos::iPos::iElemChild::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemChild::m_aPos::iPos::iElemNext::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemNext::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemParent::iPos::iPosTop::m_aPos::iPos::iElemNext::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::iElemNext::bPosFirst::false::iPos::iPosTop::m_aPos::iPos::nStart::nShift::m_aPos::iPos::nLength::nShift

#METRICS ARRAYOP:12 ASM:0 ASS:13 AUTO:0 BREAK:2 CALLS:1 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:9 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:12 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:3 ENUM:0 EQTEST:2 EXPRORCALL:9 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:6 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:58 LOCALS:83 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1875 L_END:1932 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_Adjust NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:14 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:2 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_InsertNew
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPosParent, int& iPosRel, CMarkupSTL::NodePos& node )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	bool bEmptyParentTag = iPosParent && m_aPos[iPosParent].IsEmptyElement();
	bool bNoContentParentTags = iPosParent && ! m_aPos[iPosParent].ContentLen();
	if ( node.nLength )
	{ 

		if ( ! (node.nFlags & MNF_INSERT) )
			node.nStart += node.nLength;
	 }
	else if ( iPosRel )
	{ 

		node.nStart = m_aPos[iPosRel].nStart;
		if ( ! (node.nFlags & MNF_INSERT) )
			node.nStart += m_aPos[iPosRel].nLength;
	 }
	else if ( bEmptyParentTag )
	{ 

		if ( m_aPos[iPosParent].nFlags & MNF_NONENDED )
			node.nStart = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartContent();
		else
			node.nStart = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartContent() - 1;
	 }
	else
	{ 
		if ( node.nFlags & (MNF_INSERT|MNF_REPLACE) )
			node.nStart = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartContent();
		else
			node.nStart = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartAfter() - m_aPos[iPosParent].EndTagLen();
	 }


	if ( ! (node.nFlags&(MNF_WITHNOLINES|MNF_REPLACE)) && ! bEmptyParentTag )
	{ 
		const char* szDoc = m_strDoc.c_str();
		int nChar = node.nStart;
		if ( ! x_FindAny(szDoc,nChar) || szDoc[nChar] == '<' )
			node.nStart = nChar;
	 }


	if ( ! node.nLength )
	{ 

		if ( iPosRel )
		{ 
			if ( node.nFlags & MNF_INSERT )
			{ 
				if ( ! (m_aPos[iPosRel].nFlags & MNF_FIRST) )
					iPosRel = m_aPos[iPosRel].iElemPrev;
				else
					iPosRel = 0;
			 }
		 }
		else if ( ! (node.nFlags & MNF_INSERT) )
		{ 

			if ( m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild )
				iPosRel = m_aPos[m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild].iElemPrev;
		 }
	 }


	node.nLength = (int)node.strMeta.size();


	if ( (! (node.nFlags & MNF_WITHNOLINES)) && (bEmptyParentTag || bNoContentParentTags) )
		node.nStart += x_EOLLEN;
	if ( ! (node.nFlags & MNF_WITHNOLINES) )
		node.strMeta += x_EOL;


	int nReplace = 0;
	int nInsertAt = node.nStart;
	if ( bEmptyParentTag )
	{ 
		string strTagName = x_GetTagName( iPosParent );
		string strFormat;
		if ( node.nFlags & MNF_WITHNOLINES )
			strFormat = ">";
		else
			strFormat = ">" x_EOL;
		strFormat += node.strMeta;
		strFormat += "</";
		strFormat += strTagName;
		node.strMeta = strFormat;
		if ( m_aPos[iPosParent].nFlags & MNF_NONENDED )
		{ 
			nInsertAt = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartAfter() - 1;
			nReplace = 0;
			m_aPos[iPosParent].nFlags ^= MNF_NONENDED;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			nInsertAt = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartAfter() - 2;
			nReplace = 1;
			m_aPos[iPosParent].AdjustStartTagLen( -1 );
		 }
		m_aPos[iPosParent].SetEndTagLen( 3 + (int)strTagName.size() );
	 }
	else
	{ 
		if ( node.nFlags & MNF_REPLACE )
		{ 
			nInsertAt = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartContent();
			nReplace = m_aPos[iPosParent].ContentLen();
		 }
		else if ( bNoContentParentTags )
		{ 
			node.strMeta = x_EOL + node.strMeta;
			nInsertAt = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartContent();
		 }
	 }
	x_DocChange( nInsertAt, nReplace, node.strMeta );
	return nReplace;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_InsertNew::bEmptyParentTag::iPosParent::m_aPos::iPosParent::IsEmptyElement::bNoContentParentTags::iPosParent::m_aPos::iPosParent::ContentLen::node::nLength::node::nFlags::MNF_INSERT::node::nStart::node::nLength::iPosRel::node::nStart::m_aPos::iPosRel::nStart::node::nFlags::MNF_INSERT::node::nStart::m_aPos::iPosRel::nLength::bEmptyParentTag::m_aPos::iPosParent::nFlags::MNF_NONENDED::node::nStart::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartContent::node::nStart::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartContent::node::nFlags::MNF_INSERT::MNF_REPLACE::node::nStart::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartContent::node::nStart::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartAfter::m_aPos::iPosParent::EndTagLen::node::nFlags::MNF_WITHNOLINES::MNF_REPLACE::bEmptyParentTag::szDoc::m_strDoc::c_str::nChar::node::nStart::x_FindAny::szDoc::nChar::szDoc::nChar::node::nStart::nChar::node::nLength::iPosRel::node::nFlags::MNF_INSERT::m_aPos::iPosRel::nFlags::MNF_FIRST::iPosRel::m_aPos::iPosRel::iElemPrev::iPosRel::node::nFlags::MNF_INSERT::m_aPos::iPosParent::iElemChild::iPosRel::m_aPos::m_aPos::iPosParent::iElemChild::iElemPrev::node::nLength::node::strMeta::size::node::nFlags::MNF_WITHNOLINES::bEmptyParentTag::bNoContentParentTags::node::nStart::x_EOLLEN::node::nFlags::MNF_WITHNOLINES::node::strMeta::x_EOL::nReplace::nInsertAt::node::nStart::bEmptyParentTag::string::strTagName::x_GetTagName::iPosParent::string::strFormat::node::nFlags::MNF_WITHNOLINES::strFormat::strFormat::x_EOL::strFormat::node::strMeta::strFormat::strFormat::strTagName::node::strMeta::strFormat::m_aPos::iPosParent::nFlags::MNF_NONENDED::nInsertAt::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartAfter::nReplace::m_aPos::iPosParent::nFlags::MNF_NONENDED::nInsertAt::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartAfter::nReplace::m_aPos::iPosParent::AdjustStartTagLen::m_aPos::iPosParent::SetEndTagLen::strTagName::size::node::nFlags::MNF_REPLACE::nInsertAt::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartContent::nReplace::m_aPos::iPosParent::ContentLen::bNoContentParentTags::node::strMeta::x_EOL::node::strMeta::nInsertAt::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartContent::x_DocChange::nInsertAt::nReplace::node::strMeta::nReplace
__END_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:25 ASM:0 ASS:36 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:20 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:1 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:23 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:59 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:11 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:55 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:1 IF:22 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:5 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:118 LOCALS:204 LONG:0 LT:2 L_BEGIN:1935 L_END:2052 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_InsertNew NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:41 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0

( const char* szName, int nValue, int nFlags )

	char szVal[25];

	return x_AddElem( szName, szVal, nFlags );

x_AddElem::szVal::sprintf::szVal::d::nValue::x_AddElem::szName::szVal::nFlags

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:2 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:12 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:2055 L_END:2060 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_AddElem NONLCALS:1 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:3 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_AddElem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szName, const char* szValue, int nFlags )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	if ( nFlags & MNF_CHILD )
	{ 

		if ( ! m_iPos )
			return false;
	 }


	NodePos node( nFlags );
	int iPosParent, iPosBefore;
	if ( nFlags & MNF_CHILD )
	{ 
		iPosParent = m_iPos;
		iPosBefore = m_iPosChild;
	 }
	else
	{ 
		iPosParent = m_iPosParent;
		iPosBefore = m_iPos;
		node.nStart = m_nNodeOffset;
		node.nLength = m_nNodeLength;
	 }


	if ( (nFlags&MNF_WITHNOEND) && szValue && szValue[0] )
		return false;


	int iPos = x_GetFreePos();





	ElemPos* pElem = &m_aPos[iPos];
	int nLenName = (int)strlen(szName);
	if ( ! szValue || ! szValue[0] )
	{ 

		node.strMeta = "<";
		node.strMeta += szName;
		if ( nFlags & MNF_WITHNOEND )
		{ 
			node.strMeta += ">";
			pElem->SetStartTagLen( nLenName + 2 );
			pElem->nLength = nLenName + 2;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			if ( nFlags & MNF_WITHXHTMLSPACE )
			{ 
				node.strMeta += " />";
				pElem->SetStartTagLen( nLenName + 4 );
				pElem->nLength = nLenName + 4;
			 }
			else
			{ 
				node.strMeta += "/>";
				pElem->SetStartTagLen( nLenName + 3 );
				pElem->nLength = nLenName + 3;
			 }
		 }
		pElem->SetEndTagLen( 0 );
	 }
	else
	{ 

		string strValue;
		if ( nFlags & MNF_WITHCDATA )
			strValue = x_EncodeCDATASection( szValue );
		else
			strValue = EscapeText( szValue, nFlags );
		int nLenValue = (int)strValue.size();
		node.strMeta = "<";
		node.strMeta += szName;
		node.strMeta += ">";
		node.strMeta += strValue;
		node.strMeta += "</";
		node.strMeta += szName;
		node.strMeta += ">";
		pElem->SetEndTagLen( nLenName + 3 );
		pElem->nLength = nLenName * 2 + nLenValue + 5;
		pElem->SetStartTagLen( nLenName + 2 );
	 }


	int nReplace = x_InsertNew( iPosParent, iPosBefore, node );

	pElem->nStart = node.nStart;
	pElem->iElemChild = 0;
	if ( nFlags & MNF_WITHNOEND )
		pElem->nFlags = MNF_NONENDED;
	else
		pElem->nFlags = 0;
	x_LinkElem( iPosParent, iPosBefore, iPos );

	x_Adjust( iPos, (int)node.strMeta.size() - nReplace );

	if ( nFlags & MNF_CHILD )
		x_SetPos( m_iPosParent, iPosParent, iPos );
	else
		x_SetPos( iPosParent, iPos, 0 );
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_GetSubDoc
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	if ( iPos )
	{ 
		int nStart = m_aPos[iPos].nStart;
		int nNext = nStart + m_aPos[iPos].nLength;
		const char* szDoc = m_strDoc.c_str();
		int nChar = nNext;
		if ( ! x_FindAny(szDoc,nChar) || szDoc[nChar] == '<' )
			nNext = nChar;
		return m_strDoc.substr( nStart, nNext - nStart );
	 }
	return "";
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:3 ASM:0 ASS:5 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:1 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:4 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:3 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:13 LOCALS:30 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:2170 L_END:2182 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_GetSubDoc NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:7 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_AddSubDoc
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( const char* szSubDoc, int nFlags )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	NodePos node( nFlags );
	int iPosParent, iPosBefore;
	if ( nFlags & MNF_CHILD )
	{ 

		if ( ! m_iPos )
			return false;
		iPosParent = m_iPos;
		iPosBefore = m_iPosChild;
	 }
	else
	{ 

		iPosParent = m_iPosParent;
		iPosBefore = m_iPos;
		node.nStart = m_nNodeOffset;
		node.nLength = m_nNodeLength;
	 }


	bool bWellFormed = true;
	TokenPos token( szSubDoc, m_nFlags );
	int iPosVirtual = x_GetFreePos();
	m_aPos[iPosVirtual].ClearVirtualParent();
	m_aPos[iPosVirtual].SetLevel( m_aPos[iPosParent].Level() + 1 );
	int iPos = x_ParseElem( iPosVirtual, token );
	if ( (!iPos) || m_aPos[iPosVirtual].nFlags & MNF_ILLFORMED )
		bWellFormed = false;
	if ( m_aPos[iPosVirtual].nFlags & MNF_ILLDATA )
		m_aPos[iPosParent].nFlags |= MNF_ILLDATA;


	int nExtractStart = 0;
	int iPosLast = m_aPos[iPos].iElemPrev;
	if ( bWellFormed )
	{ 
		nExtractStart = m_aPos[iPos].nStart;
		int nExtractLength = m_aPos[iPos].nLength;
		if ( iPos != iPosLast )
		{ 
			nExtractLength = m_aPos[iPosLast].nStart - nExtractStart + m_aPos[iPosLast].nLength;
			bWellFormed = false;
		 }
		node.strMeta.assign( &szSubDoc[nExtractStart], nExtractLength );
	 }
	else
	{ 
		node.strMeta = szSubDoc;
		node.nFlags |= MNF_WITHNOLINES;
	 }


	int nReplace = x_InsertNew( iPosParent, iPosBefore, node );



	int nAdjust = node.nStart - nExtractStart;
	if ( iPos && nAdjust )
	{ 
		x_Adjust( iPos, nAdjust );
		m_aPos[iPos].nStart += nAdjust;
	 }
	int iPosChild = iPos;
	while ( iPosChild )
	{ 
		int iPosNext = m_aPos[iPosChild].iElemNext;
		x_LinkElem( iPosParent, iPosBefore, iPosChild );
		iPosBefore = iPosChild;
		iPosChild = iPosNext;
	 }
	x_ReleasePos( iPosVirtual );


	x_Adjust( iPosLast, (int)node.strMeta.size() - nReplace, true );


	if ( nFlags & MNF_CHILD )
		x_SetPos( m_iPosParent, iPosParent, iPos );
	else
		x_SetPos( m_iPosParent, iPos, 0 );
	return bWellFormed;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_RemoveElem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	if ( ! iPos )
		return 0;


	int nAfterEnd = m_aPos[iPos].StartAfter();
	const char* szDoc = m_strDoc.c_str();
	int nChar = nAfterEnd;
	if ( ! x_FindAny(szDoc,nChar) || szDoc[nChar] == '<' )
		nAfterEnd = nChar;


	int nLen = nAfterEnd - m_aPos[iPos].nStart;
	x_DocChange( m_aPos[iPos].nStart, nLen, string() );
	x_Adjust( iPos, - nLen, true );
	int iPosPrev = x_UnlinkElem( iPos );
	x_CheckSavedPos();
	return iPosPrev;
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:4 ASM:0 ASS:6 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:8 CASE:0 CHAR:1 CLASS:0 CONST:1 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:4 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:10 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:4 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:22 LOCALS:28 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:2272 L_END:2293 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_RemoveElem NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:11 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_LinkElem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPosParent, int iPosBefore, int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	ElemPos* pElem = &m_aPos[iPos];
	pElem->iElemParent = iPosParent;
	if ( iPosBefore )
	{ 

		pElem->nFlags &= ~MNF_FIRST;
		pElem->iElemNext = m_aPos[iPosBefore].iElemNext;
		if ( pElem->iElemNext )
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemNext].iElemPrev = iPos;
		else
			m_aPos[m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild].iElemPrev = iPos;
		m_aPos[iPosBefore].iElemNext = iPos;
		pElem->iElemPrev = iPosBefore;
	 }
	else
	{ 

		pElem->nFlags |= MNF_FIRST;
		if ( m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild )
		{ 
			pElem->iElemNext = m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild;
			pElem->iElemPrev = m_aPos[pElem->iElemNext].iElemPrev;
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemNext].iElemPrev = iPos;
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemNext].nFlags ^= MNF_FIRST;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			pElem->iElemNext = 0;
			pElem->iElemPrev = iPos;
		 }
		m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild = iPos;
	 }
	if ( iPosParent )
		pElem->SetLevel( m_aPos[iPosParent].Level() + 1 );
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_UnlinkElem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	ElemPos* pElem = &m_aPos[iPos];


	int iPosPrev = 0;
	if ( pElem->nFlags & MNF_FIRST )
	{ 
		if ( pElem->iElemNext )
		{ 
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemParent].iElemChild = pElem->iElemNext;
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemNext].iElemPrev = pElem->iElemPrev;
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemNext].nFlags |= MNF_FIRST;
		 }
		else
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemParent].iElemChild = 0;
	 }
	else
	{ 
		iPosPrev = pElem->iElemPrev;
		m_aPos[iPosPrev].iElemNext = pElem->iElemNext;
		if ( pElem->iElemNext )
			m_aPos[pElem->iElemNext].iElemPrev = iPosPrev;
		else
			m_aPos[m_aPos[pElem->iElemParent].iElemChild].iElemPrev = iPosPrev;
	 }
	x_ReleaseSubDoc( iPos );
	return iPosPrev;
 }
__END_BODY__

( int iPos )

	int iPosNext = m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext;
	m_aPos[iPos].iElemNext = m_iPosDeleted;
	m_aPos[iPos].nFlags = MNF_DELETED;
	m_iPosDeleted = iPos;

 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:3 ASM:0 ASS:4 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:0 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:3 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:0 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:7 LOCALS:15 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:2367 L_END:2373 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_ReleasePos NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:5 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_ReleaseSubDoc
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPos )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 




	int iPosNext = 0, iPosTop = iPos;
	while ( 1 )
	{ 
		if ( m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild )
			iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemChild;
		else
		{ 
			while ( 1 )
			{ 
				iPosNext = x_ReleasePos( iPos );
				if ( iPos == iPosTop )
					return iPosNext;
				if ( iPosNext )
					break;
				iPos = m_aPos[iPos].iElemParent;
			 }
			iPos = iPosNext;
		 }
	 }
	return iPosNext;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_CheckSavedPos
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	if ( m_mapSavedPos.pTable )
	{ 
		for ( int nSlot = 0; nSlot < SavedPosMap::SPM_SIZE; ++nSlot )
		{ 
			SavedPos* pSavedPos = m_mapSavedPos.pTable[nSlot];
			if ( pSavedPos )
			{ 
				int nOffset = 0;
				int nSavedPosCount = 0;
				while ( 1 )
				{ 
					if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_USED )
					{ 
						int iPos = pSavedPos[nOffset].iPos;
						if ( ! (m_aPos[iPos].nFlags & MNF_DELETED) )
						{ 
							if ( nSavedPosCount < nOffset )
							{ 
								pSavedPos[nSavedPosCount] = pSavedPos[nOffset];
								pSavedPos[nSavedPosCount].nSavedPosFlags &= ~SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST;
							 }
							++nSavedPosCount;
						 }
					 }
					if ( pSavedPos[nOffset].nSavedPosFlags & SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST )
					{ 
						while ( nSavedPosCount <= nOffset )
							pSavedPos[nSavedPosCount++].nSavedPosFlags &= ~SavedPosMap::SPM_USED;
						break;
					 }
					++nOffset;
				 }
			 }
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_CheckSavedPos::m_mapSavedPos::pTable::nSlot::nSlot::SavedPosMap::SPM_SIZE::nSlot::SavedPos::pSavedPos::m_mapSavedPos::pTable::nSlot::pSavedPos::nOffset::nSavedPosCount::pSavedPos::nOffset::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_USED::iPos::pSavedPos::nOffset::iPos::m_aPos::iPos::nFlags::MNF_DELETED::nSavedPosCount::nOffset::pSavedPos::nSavedPosCount::pSavedPos::nOffset::pSavedPos::nSavedPosCount::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::nSavedPosCount::pSavedPos::nOffset::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_LAST::nSavedPosCount::nOffset::pSavedPos::nSavedPosCount::nSavedPosFlags::SavedPosMap::SPM_USED::nOffset

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_AdjustForNode
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPosParent, int iPos, int nShift )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	bool bAfterPos = true;
	if ( ! iPos )
	{ 



		iPos = m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild;
		if ( iPos )
		{ 
			m_aPos[iPos].nStart += nShift;
			bAfterPos = false;
		 }
		else
		{ 
			iPos = iPosParent;
			m_aPos[iPos].nLength += nShift;
		 }
	 }
	x_Adjust( iPos, nShift, bAfterPos );
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:3 ASM:0 ASS:6 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:1 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:3 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:1 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:22 LOCALS:41 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:2445 L_END:2466 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_AdjustForNode NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:7 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_AddNode
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int nNodeType, const char* szText, int nFlags )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



	if ( ! (nNodeType & (MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION|MNT_COMMENT|MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE|MNT_CDATA_SECTION)) )
		nFlags |= MNF_WITHNOLINES;


	NodePos node( nFlags );
	if ( ! x_CreateNode(node.strMeta, nNodeType, szText) )
		return false;


	int iPosBefore = m_iPos;
	int iPosParent = m_iPosParent;
	node.nStart = m_nNodeOffset;
	node.nLength = m_nNodeLength;
	node.nNodeType = nNodeType;

	int nReplace = x_InsertNew( iPosParent, iPosBefore, node );


	int iPos = iPosBefore;
	if ( nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
	{ 

		iPos = x_GetFreePos();
		ElemPos* pElem = &m_aPos[iPos];
		pElem->nStart = node.nStart;
		pElem->SetStartTagLen( node.nLength );
		pElem->SetEndTagLen( 0 );
		pElem->nLength = node.nLength;
		node.nStart = 0;
		node.nLength = 0;
		pElem->iElemChild = 0;
		pElem->nFlags = 0;
		x_LinkElem( iPosParent, iPosBefore, iPos );
	 }


	x_AdjustForNode( iPosParent, iPos, (int)node.strMeta.size() - nReplace );


	m_iPos = iPos;
	m_iPosChild = 0;
	m_nNodeOffset = node.nStart;
	m_nNodeLength = node.nLength;
	m_nNodeType = nNodeType;
	MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE;
	return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_AddNode::nNodeType::MNT_PROCESSING_INSTRUCTION::MNT_COMMENT::MNT_DOCUMENT_TYPE::MNT_CDATA_SECTION::nFlags::MNF_WITHNOLINES::NodePos::node::nFlags::x_CreateNode::node::strMeta::nNodeType::szText::false::iPosBefore::m_iPos::iPosParent::m_iPosParent::node::nStart::m_nNodeOffset::node::nLength::m_nNodeLength::node::nNodeType::nNodeType::nReplace::x_InsertNew::iPosParent::iPosBefore::node::iPos::iPosBefore::nNodeType::MNT_ELEMENT::iPos::x_GetFreePos::ElemPos::pElem::m_aPos::iPos::pElem::nStart::node::nStart::pElem::SetStartTagLen::node::nLength::pElem::SetEndTagLen::pElem::nLength::node::nLength::node::nStart::node::nLength::pElem::iElemChild::pElem::nFlags::x_LinkElem::iPosParent::iPosBefore::iPos::x_AdjustForNode::iPosParent::iPos::node::strMeta::size::nReplace::m_iPos::iPos::m_iPosChild::m_nNodeOffset::node::nStart::m_nNodeLength::node::nLength::m_nNodeType::nNodeType::MARKUP_SETDEBUGSTATE::true

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:21 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:9 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:13 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:15 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/xml/markupstl.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:3 IN:0 INDR:7 INLINE:0 INT:5 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:51 LOCALS:73 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:2469 L_END:2519 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:x_AddNode NONLCALS:1 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:29 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
x_RemoveNode
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
( int iPosParent, int& iPos, int& nNodeType, int& nNodeOffset, int& nNodeLength )
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	int iPosPrev = iPos;


	if ( nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
	{ 
		nNodeOffset = m_aPos[iPos].nStart;
		nNodeLength = m_aPos[iPos].nLength;
		iPosPrev = x_UnlinkElem( iPos );
		x_CheckSavedPos();
	 }


	int nPrevOffset = 0;
	if ( iPosPrev )
		nPrevOffset = m_aPos[iPosPrev].StartAfter();
	else if ( iPosParent )
		nPrevOffset = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartContent();
	TokenPos token( m_strDoc, m_nFlags );
	NodePos node;
	token.nNext = nPrevOffset;
	int nPrevType = 0;
	while ( token.nNext < nNodeOffset )
	{ 
		nPrevOffset = token.nNext;
		nPrevType = x_ParseNode( token, node );
	 }
	int nPrevLength = nNodeOffset - nPrevOffset;
	if ( ! nPrevLength )
	{ 

		nPrevOffset = 0;
		if ( iPosPrev )
			nPrevType = MNT_ELEMENT;
	 }


 	x_DocChange( nNodeOffset, nNodeLength, string() );
	x_AdjustForNode( iPosParent, iPosPrev, - nNodeLength );


	if ( nNodeType == MNT_LONE_END_TAG )
	{ 

		token.nNext = m_aPos[iPosParent].StartContent();
		int nEndOfContent = token.nNext + m_aPos[iPosParent].ContentLen();
		int iPosChild = m_aPos[iPosParent].iElemChild;
		while ( token.nNext < nEndOfContent )
		{ 
			if ( x_ParseNode(token,node) <= 0 )
				break;
			if ( node.nNodeType == MNT_ELEMENT )
			{ 
				token.nNext = m_aPos[iPosChild].StartAfter();
				iPosChild = m_aPos[iPosChild].iElemNext;
			 }
		 }
		if ( token.nNext == nEndOfContent )
			m_aPos[iPosParent].nFlags &= ~MNF_ILLDATA;
	 }

	nNodeType = nPrevType;
	nNodeOffset = nPrevOffset;
	nNodeLength = nPrevLength;
	iPos = iPosPrev;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
x_RemoveNode::iPosPrev::iPos::nNodeType::MNT_ELEMENT::nNodeOffset::m_aPos::iPos::nStart::nNodeLength::m_aPos::iPos::nLength::iPosPrev::x_UnlinkElem::iPos::x_CheckSavedPos::nPrevOffset::iPosPrev::nPrevOffset::m_aPos::iPosPrev::StartAfter::iPosParent::nPrevOffset::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartContent::TokenPos::token::m_strDoc::m_nFlags::NodePos::node::token::nNext::nPrevOffset::nPrevType::token::nNext::nNodeOffset::nPrevOffset::token::nNext::nPrevType::x_ParseNode::token::node::nPrevLength::nNodeOffset::nPrevOffset::nPrevLength::nPrevOffset::iPosPrev::nPrevType::MNT_ELEMENT::x_DocChange::nNodeOffset::nNodeLength::string::x_AdjustForNode::iPosParent::iPosPrev::nNodeLength::nNodeType::MNT_LONE_END_TAG::token::nNext::m_aPos::iPosParent::StartContent::nEndOfContent::token::nNext::m_aPos::iPosParent::ContentLen::iPosChild::m_aPos::iPosParent::iElemChild::token::nNext::nEndOfContent::x_ParseNode::token::node::node::nNodeType::MNT_ELEMENT::token::nNext::m_aPos::iPosChild::StartAfter::iPosChild::m_aPos::iPosChild::iElemNext::token::nNext::nEndOfContent::m_aPos::iPosParent::nFlags::MNF_ILLDATA::nNodeType::nPrevType::nNodeOffset::nPrevOffset::nNodeLength::nPrevLength::iPos::iPosPrev

  mFileMenu->addSeparator();
  for ( int i = 0; i < MaxRecentFiles; ++i )
    mFileMenu->addAction(mRecentActs[i]);
  mFileMenu->addSeparator();
  mFileMenu->addAction(mExitAct);
  connect(mFileMenu, SIGNAL(aboutToShow()), this, SLOT(slotUpdateFileMenu()));

  mEditMenu = menuBar()->addMenu(tr("&Edit"));
  mEditMenu->addAction(mUndoAct);
  mEditMenu->addAction(mRedoAct);
  mEditMenu->addSeparator();
  mEditMenu->addAction(mCutAct);
  mEditMenu->addAction(mCopyAct);
  mEditMenu->addAction(mPasteAct);
  mEditMenu->addAction(mDeleteAct);
  mEditMenu->addSeparator();
  mEditMenu->addAction(mFindAct);
  connect(mEditMenu, SIGNAL(aboutToShow()), this, SLOT(slotUpdateEditMenu()));

  mOptionMenu = menuBar()->addMenu(tr("&Option"));
  mOptionMenu->addAction(mChangeHierarchyAct);
  mOptionMenu->addAction(mChooseTemplateDirAct);

  connect(mOptionMenu, SIGNAL(aboutToShow()), this, SLOT(slotUpdateOptionMenu()));


  mWindowMenu = menuBar()->addMenu(tr("&Window"));
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mHierarchicalAct);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mGraphicalAct);
  mWindowMenu->addSeparator();
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mCloseAct);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mCloseAllAct);
  mWindowMenu->addSeparator();
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mCascadeAct);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mTileHorzAct);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mTileVertAct);
  connect(mWindowMenu, SIGNAL(aboutToShow()), this, SLOT(slotUpdateWindowsMenu()));

  mHelpMenu = menuBar()->addMenu(tr("&Help"));
  mHelpMenu->addAction(mContentAct);
  mHelpMenu->addAction(mAboutAct);





  mFileToolBar = addToolBar(tr("File"));
  mFileToolBar->addAction(mNewAct);
  mFileToolBar->addAction(mOpenAct);
  mFileToolBar->addAction(mSaveAct);
  mFileToolBar->addAction(mPrintAct);
  mFileToolBar->addAction(mGenAct);

  mEditToolBar = addToolBar(tr("Edit"));
  mEditToolBar->addAction(mUndoAct);
  mEditToolBar->addAction(mRedoAct);
  mEditToolBar->addAction(mCutAct);
  mEditToolBar->addAction(mCopyAct);
  mEditToolBar->addAction(mPasteAct);
  mEditToolBar->addAction(mMsgModeAct);



  mHelpToolBar = addToolBar(tr("Help"));
  mHelpToolBar->addAction(QWhatsThis::createAction(this));





  mModLabel = new QLabel(tr(" MOD "));
  mModLabel->setAlignment(Qt::AlignHCenter);
  mModLabel->setMinimumSize(mModLabel->sizeHint());
  mModLabel->clear();
  mModLabel->setFrameStyle(QFrame::Panel + QFrame::Sunken);

  mGraphContext = new QLabel(tr("Context: None"));
  mGraphContext->setAlignment(Qt::AlignHCenter);
  mGraphContext->setMinimumSize(mGraphContext->sizeHint());
  mGraphContext->setFrameStyle(QFrame::Panel + QFrame::Sunken);

  statusBar()->addWidget(new QLabel(), 1);
  statusBar()->addPermanentWidget(mGraphContext);
  statusBar()->addPermanentWidget(mModLabel);

  readSetting();
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/mainwindow.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:2 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:10 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:482 L_END:484 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:getDocument NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:1 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
getDocumentWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QString &fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	

	if(fn.endsWith(".acs"))
	{ 

		mGenAct->setEnabled(true);
	 }
	else
		mGenAct->setEnabled(false);

  QWidgetList list = mWorkspace->windowList();
  for ( QWidgetList::iterator it = list.begin(); it != list.end(); ++it )

	  if ( (*it)->caption() == fn )
      return *it;


	



  QString extension = QFileInfo(fn).extension(false);


  if ( extension == "acs" )
  { 
	slotClosePro();
	mGenAct->setEnabled(true);
    CConfig *doc = new CConfig(mWorkspace, this);
	CGraphicDesign *mGraphicDesign = new CGraphicDesign(mWorkspace, this, mGraphicProperties, doc);
	setContext("Context: System");
	mGraphicDesign->updateComponents();

    CProject *pro = 0;
	if (activeProject())
		activeProject()->setCConfig(doc, mGraphicDesign);
	else
	{ 
		pro = new CProject(mDock, this, doc, mGraphicDesign);
		pro->setFilename(fn);
	 }

    if ( doc && doc->readFile(fn) )
    { 
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
	  mWorkspace->addWindow(mGraphicDesign);

	  doc->show();
	  mGraphicDesign->show();	  
	  mGraphicDesign->setCaption("Graphic Design - " + fn);
	  mGraphicDesign->readProperty(doc->topLevelItem(0));
      mGraphicDesign->removeProperties();
	  mGraphicDesign->resize(mGraphicDesign->width(), mGraphicDesign->height() + 5);

      if (pro)
	  { 
		QWidget *widget =  mDock->widget();
		mDock->setWidget(pro);
		delete widget;
	   }

      if (mGraphicalAct->isEnabled() == false)
	  { 
		  doc->showMinimized();
		  return mGraphicDesign;
	   }
	  else
		  return doc;
     }
    else
    { 
      delete doc;
      delete pro;
	  delete mGraphicDesign;
     }
   }


  else if ( extension == "par" )
  { 
	  mGenAct->setEnabled(false);
    CParam *doc = new CParam(mWorkspace, this);
    if ( doc && doc->readFile(fn) )
    { 
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      return doc;
     }
    else
      delete doc;
   }


  else if ( extension == "opt" )
  { 
	  mGenAct->setEnabled(false);
    COption *doc = new COption(mWorkspace, this);
    if ( doc && doc->readFile(fn) )
    { 
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      return doc;
     }
    else
      delete doc;
   }


  else if ( extension == "wgd" )
  { 
	  mGenAct->setEnabled(false);
    CWidgetView *doc = new CWidgetView(mWorkspace, this);
    if ( doc && doc->readFile(fn) )
    { 
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      return doc;
     }
    else
      delete doc;
   }


  else if ( extension == "tcd" )
  { 
	  mGenAct->setEnabled(false);
    CTextControl *doc = new CTextControl(mWorkspace, this);
    if ( doc && doc->readFile(fn) )
    { 
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      return doc;
     }
    else
      delete doc;
   }


  else
  { 
	  mGenAct->setEnabled(false);
    CText *doc = new CText(mWorkspace, this);
    if ( doc && doc->readFile(fn) )
    { 
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      return doc;
     }
    else
      delete doc;
   }


  return 0;
 }
__END_BODY__

slotNew
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CNewFileDialog dialog(this);
  QString path = QDir::currentDirPath();
  if (QDir::currentDirPath().contains("Confi efault", Qt::CaseInsensitive))
  { 
	  QDir dir(QDir::currentDirPath());
	  dir.cdUp();	dir.cdUp();		dir.cdUp();
	  path = dir.absolutePath();
   }
  dialog.dirEdit->setText(path);
  mGenAct->setEnabled(false);
  QDir systDir;
  QString relativeFN;




  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted)
  { 
    QWidget *doc = 0;
	QString filename = dialog.filename();


    if ( dialog.list->currentItem()->text() == "Project File" )
    { 

		
		slotClosePro();

		QString systName = dialog.systemname();

		systDir = QFileInfo(filename).absoluteDir();
		relativeFN = systDir.relativeFilePath(filename);
		systDir.mkdir(systName);

		systDir.cd(systName);

		systDir.mkdir("Config");
		systDir.mkdir("Doc");
		systDir.mkdir("Src");
		systDir.mkdir("Res");

		systDir.cd("Config");
		systDir.mkdir("Default");
		systDir.cd("Default");

		filename = systDir.absolutePath()+"/"+relativeFN;

	  mGenAct->setEnabled(true);
      CConfig *cdoc = new CConfig(mWorkspace, this, systName);
	  statusBar()->message(QString("Config document created"));
	  cdoc->setCaption(filename);

	  CGraphicDesign *mGraphicDesign = new CGraphicDesign(mWorkspace, this, mGraphicProperties, cdoc);
	  statusBar()->message(QString("Graphical document created"));

	  CProject *pro = new CProject(mDock, this, cdoc, mGraphicDesign);
      pro->setFilename(filename);
      pro->show();

	  mWorkspace->addWindow(cdoc);
	  mWorkspace->addWindow(mGraphicDesign);


	  cdoc->show();
	  mGraphicDesign->show();
	  mGraphicDesign->setCaption("Graphic Design - " + filename);
	  setContext("Context: System");
	  mGraphicDesign->updateComponents();
	  if (mGraphicalAct->isEnabled() == false)
	  { 
		  cdoc->showMinimized();
		  doc = mGraphicDesign;
	   }
	  else
		  doc = cdoc;

      QWidget *widget =  mDock->widget();
      mDock->setWidget(pro);
      delete widget;
     }


    else if ( dialog.list->currentItem()->text() == "Parameter File" )
    { 
      doc = new CParam(mWorkspace, this);
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      statusBar()->message(QString("Parameter table document created"));
	  doc->setCaption(filename);
     }


    else if ( dialog.list->currentItem()->text() == "Option File" )
    { 
      doc = new COption(mWorkspace, this);
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      statusBar()->message(QString("Option document created"));
	  doc->setCaption(filename);
     }


    else if ( dialog.list->currentItem()->text() == "Widget File" )
    { 
      doc = new CWidgetView(mWorkspace, this);
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      statusBar()->message(QString("Widget document created"));
	  doc->setCaption(filename);
     }


    else if ( dialog.list->currentItem()->text() == "Text Control File" )
    { 
      doc = new CTextControl(mWorkspace, this);
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      statusBar()->message(QString("Text Control document created"));
	  doc->setCaption(filename);
     }


    else
    { 
      doc = new CText(mWorkspace, this);
      mWorkspace->addWindow(doc);
      statusBar()->message(QString("Text document created"));
	  doc->setCaption(filename);
     }

    if ( activeDocument() )
      doc->showMaximized();
    else
      doc->show();
    QDir::setCurrent(QFileInfo(filename).absoluteDir().path());
    slotSave();

    return true;
   }

  return false;
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotClosePro
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CProject *pro = activeProject();

  if ( pro )
  { 
	  QWidgetList windows = mWorkspace->windowList(CWorkspace::CreationOrder);
		for(int i=0; i<windows.size(); i++)
		{ 
			if (windows.at(i)->windowTitle() == ("Graphic Design - " + pro->filename()))
				continue;
			else
				windows.at(i)->close();
		 }
		if (mWorkspace->windowList(CWorkspace::CreationOrder).size() == 0)
		{ 
			pro->close();
			CGraphicProperties::getInstance()->updateDisplay(0);
			setContext("Context: None");
			mComponents->setComponentsEnabled("Context: None", true, true, false);
			

			mDock->setWidget(new QWidget);
		 }
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotDelete
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( mWorkspace->activeWindow() && mWorkspace->activeWindow()->hasFocus() )
  { 
    IDocument *doc = activeDocument();
 
    if ( doc )
	{ 
		if (doc->type() == "Config")
		{ 
			if (getGraphicDesign())
				getGraphicDesign()->editDelete();
		 }
		else
			doc->editDelete();
	 }
   }
  else if ( activeProject() && activeProject()->hasFocus() )
    activeProject()->editDelete();
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotHierarchicalInterface
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	mDockToolbar->hide();
	mDockProperties->hide();
	mGraphicalAct->setEnabled(true);
	mHierarchicalAct->setEnabled(false);

	QWidgetList windows = mWorkspace->windowList(CWorkspace::CreationOrder);
	for(int i=0; i<windows.size(); i++)
		if (windows.at(i)->windowTitle() == activeProject()->filename())
			mWorkspace->setActiveWindow(windows.at(i));
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotGraphicalInterface
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	mDockToolbar->show();
	mDockProperties->show();
	mDockToolbar->setWidget(mComponents);
	mGraphicalAct->setEnabled(false);
	mHierarchicalAct->setEnabled(true);

	QWidgetList windows = mWorkspace->windowList(CWorkspace::CreationOrder);
	bool maxwin;
	if (windows.size() > 0)
		maxwin = mWorkspace->activeWindow()->isMaximized();
	for(int i=0; i<windows.size(); i++)
	{ 
		if (windows.at(i)->windowTitle() == ("Graphic Design - " + activeProject()->filename()))
		{ 
			mWorkspace->setActiveWindow(windows.at(i));
			if (maxwin)
				windows.at(i)->showMaximized();
		 }
		else
			if (maxwin)
				windows.at(i)->showMinimized();
	 }

	if (windows.size() == 0)
		mComponents->setComponentsEnabled("Context: None", true, true, false);
 }
__END_BODY__

()

{ 
	slotGraphicalInterface();
	QWidgetList windows = mWorkspace->windowList(CWorkspace::CreationOrder);
	for(int i=0; i<windows.size(); i++)
	{ 
		if (windows.at(i)->windowTitle() == ("Graphic Design - " + activeProject()->filename()))
			windows.at(i)->resize(windows.at(i)->minimumSize());
		if (windows.at(i)->isMinimized())
			windows.at(i)->showNormal();
	 }
	mWorkspace->cascade();
 }

()

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	if (!getGraphicDesign())
		return;

	if (getGraphicDesign()->getDrawMode() == Normal)
	{ 
		getGraphicDesign()->setDrawMode(Message);
		getGraphicDesign()->update();
		mMsgModeAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage ink_delete_24.png"));
		mMsgModeAct->setStatusTip(tr("Exit the message mode"));
	 }
	else
	{ 
		getGraphicDesign()->setDrawMode(Normal);
		getGraphicDesign()->update();
		mMsgModeAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage ink_add_24.png"));
		mMsgModeAct->setStatusTip(tr("Enter the message mode"));
	 }
	getGraphicDesign()->updateComponents();
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotUpdateWindowsMenu
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  IDocument *doc = activeDocument();


  mWindowMenu->clear();
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mHierarchicalAct);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mGraphicalAct);
  mWindowMenu->addSeparator();
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mCloseAct);
  mCloseAct->setEnabled(doc);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mCloseAllAct);
  mCloseAllAct->setEnabled(doc);
  mWindowMenu->addSeparator();
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mCascadeAct);
  mCascadeAct->setEnabled(doc);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mTileHorzAct);
  mTileHorzAct->setEnabled(doc);
  mWindowMenu->addAction(mTileVertAct);
  mTileVertAct->setEnabled(doc);

  if (mHierarchicalAct->isEnabled() && mGraphicalAct->isEnabled())
	  mHierarchicalAct->setEnabled(false);
  

  if ( doc )
  { 
    mWindowMenu->addSeparator();

    QWidgetList windows = mWorkspace->windowList(CWorkspace::CreationOrder);

    int nb = 0;
    for ( QWidgetList::iterator it = windows.begin(); it != windows.end(); ++it )
    { 
      if ( !(*it)->isHidden() )
      { 
        QString text = tr("&%1 %2").arg(nb + 1).arg((*it)->caption());
        int id = mWindowMenu->insertItem(text, this, SLOT(slotActivateWindow(int)));
        bool isActive = mWorkspace->activeWindow() == *it;
        mWindowMenu->setItemChecked(id, isActive);
        mWindowMenu->setItemParameter(id, (int)*it);
        ++nb;
       }
     }
   }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotUpdateModIndicator
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  IDocument *doc = activeDocument();

  if ( doc && doc->isModified() )
    mModLabel->setText(tr("MOD"));
  else
    mModLabel->clear();

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readSetting
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QSettings settings("cae.com", "ACS Editor");

  if ( settings.readBoolEntry("geometr aximized", false) )
    showMaximized();
  else
  { 
    int x = settings.readNumEntry(" eometr ", 320);
    int y = settings.readNumEntry(" eometr ", 256);
    move(x, y);

    int w = settings.readNumEntry(" eometr idth", 640);
    int h = settings.readNumEntry(" eometr eight", 512);
    resize(w, h);
   }

  QStringList files = settings.value(" ecents").toStringList();
  for ( int i = 0; i < MaxRecentFiles; ++i )
    if ( i < files.size() )
    { 
      QString text = tr("&%1 %2").arg(i + 1).arg(QFileInfo(files[i]).fileName());
      mRecentActs[i]->setText(text);
      mRecentActs[i]->setData(files[i]);
      mRecentActs[i]->setToolTip(files[i]);
      mRecentActs[i]->setVisible(true);
     }
    else
      mRecentActs[i]->setVisible(false);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
openFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QString &fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QWidget *doc = getDocumentWidget(fn);
  if ( doc )
  { 
    if ( activeDocument() )
      doc->showMaximized();
    else
      doc->show();

    doc->setFocus();
    statusBar()->message("Document loaded", 2000);
    QDir::setCurrent(QFileInfo(fn).absoluteDir().path());
    return true;
   }

  statusBar()->message(tr("Loading canceled"), 2000);
  return false;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
addRecentFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QString &fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QSettings settings("cae.com", "ACS Editor");
  QStringList files = settings.value(" ecents").toStringList();
  files.removeAll(fn);
  files.prepend(fn);
  while ( files.size() > MaxRecentFiles )
    files.removeLast();

  settings.setValue(" ecents", files);

  for ( int i = 0; i < MaxRecentFiles; ++i )
    if ( i < files.size() )
    { 
      QString text = tr("&%1 %2").arg(i + 1).arg(QFileInfo(files[i]).fileName());
      mRecentActs[i]->setText(text);
      mRecentActs[i]->setData(files[i]);
      mRecentActs[i]->setToolTip(files[i]);
      mRecentActs[i]->setVisible(true);
     }
    else
      mRecentActs[i]->setVisible(false);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotChooseTemplateDir
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QDir applicationDir;
	QFile *templateDirSetup;
	int indexEnd;
	QByteArray temp;
  QString dirname = QFileDialog::getExistingDirectory(
                    this,
                    "Choose a directory",
                    ".",
                    QFileDialog::ShowDirsOnly | QFileDialog::DontResolveSymlinks);  

    if ( !dirname.isEmpty() )
	{ 
			
			applicationDir = QApplication::applicationDirPath();
		    templateDirSetup = new QFile(applicationDir.absFilePath("TemplateDirSetup.txt"));
			templateDirSetup->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite|QIODevice::Text );
			temp = templateDirSetup->readAll();
			indexEnd = temp.indexOf("<!--",0);

			temp.remove(0, indexEnd);
			temp.insert(0, dirname+'\n');

			templateDirSetup->remove();
			templateDirSetup->close();

			templateDirSetup = new QFile(applicationDir.absFilePath("TemplateDirSetup.txt"));
			templateDirSetup->open(QIODevice::WriteOnly|QIODevice::Text );

			templateDirSetup->write(temp);
			templateDirSetup->close();

	
	 }

	
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(0);
  QString str = mModel->value("FormatString").toString() + mModel->value("LegendString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width, height), str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  if ( mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()) == QColor(Qt::black) )
    painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  else
    painter.setPen(mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()));


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width, height), str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width - 400, height), str, align);


  painter.translate(width - 200, height / 2);  
  if ( mModel->value("OpeningMode").toString() == "A661_OPEN_UP" )
    painter.rotate(180);

  Q3PointArray pts;
  pts.setPoints( 3, -100, 100, 100, 100, 0, -100);
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::white));
  painter.drawPolygon(pts);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush(QColor(Qt::darkGray), Qt::CrossPattern));
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i));
    if ( widget->isVisible() )
      widget->draw(painter);
   }

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush(QColor(Qt::darkGray), Qt::CrossPattern));
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i));
    if ( widget->isVisible() )
      widget->draw(painter);
   }

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
