#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:10 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:10 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/library/wselectionlistbutton.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:10 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:17 LOCALS:17 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:72 L_END:88 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:init NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:10 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width - 400, height), str, align);
  

  painter.translate(width - 200, height / 2);
  if ( mModel->value("OpeningMode").toString() == "A661_OPEN_UP" )
    painter.rotate(180);
  else if ( mModel->value("OpeningMode").toString() == "A661_OPEN_CENTERED" )
    painter.rotate(90);
  Q3PointArray pts;
  pts.setPoints(3, -100, 100, 100, 100, 0, -100);
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::white));
  painter.drawPolygon(pts);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));

  QColor color(Qt::darkGray);
  color.setAlpha(128);
  painter.setBrush(color);
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width, height), str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("EntryList").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width-height, height), str, align);


  painter.translate(width-height / 2, height / 2);
  int g = height / 4;
  painter.drawLine(-g, g, g, g);
  painter.drawLine(g, g, 0, -g);
  painter.drawLine(0, -g, -g, g);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::black));
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::black));
  painter.drawRect(width - 400, 0, 400, height);
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::darkGray));
  painter.drawRect(width - 400, 800, 400, 800);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width - 400, height), str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
setVisible
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(bool vis)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CWidget::setVisible(vis);

  CWidget *active = 0;
  CWidget *select = 0;
  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i));

    if ( !active && widget->model("WidgetIdent") == mActiveTab )
      active = widget;
    else if ( !select && widget->isVisible() )
      select = widget;

    widget->setVisible(false);
   }

  if ( select )
    active = select;
  mActiveTab = active->model("WidgetIdent");
  active->setVisible(true);
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:1 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/library/wtabbedpanelgroup.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:2 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:4 LOCALS:9 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:138 L_END:141 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:resetVisibility NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  if ( mModel->value("TabPosition").toString() == "A661_TOP" )
  { 
    int tabWidth = width / childCount();

    painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
    painter.setBrush(QBrush());
    painter.drawLine(width, height - 750, width, 0);
    painter.drawLine(width, 0, 0, 0);
    painter.drawLine(0, 0, 0, height - 750);

    painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
    int xx = 0;
    for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
    { 
      CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i));

      if ( widget->model("WidgetIdent") == mActiveTab )
        painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
      else
        painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
      painter.setBrush(QBrush());

      const CFont &font = mStyle->font(0);
      QString str = widget->model("LabelString");
      font.draw(painter, QRect(xx, height - 750, tabWidth, 750), str, "A661_CENTER");

      painter.drawLine(xx, height - 750, xx + 100, height);
      painter.drawLine(xx + 100, height, xx + tabWidth - 200, height);
      painter.drawLine(xx + tabWidth - 200, height, xx + tabWidth, height - 750);

      if ( widget->model("WidgetIdent") != mActiveTab )
        painter.drawLine(xx + tabWidth, height - 750, xx, height - 750);

      xx += tabWidth;
     }
   }
  else
  { 
    painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
    painter.setBrush(QBrush());
    painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);
   }


  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i));
    if ( widget->isVisible() )
      widget->draw(painter);
   }

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

  painter.setPen(QPen(QColor(Qt::gray), 1, Qt::SolidLine));

  QColor color(Qt::darkGray);
  color.setAlpha(128);
  painter.setBrush(color);
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width, height), str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("EntryList").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width - height, height), str, align);


  painter.translate(width - height / 2, height / 2);  
  int g = height / 4;
  painter.drawLine(-g, g, g, g);
  painter.drawLine(g, g, 0, -g);
  painter.drawLine(0, -g, -g, g);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);


  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i));
    if ( widget->isVisible() )
      widget->draw(painter);
   }

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:9 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:9 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/library/wgpline.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:9 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:14 LOCALS:16 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:72 L_END:85 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:init NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:9 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x1 = mModel->value("PosXStart").toInt();
  int y1 = mModel->value("PosYStart").toInt();
  int x2 = mModel->value("PosXEnd").toInt();
  int y2 = mModel->value("PosYEnd").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  Q3PointArray pts;
  pts.setPoints(2, x1, y1, x2, y2);
  mArea = matrix.map(pts);


  if ( mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()) == QColor(Qt::black) )
    painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  else
    painter.setPen(mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()));


  painter.drawLine(x1, y1, x2, y2);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  if ( mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()) == QColor(Qt::black) )
    painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  else
    painter.setPen(mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()));


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width, height), str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);


  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i));
    if ( widget->isVisible() )
      widget->draw(painter);
   }

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  if ( mModel->value("PicturePosition").toString() == "A661_LEFT" )
  { 
    painter.drawRect(height / 4, height / 4, height / 2, height / 2);
    painter.translate(height, 0);
   }
  else
    painter.drawRect(width - height + height / 4, height / 4, height / 2, height / 2);


  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();
  font.draw(painter, QRect(0, 0, width, height), str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);

  const CFont &font = mStyle->font(mModel->value("Font").toInt());
  QString str = mModel->value("LabelString").toString();
  QString align = mModel->value("Alignment").toString();

  QRect area = font.getArea(str);
  mArea = painter.matrix().mapRect(area);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QBrush());
  painter.drawRect(area);


  if ( mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()) == QColor(Qt::black) )
    painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::white));
  else
    painter.setPen(mStyle->color(mModel->value("ColorIndex").toInt()));


  font.draw(painter, area, str, align);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  int x = mModel->value("PosX").toInt();
  int y = mModel->value("PosY").toInt();
  int width = mModel->value("SizeX").toInt();
  int height = mModel->value("SizeY").toInt();

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(x, y);
  mArea = matrix.mapRect(QRect(x, y, width, height));


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::black));
  painter.drawRect(0, 0, width, height);


  painter.setPen(QColor(Qt::gray));
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::black));
  painter.drawRect(width - 400, 0, 400, height);
  painter.setBrush(QColor(Qt::darkGray));
  painter.drawRect(width - 400, 800, 400, 800);

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }

QTreeWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setObjectName("theWidgetList");

  mParent = parent;
  mView = view;
  mFind = 0;





  setColumnCount(1);
  QStringList headers;
  headers << tr("Widget");
  setHeaderLabels(headers);
  header()->setResizeMode(0, QHeaderView::Stretch);

  setSortingEnabled(false);
  setRootIsDecorated(true);
  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
  setHorizontalScrollBarPolicy(Qt::ScrollBarAlwaysOff);

  mIndex = mParent->addItem(this, QString("Layer X"));





  QMap<QString, QVariant> extra;
  extra["readonly"] = true;

  mModel = new CProperties(this);
  mModel->setProperty("LayerName", "");
  mModel->setProperty("LayerIdent", "", extra);
  mModel->setProperty("ContextNumber", "", extra);
  mModel->setProperty("Height", "");
  mModel->setProperty("Width", "");
  mModel->setProperty("Refresh", "");





  mEditLayerAct = new QAction(tr("Edit Layer"), this);
  mEditLayerAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+L"));
  mEditLayerAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits the layer data"));
  connect(mEditLayerAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditLayer()));

  mEditWidgetAct = new QAction(tr("Edit Widget"), this);
  mEditWidgetAct->setShortcut(tr("F2"));
  mEditWidgetAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits the run-time data and events"));
  connect(mEditWidgetAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditWidget()));

  mShowDefinitionAct = new QAction(tr("Definition Data"), this);
  mShowDefinitionAct->setShortcut(tr("F1"));
  mShowDefinitionAct->setStatusTip(tr("Shows the creation structure"));
  connect(mShowDefinitionAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotShowDefinition()));

  mResetVisAct = new QAction(tr("&Reset Visibility"), this);
  mResetVisAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+R"));
  mResetVisAct->setStatusTip(tr("Reserts widget visibility"));
  connect(mResetVisAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotResetVisib()));

  mFindAct = new QAction(tr("&Find Widget"), this);
  mFindAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+F"));
  mFindAct->setStatusTip(tr("Finds widget"));
  connect(mFindAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotFind()));





  mTip = 0;





  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotSelection(QTreeWidgetItem *)));
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QString name = xml.getAttrib("name").c_str();





  mModel->setValue("LayerName", name);

  xml.findChildElem("model");
  xml.intoElem();

  while ( xml.findChildElem("prop") )
  { 
    QString name = xml.getChildAttrib("name").c_str();
    QString value = xml.getChildAttrib("value").c_str();
    mModel->setValue(name, value);
   }

  xml.outOfElem();





  CWidget *after = 0;

  while ( xml.findChildElem("a661_widget") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();

    QString type = xml.getAttrib("type").c_str();

    CWidget *widget = CWidgetFactory::create(type, this, after);
    widget->setText(0, type);
    widget->load(xml);
    after = widget;

    xml.outOfElem();
   }


  mParent->setItemLabel(mIndex, QString("Layer %1 %2").arg(layerId()).arg(name));
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
save
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.addElem("a661_layer");
  xml.addAttrib("name", layerName().toAscii().data());

  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("model");





  QStringList params = mModel->names();
  for ( int i = 1; i < params.count(); ++i )
  { 
    xml.addChildElem("prop");
    xml.addChildAttrib("name", params[i].toAscii().data());
    xml.addChildAttrib("value", mModel->value(params[i]).toString().toAscii().data());
   }





  for ( int i = 0; i < topLevelItemCount(); ++i )
    static_cast<CWidget *>(topLevelItem(i))->save(xml);

  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__

  mView->repaint();

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenu
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QTreeWidgetItem *item, QPoint pos)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(item);

  if ( widget )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mEditLayerAct);
    menu.addAction(mResetVisAct);
    menu.addSeparator();
    menu.addAction(mShowDefinitionAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditWidgetAct);
    menu.addSeparator();

    QAction vis("Widget Visibility", this);
    vis.setCheckable(true);
    vis.setChecked(widget->isVisible());
    menu.addAction(&vis);

    if ( menu.exec(pos) == &vis )
    { 
      widget->setVisible(vis.isOn());
      mView->repaint();
     }
   }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
QDialog
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent, name, modal, fl)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( !name )
    setName("CFindWidgetDialog");

  setCaption(tr("Find Widget"));

  QGridLayout *layout = new QGridLayout(this, 1, 1, 11, 6, "layout");





  mLabel = new QLabel(this, "mLabel");
  mLabel->setText(tr("Find:"));
  layout->addWidget(mLabel, 0, 0);

  mEdit = new QLineEdit(this, "mEdit");


  layout->addWidget(mEdit, 0, 1);





  mGroup = new Q3ButtonGroup(this, "mGroup");
  mGroup->setTitle(tr("Key"));
  mGroup->setExclusive(true);
  mGroup->setColumnLayout(0, Qt::Vertical);
  mGroup->layout()->setSpacing(6);
  mGroup->layout()->setMargin(11);

  QGridLayout *groupLayout = new QGridLayout(mGroup->layout());
  groupLayout->setAlignment(Qt::AlignTop);

  mId = new QRadioButton(mGroup, "mId");
  mId->setText(tr("Widget Ident"));
  mId->setChecked(true);
  QToolTip::add(mId, "Find widget ident");
  groupLayout->addWidget(mId, 0, 0);

  mName = new QRadioButton(mGroup, "mName");
  mName->setText(tr("Widget Name"));
  QToolTip::add(mName, "Find widget name");
  groupLayout->addWidget(mName, 1, 0);

  mType = new QRadioButton(mGroup, "mType");
  mType->setText(tr("Widget Type"));
  QToolTip::add(mType, "Find widget type");
  groupLayout->addWidget(mType, 2, 0);

  layout->addMultiCellWidget(mGroup, 1, 2, 0, 1);

  QSpacerItem *spacer1 = new QSpacerItem(20, 110, QSizePolicy::Minimum, QSizePolicy::Expanding);
  layout->addMultiCell(spacer1, 2, 3, 2, 2);





  mFind = new QPushButton(this, "mFind");
  mFind->setText(tr("&Find"));
  mFind->setAccel(QKeySequence(tr("Alt+F, Return")));
  mFind->setEnabled(false);
  mFind->setDefault(true);
  layout->addWidget(mFind, 0, 2);

  mClose = new QPushButton(this, "mClose");
  mClose->setText(tr("Close"));
  mClose->setAccel(QKeySequence(tr("Esc")));
  layout->addWidget(mClose, 1, 2);

  QSpacerItem *spacer2 = new QSpacerItem(20, 20, QSizePolicy::Minimum, QSizePolicy::Expanding);
  layout->addItem(spacer2, 3, 1);


  resize(QSize(384, 169).expandedTo(minimumSizeHint()));






  connect(mEdit, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(enableFindButton(const QString &)));
  connect(mFind, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(find()));
  connect(mClose, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(reject()));
 }
__END_BODY__

isVisible

__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  bool vis = mVisible;

  CWidget *parent = (CWidget *)this->parent();
  while ( parent )
  { 
    vis = vis && parent->isVisible();

    parent = (CWidget *)parent->parent();
   }

  return vis;
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:0 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:0 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/widget.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:4 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:164 L_END:166 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:draw NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:0 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QMap<QString, QVariant> extra;
  extra["readonly"] = true;

  QString name = xml.getAttrib("name").c_str();
  QString cname = xml.getAttrib("cname").c_str();





  mModel->setProperty("WidgetType", text(0), extra);
  mModel->setProperty("WidgetName", name, extra);

  xml.findChildElem("model");
  xml.intoElem();

  while ( xml.findChildElem() )
  { 
    if ( xml.getChildTagName() == "prop" )
    { 
      QString name = xml.getChildAttrib("name").c_str();
      QString value = xml.getChildAttrib("value").c_str();
      mModel->setProperty(name, value, extra);
     }
    else if ( xml.getChildTagName() == "arrayprop" )
    { 
      QString name = xml.getChildAttrib("name").c_str();

      xml.intoElem();
      QStringList array;
      while ( xml.findChildElem("entry") )
        array += xml.getChildAttrib("value").c_str();
      xml.outOfElem();

      mModel->setProperty(name, array, extra);
     } 
   }

  xml.outOfElem();





  if ( !cname.isEmpty() )
    mRuntime->setValue("ClassName", cname);
  mRuntime->setValue("WidgetType", text(0));
  mRuntime->setValue("WidgetName", name);
  mRuntime->setValue("WidgetIdent", mModel->value("WidgetIdent").toString());

  if ( xml.findChildElem("runtime") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();

    while ( xml.findChildElem("prop") )
    { 
      QString name = xml.getChildAttrib("name").c_str();
      QString value = xml.getChildAttrib("value").c_str();
      mRuntime->setValue(name, value);
     }

    xml.outOfElem();
   }





  CWidget *after = 0;

  while ( xml.findChildElem("a661_widget") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();

    QString type = xml.getAttrib("type").c_str();

    CWidget *widget = CWidgetFactory::create(type, this, after);
    widget->setText(0, type);
    widget->load(xml);
    after = widget;

    xml.outOfElem();
   }


  mVisible = mModel->value("Visible").toString() == "A661_TRUE";
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
save
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.addElem("a661_widget");
  xml.addAttrib("name", mRuntime->value("WidgetName").toString().toAscii().data());
  xml.addAttrib("type", mRuntime->value("WidgetType").toString().toAscii().data());
  xml.addAttrib("cname", mRuntime->value("ClassName").toString().toAscii().data());





  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("model");

  QStringList params = mModel->names();
  for ( int i = 2; i < params.count(); ++i )
  { 
    QVariant value = mModel->property(params[i]);
    if ( value.type() == QVariant::String )
    { 
      xml.addChildElem("prop");
      xml.addChildAttrib("name", params[i].toAscii().data());
      xml.addChildAttrib("value", value.toString().toAscii().data());
     }
    else if ( value.type() == QVariant::StringList )
    { 
      QStringList array = value.toStringList();

      xml.addChildElem("arrayprop");
      xml.addChildAttrib("name", params[i].toAscii().data());

      xml.intoElem();
      for ( int i = 0; i < array.count(); ++i )
      { 
        xml.addChildElem("entry");
        xml.addChildAttrib("value", array[i].toAscii().data());
       }
      xml.outOfElem();      
     }
    else
      xml.addChildAttrib("value", "");
   }





  xml.addElem("runtime");

  params = mRuntime->names();
  for ( i = 4; i < params.count(); ++i )
  { 
    xml.addChildElem("prop");
    xml.addChildAttrib("name", params[i].toAscii().data());
    xml.addChildAttrib("value", mRuntime->value(params[i]).toString().toAscii().data());
   }





  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
    static_cast<CWidget *>(child(i))->save(xml);

  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
getArea
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QString &str)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QStringList text = QStringList::split(QChar(0x0D), QString(str).remove(QChar(0x0A)));

  int height = text.count() * mInterline;


  for ( int max = 0, i = 0; i < text.count(); ++i )
    max = QMAX(max, text[i].length());
  int width = max * mAdvance;

  return QRect(0, 0, width, height);
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:6 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:10 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:4 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:11 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/style/font.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:3 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:12 LOCALS:23 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:66 L_END:77 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:getArea NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:7 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
draw
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter, QRect area, const QString &str, const QString &align)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QStringList text = QStringList::split(QChar(0x0D), QString(str).remove(QChar(0x0A)));

  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.translate(area.x(), area.y());


  int height = text.count() * mInterline - (mInterline - mHeight);

  if ( align.contains("BOTTOM") )
    painter.translate(0, 0);
  else if ( align.contains("TOP") )
    painter.translate(0, area.height() - mHeight);
  else
    painter.translate(0, area.height() - (area.height() - height) / 2 - mHeight);


  for ( int i = 0; i < text.count(); ++i )
  { 
    QMatrix save = painter.matrix();


    int width = text[i].length() * mAdvance - (mAdvance - mWidth);

    if ( align.contains("LEFT") )
      painter.translate(0, 0);
    else if ( align.contains("RIGHT") )
      painter.translate(area.width() - width, 0);
    else
      painter.translate((area.width() - width) / 2, 0);

    drawLine(painter, text[i]);


    painter.setMatrix(save);
    painter.translate(0, -mInterline);
   }

  painter.setClipping(false);
  painter.setMatrix(matrix);
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
draw::QStringList::text::QStringList::split::QChar::QString::str::remove::QChar::QMatrix::matrix::painter::matrix::painter::translate::area::x::area::y::height::text::count::mInterline::mInterline::mHeight::align::contains::BOTTOM::painter::translate::align::contains::TOP::painter::translate::area::height::mHeight::painter::translate::area::height::area::height::height::mHeight::i::i::text::count::i::QMatrix::save::painter::matrix::width::text::i::length::mAdvance::mAdvance::mWidth::align::contains::LEFT::painter::translate::align::contains::RIGHT::painter::translate::area::width::width::painter::translate::area::width::width::drawLine::painter::text::i::painter::setMatrix::save::painter::translate::mInterline::painter::setClipping::false::painter::setMatrix::matrix
__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
#METRICS ARRAYOP:2 ASM:0 ASS:6 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:33 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:6 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:28 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:4 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:42 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/style/font.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:4 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:3 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:41 LOCALS:47 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:91 L_END:131 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:draw NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:4 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:19 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
drawLine
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter, const QString &str)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  for ( int i = 0; i < str.length(); i++ )
  { 
    drawChar(painter, str[i].toAscii());
    painter.translate(mAdvance, 0);
   }
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:4 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:3 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/style/font.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:7 LOCALS:17 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:146 L_END:152 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:drawLine NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:4 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
drawChar
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPainter &painter, char ch)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QMatrix matrix = painter.matrix();
  painter.scale(mWidth / 80, mHeight / 100);

  switch ( ch )
  { 
    case ' ' :
      break;

    case '!' :
      painter.drawLine(40,  30, 40, 100);
      painter.drawLine(35,   0, 45,   0);
      painter.drawLine(45,   0, 45,  10);
      painter.drawLine(45,  10, 35,  10);
      painter.drawLine(45,  10, 35,   0);
      break;   

    case '\"' :
      painter.drawLine(20,  75, 25,  75);
      painter.drawLine(25,  75, 25, 100);
      painter.drawLine(25, 100, 20, 100);
      painter.drawLine(20, 100, 20,  75);
      painter.drawLine(55,  75, 60,  75);
      painter.drawLine(60,  75, 60, 100);
      painter.drawLine(60, 100, 55, 100);
      painter.drawLine(55, 100, 55,  75);
      break;

    case '
      painter.drawLine(25, 100, 25,   0);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  70, 80,  70);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  30, 80,  30);
      painter.drawLine(55, 100, 55,   0);
      break;

    case '$' :
      painter.drawLine(60,  85, 75,  75);
      painter.drawLine(20,  85,  0,  70);
      painter.drawLine(20,  15, 60,  15);
      painter.drawLine(60,  15, 80,  30);
      painter.drawLine(20,  15,  5,  25);
      painter.drawLine(20,  50, 60,  50);
      painter.drawLine(20,  50,  0,  60);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  70,  0,  60);
      painter.drawLine(60,  50, 80,  40);
      painter.drawLine(80,  40, 80,  30);
      painter.drawLine(25, 100, 25,   0);
      painter.drawLine(55, 100, 55,   0);
      painter.drawLine(20,  85, 60,  85);
      break;

    case '%' :
      painter.drawLine(80, 100,  0,   0);
      painter.drawLine(15, 100, 30, 100);
      painter.drawLine(50,  40, 65,  40);
      painter.drawLine(65,  40, 75,  30);
      painter.drawLine(75,  30, 75,  15);
      painter.drawLine(75,  15, 65,   5);
      painter.drawLine(65,   5, 50,   5);
      painter.drawLine(50,   5, 40,  15);
      painter.drawLine(40,  15, 40,  30);
      painter.drawLine(40,  30, 50,  40);
      painter.drawLine(30, 100, 40,  90);
      painter.drawLine(40,  90, 40,  75);
      painter.drawLine(40,  75, 30,  65);
      painter.drawLine(30,  65, 15,  65);
      painter.drawLine(15,  65,  5,  75);
      painter.drawLine( 5,  75,  5,  90);
      painter.drawLine( 5,  90, 15, 100);
      break;

    case '&' :
      painter.drawLine(80,   0,  0,  70);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  70,  0,  85);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  85, 10, 100);
      painter.drawLine(10, 100, 25, 100);
      painter.drawLine(25, 100, 35,  85);
      painter.drawLine(35,  85, 35,  70);
      painter.drawLine(35,  70,  0,  35);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  35,  0,  15);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  15, 30,   0);
      painter.drawLine(30,   0, 80,  30);
      break;

    case '\'' :
      painter.drawLine(40,  85, 50,  85);
      painter.drawLine(50,  85, 50,  95);
      painter.drawLine(50,  95, 40,  95);
      painter.drawLine(40,  95, 40,  85);
      painter.drawLine(50,  85, 40,  65);

      break;

    case '(' :
      painter.drawLine(40,  20, 60,   0);
      painter.drawLine(40,  90, 40,  20);
      painter.drawLine(60, 110, 40,  90);
      break;

    case ')' :
      painter.drawLine(30, 110, 50,  90);
      painter.drawLine(50,  90, 50,  20);
      painter.drawLine(50,  20, 30,   0);
      break;

    case '*' :
      painter.drawLine( 0,  50, 80,  50);
      painter.drawLine(40,  90, 40,  10);
      painter.drawLine(70,  80, 10,  20);
      painter.drawLine(10,  80, 70,  20);
      break;

    case '+' :
      painter.drawLine( 0,  50, 80,  50);
      painter.drawLine(40,  90, 40,  10);
      break;

    case ',' :
      painter.drawLine(30,   0, 40,   0);
      painter.drawLine(40,   0, 40,  10);
      painter.drawLine(40,  10, 30,  10);
      painter.drawLine(30,  10, 30,   0);
      painter.drawLine(40,   0, 30, -20);
      break;

    case '-' :
      painter.drawLine( 0,  50, 80,  50);
      break;

    case '.' :
      painter.drawLine(30,  20, 20,  10);
      painter.drawLine(20,  10, 30,   0);
      painter.drawLine(30,   0, 40,  10);
      painter.drawLine(40,  10, 40,  10);
      painter.drawLine(40,  10, 30,  20);
      break;

    case '/' :
      painter.drawLine(80, 110,  0,   0);
      break;

    case '0' :
      painter.drawLine(20, 110,  0,  90);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  20, 20,   0);
      painter.drawLine(20,   0, 60,   0);
      painter.drawLine(60,   0, 80,  20);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  90,  0,  20);
      painter.drawLine(80,  90, 80,  20);
      painter.drawLine(80,  90, 60, 110);
      painter.drawLine(60, 110, 20, 110);
      break;

    case '1' :
      painter.drawLine(40, 110, 40,   0);
      painter.drawLine(40, 110, 20,  90);
      painter.drawLine(10,   0, 70,   0);
      break;

    case '2' :
      painter.drawLine( 0,  90, 20, 110);
      painter.drawLine(20, 110, 60, 110);
      painter.drawLine(60, 110, 80,  90);
      painter.drawLine(80,  90, 80,  60);
      painter.drawLine(80,  60,  0,  20);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  20,  0,   0);
      painter.drawLine( 0,   0, 80,   0);
      painter.drawLine(80,   0, 80,  20);
      break;

    case '3' :
      painter.drawLine( 0,  90, 20, 110);
      painter.drawLine(20, 110, 60, 110);
      painter.drawLine(60, 110, 80,  90);
      painter.drawLine(80,  75, 60,  55);
      painter.drawLine(60,  55, 30,  55);
      painter.drawLine(60,  55, 80,  35);
      painter.drawLine(80,  90, 80,  75);
      painter.drawLine(80,  35, 80,  20);
      painter.drawLine(80,  20, 60,   0);
      painter.drawLine(60,   0, 20,   0);
      painter.drawLine(20,   0,  0,  20);
      break;

    case '4' :
      painter.drawLine(60, 110, 60,   0);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  45, 80,  45);
      painter.drawLine(60, 110,  0,  45);
      break;

    case '5' :
      painter.drawLine(80, 110,  0, 110);
      painter.drawLine( 0, 110,  0,  65);
      painter.drawLine(80,  45, 80,  20);
      painter.drawLine( 0,  65, 60,  65);
      painter.drawLine(60,  65, 80,  45);
      painter.drawLine(80,  20, 60,   0);
      painter.drawLine(60,   0, 20,   0);
      painter.drawLine(20,   0,  0,  20);
      break;

    case '6' :
      painter.drawLine( 0,  90, 20, 110);
      painter.drawLine(20, 110, 60, 110);
      painter.drawLine(60, 110, 80,  90);
      painter.drawLine(60,  65, 20,  65);

      painter.drawLine(20,   0,  0,  20);

    case '7' :

      painter.drawLine( 0,  20,  0,   0);

    case ' }' :

      painter.drawLine(30,  80, 50,  60);

    case 0x80 :

    case 0x81 :

   }

  painter.setMatrix(matrix);

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setObjectName("theCWidgetView");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_16.png"));

  mMainWindow = mw;

  mStyle = new CStyle;





  QPalette palette;
  palette.setColor(backgroundRole(), "black");
  setPalette(palette);





  mDock = new QDockWidget(this);
  mDock->setFeatures(QDockWidget::AllDockWidgetFeatures);
  mDock->setWindowTitle("Widget List");
  mMainWindow->addDockWidget(Qt::RightDockWidgetArea, mDock);

  mWidgetList = new QToolBox(mDock);
  mWidgetList->setMinimumSize(250, 0);
  mWidgetList->setFrameShape(QToolBox::NoFrame);
  mWidgetList->setFrameShadow(QToolBox::Plain);
  mWidgetList->setCurrentIndex(0);
  mDock->setWidget(mWidgetList);
  mWidgetList->show();





  mProperties = new CProperties(this);

  QMap<QString, QVariant> extra;
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Enter widget driver document comment");
  mProperties->setProperty("comment", "", extra);





  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mMainWindow, SLOT(slotUpdateModIndicator()));
  connect(mWidgetList, SIGNAL(currentChanged(int)), this, SLOT(repaint()));
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:4 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/widgetview.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:3 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:11 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:235 L_END:240 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:editFind NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



  CMarkup xml;
  if ( !xml.load(fn) )
  { 
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "XML document error.");
    return false;
   }



  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));






  for ( int i = 0; i < mWidgetList->count(); ++i )
  { 
    QWidget *item = mWidgetList->item(i);
    mWidgetList->removeItem(item);
    delete item;
   }


  xml.findElem();
  mVersion = atoi(xml.getAttrib("library_version").c_str());
  mSupp = atoi(xml.getAttrib("supp_version").c_str());

  xml.findChildElem("model");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findChildElem("prop");
  mId = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("value").c_str());
  xml.outOfElem();

  while ( xml.findChildElem("a661_layer") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();

    CWidgetList *layer = new CWidgetList(mWidgetList, this);
    layer->load(xml);
    connect(layer, SIGNAL(currentChanged(Q3ListViewItem *)), this, SLOT(repaint()));

    xml.outOfElem();
   }





    QString backup = QDir::currentDirPath();
  QDir::setCurrent(QFileInfo(fn).dirPath());

  CMarkup style;
  if ( style.load("style.xml") )
    mStyle->load(style);
  else
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "XML style document not found.");

  QDir::setCurrent(backup);


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:7 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:43 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:5 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:21 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:1 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:47 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/widgetview.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:6 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:72 LOCALS:85 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:254 L_END:325 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:readFile NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:8 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:33 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:1 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
writeFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( fn.isEmpty() )
  { 
    fn = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(".", filter(), 0);

    if ( fn.isEmpty() )
      return false;
    else if ( QFileInfo(fn).extension(false).isEmpty() )
      fn += ".wgd";
   }

  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  CMarkup xml;
  xml.setDoc("<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<!DOCTYPE a661_rf>\n");
  xml.addElem("a661_rf");
  xml.addAttrib("library_version", mVersion);
  xml.addAttrib("supp_version", mSupp);

  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("model");
  xml.addChildElem("prop");
  xml.addChildAttrib("name", "ApplicationId");
  xml.addChildAttrib("value", mId);





  for ( int i = 0; i < mWidgetList->count(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidgetList *layer = qobject_cast<CWidgetList *>(mWidgetList->item(i));
    if ( layer )
      layer->save(xml);
   }





  if ( !xml.save(fn) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(fn);
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "FMS Editor", message);

    QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
    return false;
   }


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
paintEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPaintEvent *)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CWidgetList *layer = qobject_cast<CWidgetList *>(mWidgetList->currentItem());

  if ( !layer )
    return;

  QPainter painter(this);











  painter.setWindow(0, layer->layerHeight(), layer->layerWidth(), -layer->layerHeight());





  for ( int i = 0; i < layer->topLevelItemCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(layer->topLevelItem(i));

    if ( widget->isVisible() )
      widget->draw(painter);
   }





  CWidget *current = (CWidget *)layer->currentItem();
  if ( current )
  { 
    QPen pen("lightGreen");


    painter.setPen(pen);
    painter.setBrush(QBrush());
    painter.drawPolygon(current->getArea());
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
mousePressEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QMouseEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CWidgetList *layer = qobject_cast<CWidgetList *>(mWidgetList->currentItem());
  if ( !layer )
    return;





  QPainter painter(this);
  QRect area = painter.viewport();

  QPoint pos(event->pos());
  pos.setX( pos.x() * layer->layerWidth() / area.width() );
  pos.setY( layer->layerHeight() - pos.y() * layer->layerHeight() / area.height() );

  CWidget *widget = getWidget(pos);
  if ( widget )
  { 
    layer->setCurrentItem(widget);
    layer->scrollToItem(widget);

   }
  else
    layer->clearSelection();

  repaint();
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
maybeSave
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( isModified() )
  { 
    QString fn = QFileInfo(filename()).fileName();
    int ret = QMessageBox::warning( 0,
                                    "Editor",
                                    QString("File %1 has been modified.\n"
                                            "Do you want to save your changes?").arg(fn),
                                    QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::Default,
                                    QMessageBox::No,
                                    QMessageBox::Cancel | QMessageBox::Escape );
    if ( ret == QMessageBox::Yes )
      return writeFile(filename());
    else if ( ret == QMessageBox::Cancel )
      return false;
   }
  return true;
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
getWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPoint pos)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CWidgetList *layer = qobject_cast<CWidgetList *>(mWidgetList->currentItem());
  if ( !layer )
    return 0;

  CWidget *current = 0;

  QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> list = layer->findItems("*", Qt::MatchWildcard | Qt::MatchRecursive);
  for ( QList<QTreeWidgetItem *>::iterator it = list.begin(); it != list.end(); ++it )
  { 
    CWidget *widget = static_cast<CWidget *>(*it);

    if ( widget->isVisible() && QRegion(widget->getArea()).contains(pos) )
      current = widget;
   }


  return current;
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/widget/style.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:4 LOCALS:7 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:43 L_END:46 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:mDefaultFont NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:4 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.findElem("style");
  xml.intoElem();





  xml.findElem("colortable");

  while ( xml.findChildElem("color") )
  { 
    int index = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("index").c_str());
    int r = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("red").c_str());
    int g = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("green").c_str());
    int b = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("blue").c_str());

    mColor.insert(index, new QColor(r, g, b));
   }





  xml.findElem("fonttable");

  while ( xml.findChildElem("font") )
  { 
    int index = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("index").c_str());
    int width = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("width").c_str());
    int height = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("height").c_str());
    int advance = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("advance").c_str());
    int interline = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("interline").c_str());

    mFont.insert(index, new CFont(width, height, advance, interline));
   }





  xml.findElem("picturetable");

  while ( xml.findChildElem("picture") )
  { 
    int index = atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("index").c_str());
    QString file = xml.getChildAttrib("file").c_str();

    QPixmap pix;
    if ( pix.load(file) )
      mPicture.insert(index, &pix);


   }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
QTreeWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setObjectName("theCProject");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_16.png"));

  mMainWindow = mw;
  mDocument = doc;
  CGraphicDesign *mGraphicDesign = graphic;
  mComponentCmdStack = new CUndoStack();

  doc->mProject = this;
  doc->mGraphicDesign = graphic;
  doc->mCmdStack = mComponentCmdStack;
  mGraphicDesign->mProject = this;
  mGraphicDesign->mCmdStack = mComponentCmdStack;
  

  mFilename = doc->filename();




  setColumnCount(2);
  QStringList headers;
  headers << tr("Files") << tr("Type");
  setHeaderLabels(headers);
  header()->setResizeMode(0, QHeaderView::Stretch);

  setSortingEnabled(false);
  setRootIsDecorated(false);
  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
  header()->hide();





  mOpenAct = new QAction(tr("&Open"), this);
  mOpenAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+O"));
  mOpenAct->setIcon(QIcon(":image older_24.png"));
  mOpenAct->setStatusTip(tr("Opens document"));
  connect(mOpenAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotOpen()));

  mPropAct = new QAction(tr("&Properties..."), this);
  mPropAct->setIcon(QIcon(":image rench_24.png"));
  mPropAct->setStatusTip(tr("Shows the active document properties"));
  connect(mPropAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotProperties()));

  mAddAct = new QAction(tr("&Add Document..."), this);
  mAddAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddAct->setIcon(QIcon(":image ocument_add_24.png"));
  mAddAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds document to project"));
  connect(mAddAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAdd()));

  mGenAct = new QAction(tr("&Generate"), this);
  mGenAct->setIcon(QIcon(":image ext_code_cpluplus_24.png"));
  mGenAct->setStatusTip(tr("Generates source from the active document"));
  connect(mGenAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotGenerate()));

  mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
  mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
  mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
  mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Removes the active document from project"));
  connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDelete()));





  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemDoubleClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotDoubleClick()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemCollapsed(QTreeWidgetItem *)), this, SLOT(collapseItem(QTreeWidgetItem *)));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mMainWindow, SLOT(slotUpdateModIndicator()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(activeProjectModified(CConfig*, CGraphicDesign*)), CGraphicProperties::getInstance(), SLOT(slotUpdateProject(CConfig*, CGraphicDesign*)));





  CProjectDocItem *pro = new CProjectDocItem(this);
  setItemExpanded(pro, true);
  pro->setText(0, "project");


  emit(activeProjectModified(mDocument, mGraphicDesign));
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  clear();
  CProjectDocItem *pro = new CProjectDocItem(this);
  setItemExpanded(pro, true);
  pro->filename(mFilename);

  while ( xml.findElem("doc") )
  { 
    QString type = xml.getAttrib("type").c_str();

    CBaseProjectItem *item = 0;
    if ( type == "param" )
      item = new CParamDocItem(pro);
    else if ( type == "option" )
      item = new COptionDocItem(pro);
    else if ( type == "widget" )
      item = new CWidgetDocItem(pro);
    item->load(xml);
   }

  mCmdStack.clear();
 }
__END_BODY__

slotAdd

__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QString filename = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName( ".",
                                                   "Param Files (*.par)\n"
                                                   "Option Files (*.opt)\n"
                                                   "Widget Files (*.wgd)",
                                                   this );

  if ( QFileInfo(filename).exists() )
  { 
    QString extension = QFileInfo(filename).extension(false);

    CBaseProjectItem *item;

    if ( extension == "par" )
      item = new CParamDocItem(currentItem());
    else if ( extension == "opt" )
      item = new COptionDocItem(currentItem());
    else if ( extension == "wgd" )
      item = new CWidgetDocItem(currentItem());

    item->filename(filename);
   }
 }

slotOpen
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CBaseProjectItem *item = (CBaseProjectItem *)selectedItems().value(0);

  if ( item )
  { 
    QWidget *doc = mMainWindow->getDocumentWidget(QFileInfo(item->filename()).absFilePath());

    if ( doc )
    { 
      if ( mMainWindow->activeDocument() )
        doc->showMaximized();
      else
        doc->show();

      doc->setFocus();
     }
   }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenuEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QContextMenuEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

  if ( item == 0 )
    return;

  if ( item->type() == ProjectDoc )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mOpenAct);
    menu.addAction(mGenAct);
    menu.insertSeparator();
    menu.addAction(mAddAct);
    menu.insertSeparator();
    menu.addAction(mPropAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mOpenAct);
    menu.insertSeparator();
    menu.addAction(mPropAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setText(1, xml.getAttrib("cname").c_str());

  xml.intoElem();
  CBaseConfigItem *previous = 0;
  while ( xml.findElem() )
  { 
    CBaseConfigItem *item = 0;

    if ( xml.getTagName() == "LRU" )
      item = new CConfigLRU(this, previous);
    else if(xml.getTagName() == "value")
      item = new CConfigValue(this, previous);
    else if(xml.getTagName() == "userValue")
      item = new CConfigUserValue(this, previous);

    item->load(xml);
    previous = item;
   }
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:4 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:1 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:4 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/project/configitem.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:5 LOCALS:10 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:130 L_END:134 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:CBaseConfigItem NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:3 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:3 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setText(1, xml.getAttrib("cname").c_str());

  xml.intoElem();
  CBaseConfigItem *previous = 0;
  CBaseConfigItem *io = 0;
  CBaseConfigItem *cots = 0;
  while ( xml.findElem() )
  { 
    CBaseConfigItem *item = 0;

    if ( xml.getTagName() == "PARTBL" )
      item = new CConfigTable(this, previous);
    else if ( xml.getTagName() == "INTERFACE" )
      io = item = new CConfigInterface(this, previous);
    else if ( xml.getTagName() == "COTS" )
      cots = item = new CConfigCots(this, previous);
    else if ( xml.getTagName() == "PROCESSOR" )
      item = new CConfigProcess(this, previous);
    else if ( xml.getTagName() == "value" )
      item = new CConfigValue(this, previous);
    else if ( xml.getTagName() == "userValue" )
      item = new CConfigUserValue(this, previous);

    item->load(xml);
    previous = item;
   }
  xml.outOfElem();

 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

	CBaseConfigItem *item = NULL;

	if(xml.getTagName() == "value")
		item = new CConfigValue(this, previous);
	else if(xml.getTagName() == "userValue")
		item = new CConfigUserValue(this, previous);

	item->load(xml);
    previous = item;
   }
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__

__END_IDS__

  xml.intoElem();

    static_cast<CBaseConfigItem *>(child(i))->save(xml);
  xml.outOfElem();

__BEGIN_NAME__
QTreeWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setObjectName("theCConfig");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_16.png"));

  mMainWindow = mw;
  mSystem = NULL;




  setColumnCount(3);
  QStringList headers;
  headers << tr("Component") << tr("Type") << tr("Value") << tr("Comment");
  setHeaderLabels(headers);
  header()->resizeSection(0, 250);
  header()->resizeSection(1, 125);
  header()->setResizeMode(2, QHeaderView::Stretch);

  setSortingEnabled(false);
  setRootIsDecorated(false);
  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);





  mProperties = new CProperties(this);

  QMap<QString, QVariant> extra;
  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Enter project document comment");
  mProperties->setProperty("comment", "", extra);





  mAddLRUAct = new QAction(tr("&Add LRU"), this);
  mAddLRUAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddLRUAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds LRU component"));
  connect(mAddLRUAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddLRU()));

  mAddProcessAct = new QAction(tr("&Add Processor"), this);
  mAddProcessAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddProcessAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds processor component"));
  connect(mAddProcessAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddProcess()));

  mAddInterfaceAct = new QAction(tr("Add &Interface"), this);
  mAddInterfaceAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+I"));
  mAddInterfaceAct->setStatusTip(tr("Add Interface component"));
  connect(mAddInterfaceAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddInterface()));

  mAddParamTblAct = new QAction(tr("Add Parameter &Table"), this);
  mAddParamTblAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+T"));
  mAddParamTblAct->setStatusTip(tr("Add Parameter Table component"));
  connect(mAddParamTblAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddParamTbl()));

  mAddCotsAct = new QAction(tr("Add &COTS"), this);
  mAddCotsAct->setStatusTip(tr("Add Off The Shelf component"));
  connect(mAddCotsAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddCots()));

  mAddValueAct = new QAction(tr("Add &Value"), this);
  mAddValueAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds user's value"));
  connect(mAddValueAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddValue()));

  mAddPropertyAct = new QAction(tr("Add &Property"), this);

  mAddPropertyAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds a new property"));
  connect(mAddPropertyAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddProperty()));

  mEditSystemAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditSystemAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditSystemAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditSystemAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits System"));
  connect(mEditSystemAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditSystem()));

  mEditLRUAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditLRUAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditLRUAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditLRUAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits LRU"));
  connect(mEditLRUAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditLRU()));

  mEditTableAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditTableAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditTableAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditTableAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits parameter table"));
  connect(mEditTableAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditTable()));

  mEditInterfaceAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditInterfaceAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditInterfaceAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditInterfaceAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits interface"));
  connect(mEditInterfaceAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditInterface()));

  mEditPowerAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditPowerAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditPowerAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditPowerAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits power supply"));
  connect(mEditPowerAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditPowerSupply()));

  mEditProcessAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditProcessAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditProcessAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditProcessAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits processor"));
  connect(mEditProcessAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditProcess()));

  mEditValueAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditValueAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditValueAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditValueAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits value"));
  connect(mEditValueAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditValue()));

  mEditUserValueAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditUserValueAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditUserValueAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditUserValueAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits value"));
  connect(mEditUserValueAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditUserValue()));

  mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
  mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
  mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
  mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
  connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDelete()));





  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemDoubleClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotDoubleClick()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemCollapsed(QTreeWidgetItem *)), this, SLOT(collapseItem(QTreeWidgetItem *)));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mMainWindow, SLOT(slotUpdateModIndicator()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotUpdateSelection()));





  CConfigSystem *system = new CConfigSystem(this, 0, systemName);

  CConfigValue *value = 0;
  value = new CConfigValue(system, value);
  value->setText(0, "Name");
  value->setText(1, "string");
  value->setText(2, "theSystem");

  value = new CConfigValue(system, value);
  value->setText(0, "Version");
  value->setText(1, "string");
  value->setText(2, "1.0");
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
menu
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const Menu &item)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  switch ( item )
  { 
    case EditUndo :
      return mCmdStack->canUndo();
    case EditRedo :
      return mCmdStack->canRedo();
    case EditCut :
      return true;
    case EditCopy :
      return true;
    case EditPaste :
      return true;
    case EditDelete :
      return true;
    case EditFind :
      return true;
    default:
      return false;
   }
 }

editDelete
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();
  CGraphicElement* graphicItem;

  if ( item->type() != ConfigSystem && item->type() != ConfigValue )
  { 
	graphicItem = mGraphicDesign->getGraphicElement(item);
	mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdDel("delete project item", item, graphicItem, mGraphicDesign, this));
	emit modified();
   }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
editFind
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CFindDialog dialog;
  dialog.caseCheck->hide();
  dialog.startCheck->hide();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString text = dialog.findEdit->text();

    Qt::MatchFlags flags = Qt::MatchRecursive;
    if ( dialog.exactCheck->isChecked() )
      flags |= Qt::MatchCaseSensitive;

    QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> found = findItems(text, flags, 0);
    if ( found.count() )
      scrollToItem(found[0]);
   }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:4 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:8 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:6 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:11 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/project/config.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:3 IN:0 INDR:5 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:18 LOCALS:32 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:427 L_END:444 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:editFind NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:4 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:8 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



  CMarkup xml;
  if ( !xml.load(fn) )
  { 
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "XML document error.");
    return false;
   }



  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  clear();

  xml.findElem();
  xml.intoElem();

  xml.findElem("SYSTEM");
  mSystem = new CConfigSystem(this, 0);
  mSystem->load(xml);





  if ( mProject )
    mProject->load(xml);





  xml.findElem("properties");
 
  while ( xml.findChildElem() )
  { 
    QString name = xml.getChildTagName().c_str();
    QString value = xml.getChildData().c_str();
    mProperties->setProperty(name, value);
	
   }
  xml.outOfElem();

  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack->clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
		
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
writeFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  mGraphicDesign->writeProperties();
  
  if ( fn.isEmpty() )
  { 
    fn = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(".", filter(), 0);

    if ( fn.isEmpty() )
	{ 
		mGraphicDesign->removeProperties();
		return false;
	 }
    else if ( QFileInfo(fn).extension(false).isEmpty() )
      fn += ".acs";

	if (QFileInfo(fn).exists())
	{ 
		int rep = QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "This file already exists.  Do you want to overwrite it?", 
			QMessageBox::Yes, QMessageBox::No);
		if (rep == QMessageBox::No)
		{ 
			mGraphicDesign->removeProperties();
			return false;
		 }
	 }
	

	
	QDir systDir;
    QString relativeFN;
	QString systName ; 

	bool ok;

	
	
        systName = QInputDialog::getText(this, "",
                                            "Enter System Name", QLineEdit::Normal,
                                             "", &ok);
		if(!ok)
			return false;
		

		if ( systName.isEmpty())
		{ 	
			QMessageBox::warning(0,"Cancelling Save As", "No system name provided");
			return false;
		 }

		systDir = QFileInfo(fn).absoluteDir();
		relativeFN = systDir.relativeFilePath(fn);
		systDir.mkdir(systName);

		systDir.cd(systName);

		systDir.mkdir("Config");
		systDir.mkdir("Doc");
		systDir.mkdir("Src");
		systDir.mkdir("Res");

		systDir.cd("Config");
		systDir.mkdir("Default");
		systDir.cd("Default");

		fn= systDir.absolutePath()+"/"+relativeFN;

   }

  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  CMarkup xml;
  xml.setDoc("<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n");
  xml.addElem("ACS");
  xml.addAttrib("type", "project");
  xml.addAttrib("version", glb::version);

  xml.intoElem();

  



  for ( int i = 0; i < topLevelItemCount(); ++i )
  { 
    static_cast<CBaseConfigItem *>(topLevelItem(i))->save(xml);
	
   }





  if ( mProject )
    mProject->save(xml);





  xml.addElem("properties");
  QStringList list = mProperties->names();
  for ( int i = 0; i < list.count(); ++i )
  { 
    xml.addChildElem(list[i].toAscii().data());
    xml.setChildData(mProperties->value(list[i]).toString().toAscii().data());
   }

  xml.outOfElem();





  if ( !xml.save(fn) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(fn);
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "FMS Editor", message);

    QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
    return false;
   }

  mGraphicDesign->removeProperties();

  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack->clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

  return false;

	CGraphicElement *graphicCOTS = NULL;

    QTreeWidgetItem *selected = selectedItems().value(0);
    QTreeWidgetItem *last = selected;
    if ( last )
      last = last->child(last->childCount() - 1);
	

	CConfigCots *component = new CConfigCots(selected, last);
	mGraphicCots->addCots(selectedCots, selected, last, component);

	if ( cname == "acs_PowerSupply" )

		graphicCOTS = mMainWindow->getGraphicDesign()->addElement(gCOTS, component, selected, QPoint(0, 0));
		mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdAdd("add processor item", component, graphicCOTS, mGraphicDesign));
		setCurrentItem(component);
		emit modified();
	 }
	else
	{ 
		graphicCOTS = mMainWindow->getGraphicDesign()->addElement(gCOTS, component, selected, QPoint(0, 0));
		mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdAdd("add processor item", component, graphicCOTS, mGraphicDesign));
		setCurrentItem(component);
		emit modified();
	 }


 }

{ 
	QTreeWidgetItem *selected = selectedItems().value(0);
    QTreeWidgetItem *last = selected;
	CGraphicElement *graphicParamTbl = NULL;

    emit modified();
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotAddValue
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CConfigEditDialog dialog(this, Value);

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.name();
    QString type = dialog.type();
    QString value = dialog.value();

    QTreeWidgetItem *selected = selectedItems().value(0);
    CConfigValue *item = 0;
    if ( selected->type() == ConfigValue )
      item = new CConfigValue(selected->parent(), selected);
    else
      item = new CConfigValue(selected, 0);

    item->setText(0, name);
    item->setText(1, type);
    item->setText(2, value);

    emit modified();
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotAddProperty
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	CAddPropDialog dialog(this);
	int index;

	if(dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted)
	{ 
		QTreeWidgetItem *selected = selectedItems().value(0);
		QTreeWidgetItem *parent = selected;
		QTreeWidgetItem *lastProperty = selected;
		if(selected == NULL)
		{ 
			QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
										"No item is selected in the TreeView.\n\n",
										"OK");
			return;
		 }


		for(index = 0; index < lastProperty->childCount(); index++)
		{ 
			if(parent->child(index)->type() < ConfigValue ||
				parent->child(index)->type() > ConfigUserValue)
				break;
		 }
		index--;
		if(index >= 0)
		{ 
			lastProperty = parent->child(index);
		 }

		if (selected->type() >= ConfigSystem &&
			selected->type() <= ConfigProcess)
		{ 

			QString typeText;
			if(dialog.custTypeChk->checkState() == Qt::Checked)
			{ 
				typeText = dialog.custTypeEdit->text();
			 }
			else if(dialog.custTypeChk->checkState() == Qt::Unchecked)
			{ 
				typeText = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
			 }


			if(!propertyExists(parent, dialog.nameEdit->text()))
			{ 

				CConfigUserValue *item = new CConfigUserValue(selected, lastProperty);
				item->setText(0, dialog.nameEdit->text());
				item->setText(1, typeText);
				item->setText(2, dialog.valueEdit->text());


				mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdAdd("add custom property", item, NULL, NULL));
				setCurrentItem(item->parent());
				emit modified();
			 }
			else
			{ 
				QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
											"A property with this name already exists.\n\n",
											"OK");
			 }
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

slotAddMessage

__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString typeProc, CGraphicMessage *msg, QTreeWidgetItem *processor)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	setCurrentItem(processor);
	QTreeWidgetItem *selected = selectedItems().value(0);
    QTreeWidgetItem *last = selected;
    if ( last )
      last = last->child(last->childCount() - 1);

	CConfigValue *item = 0;
	item = new CConfigValue(selected, last);
    item->setText(0, "msgFilter");
    item->setText(1, "bool");
	if (msg->getFilter())
		item->setText(2, "TRUE");
	else
		item->setText(2, "FALSE");

	item = new CConfigValue(selected, last);
    item->setText(0, "msgPeriodicity");
    item->setText(1, "int");
	item->setText(2, QString("%1").arg(msg->getPeriodicity()));

	item = new CConfigValue(selected, last);
    item->setText(0, "msgTypeMsg");
    item->setText(1, "string");
	item->setText(2, msg->getTypeMsg());

	item = new CConfigValue(selected, last);
    item->setText(0, "msgID");
    item->setText(1, "int");
	item->setText(2, QString("%1").arg(msg->getID()));

    item = new CConfigValue(selected, last);
    item->setText(0, "msgName");
    item->setText(1, "string");
	item->setText(2, msg->getName());

	item = new CConfigValue(selected, last);
    item->setText(0, "msgTypeProc");
    item->setText(1, "string");
    item->setText(2, typeProc);
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotEditValue
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

	CConfigEditDialog dialog(this, Value);
	dialog.name(item->text(0));
	dialog.mName->setEnabled(false);
	dialog.type(item->text(1));
	dialog.mType->setEnabled(false);
	dialog.value(item->text(2));
	dialog.slotReresh();

	if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
	{ 
		QString name = dialog.name();
		QString type = dialog.type();
		QString value = dialog.value();

		mCmdStack->push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "edit value item"));
		mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("", item, 0, name, false));
		mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("", item, 1, type, false));
		mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("", item, 2, value, false));
		mCmdStack->push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "edit value item"));
		emit modified();
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotEditUserValue
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();
	CAddPropDialog dialog(this);
	int index, count;


	dialog.setWindowTitle(tr("Edit custom property"));
	dialog.addButton->setText(tr("Save"));



	dialog.nameEdit->setText(item->text(0));

	if((index = dialog.typeEdit->findText(item->text(1), Qt::MatchExactly)) == -1)
	{ 
		dialog.typeEdit->setDisabled(true);
		dialog.custTypeChk->setChecked(true);
		dialog.custTypeEdit->setText(item->text(1));
	 }
	else
	{ 
		dialog.custTypeEdit->setDisabled(true);
		dialog.custTypeChk->setChecked(false);
		dialog.typeEdit->setCurrentIndex(index);
	 }

	dialog.valueEdit->setText(item->text(2));

	if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
	{ 
		QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
		QString type;
		QString value = dialog.valueEdit->text();


		if(dialog.custTypeChk->checkState() == Qt::Checked)
			type = dialog.custTypeEdit->text();
		else
			type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();


		if(propertyExists(item->parent(), name) &&
			item->text(0) != name)
		{ 
			emit modified();
					QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
												"A property with this name already exists.\n\n",
												"OK");
		 }
		else
		{ 
			mCmdStack->push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "edit user value item"));
			mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("", item, 0, name, false));
			mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("", item, 1, type, false));
			mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("", item, 2, value, false));
			mCmdStack->push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "edit user value item"));
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotDeleteMessage
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QTreeWidgetItem *processor, QString typeProc, QString name)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	for(int i=0; i<processor->childCount(); i++)
	{ 
		if (processor->child(i)->text(0) == "msgTypeProc")
		{ 
			if ((typeProc == "") || ((processor->child(i)->text(2) == typeProc) && 
				(processor->child(i+1)->text(2) == name)))
			{ 
				processor->takeChild(i+5);
				processor->takeChild(i+4);
				processor->takeChild(i+3);
				processor->takeChild(i+2);
				processor->takeChild(i+1);
				processor->takeChild(i);
				i = -1;
			 }
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenuEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QContextMenuEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

  if ( item == 0 )
    return;

  if ( item->type() == ConfigSystem )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mEditSystemAct);
    menu.addAction(mAddLRUAct);
	menu.addAction(mAddPropertyAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ConfigLRU )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddProcessAct);
	if (!hasInterface(item))
		menu.addAction(mAddInterfaceAct);
	if (!hasParamTbl(item))
		menu.addAction(mAddParamTblAct);
	menu.addAction(mAddCotsAct);
	menu.addAction(mAddPropertyAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditLRUAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ConfigTable )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
	menu.addAction(mAddPropertyAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditTableAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ConfigInterface )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
	menu.addAction(mAddPropertyAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditInterfaceAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ConfigPowerSupply )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
	menu.addAction(mAddPropertyAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditPowerAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ConfigProcess )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
	menu.addAction(mAddPropertyAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditProcessAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ConfigValue )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mEditValueAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == ConfigUserValue )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mEditUserValueAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());

   }
 }
__END_BODY__

(QCloseEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( maybeSave() )
  { 
	event->accept();
	mMainWindow->setContext("Context: None");
	CGraphicComponents::getInstance()->setComponentsEnabled("Context: None", true, true, false);
	mGraphicDesign->close();
   }

    event->ignore();

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
maybeSave
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( isModified() )
  { 
    QString fn = QFileInfo(filename()).fileName();
    int ret = QMessageBox::warning( 0,
                                    "Editor",
                                    QString("File %1 has been modified.\n"
                                            "Do you want to save your changes?").arg(fn),
                                    QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::Default,
                                    QMessageBox::No,
                                    QMessageBox::Cancel | QMessageBox::Escape );
    if ( ret == QMessageBox::Yes )
      return writeFile(filename());
    else if ( ret == QMessageBox::Cancel )
      return false;
   }
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
maybeSave::isModified::QString::fn::QFileInfo::filename::fileName::ret::QMessageBox::warning::Editor::QString::File::has::been::modified::n::Do::you::want::to::save::your::changes::arg::fn::QMessageBox::Yes::QMessageBox::Default::QMessageBox::No::QMessageBox::Cancel::QMessageBox::Escape::ret::QMessageBox::Yes::writeFile::filename::ret::QMessageBox::Cancel::false::true
