#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/project/config.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:4 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:13 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:1681 L_END:1686 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:hasInterface NONLCALS:2 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:4 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
generate
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	CMarkup xml_gen;
	QString s_gen;
	int i =0;
	QErrorMessage *errorMessageDialog = new QErrorMessage(this);
	bool errorFound=false;

	CCodeDocGen genAll ;
	
	s_gen = filename();  
	QStringList errors;

	if(s_gen.size()!=0)
	{ 
		QFileInfo ProFileName(s_gen);
		QDir genDir = ProFileName.absoluteDir();
		genDir.cdUp();
		genDir.cdUp();
		QString message;
		message =" All Files generated correctly in "+genDir.absolutePath();
	 
  
		if ( !xml_gen.load(s_gen) )
		{ 
			QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "XML document error.");
		 }

		xml_gen.findElem();
		xml_gen.intoElem();
		

		xml_gen.findElem("SYSTEM");
		genAll.gen(xml_gen, s_gen);

		errors = genAll.getFileErrors();
		
		if(errors.size()!=0)
		{ 	
			message +='\n';
			message +='\n';
			message += "Except those depending on";
			
			message +='\n';
			message +="Files";
			message +='\n';
			errorFound = true;

			for(i = 0; i<errors.size();i++)
			{ 
				
				message +=errors[i];
				message +='\n';
				
			
			 }
		 }
		errors = genAll.getFolderErrors();
		
		if(errors.size()!=0)
		{ 
			if (!errorFound)
			{ 
				message +='\n';
				message +='\n';
				message += "Except those depending on";
				errorFound = true;
			 }
			
			message +='\n';
			message +="Folders";
			message +='\n';

			for(i = 0; i<errors.size();i++)
			{ 
				
				message +=errors[i];
				message +='\n';
				
			
			 }
		 }

		errors = genAll.getProgramErrors();
		
		if(errors.size()!=0)
		{ 
			if (!errorFound)
			{ 
				message +='\n';
				message +='\n';
				message += "Except those depending on";
				errorFound = true;
			 }

			message +='\n';
			message +="Programs";
			message +='\n';

			for(i = 0; i<errors.size();i++)
			{ 
				
				message +=errors[i];
				message +='\n';
				
			
			 }
		 }

		QMessageBox mb("Generation Completed",message,
							QMessageBox::NoIcon,
							QMessageBox::NoButton,
							QMessageBox::Ok,
							QMessageBox::NoButton);
		mb.setModal(false);
			mb.exec();
	 }

 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:2 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:0 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:0 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/project/configcmd.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:4 LOCALS:10 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:73 L_END:76 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:CConfigCmd NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
redo
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int graphicItemType;
	QTreeWidgetItem* item;
	CGraphicProperties* graphicProp = CGraphicProperties::getInstance();



	item = mParent->child(mIndex);
	if(item == mItem)
	{ 
		mParent->takeChild(mIndex);
	 }
	mParent->insertChild(mIndex, mItem);



	if(mItem->type() == ConfigUserValue)
	{ 

		graphicProp->updateDisplay(graphicProp->getSelectedItem());
	 }
	else
	{ 

		mItem->treeWidget()->setCurrentItem(mItem);


		mGraphicDesign->updateComponents();

		mGraphicItem->show();
		graphicItemType = mGraphicItem->getTypeElement();
		if(mGraphicDesign->getMainWindow()->getContext() == "Context: System")
		{ 
			if( graphicItemType == gInterface ||
				graphicItemType == gParamTbl ||
				graphicItemType == gProcessor ||
				graphicItemType == gCOTS)
			{ 
				mGraphicItem->hide();
			 }
		 }
		else if(mGraphicDesign->getMainWindow()->getContext() == "Context: System->LRU")
		{ 
			if(graphicItemType == gLRU)
			{ 
				mGraphicItem->hide();
			 }
		 }
		mGraphicDesign->getList()->append(mGraphicItem);

		for(int i=0; i<mGraphicDesign->getList()->size(); i++)
			if (mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i)->isSelected())
				graphicProp->updateDisplay(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i));

		mGraphicDesign->update();
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:4 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:29 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:9 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:2 ENUM:0 EQTEST:9 EXPRORCALL:37 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/project/configcmd.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:7 IN:0 INDR:30 INLINE:0 INT:2 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:57 LOCALS:84 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:86 L_END:142 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:redo NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:18 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
undo
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	CGraphicProperties* graphicProp = CGraphicProperties::getInstance();
	QList<QTreeWidgetItem*> itemList;
	QTreeWidget* tree = mItem->treeWidget();


	itemList = mParent->takeChildren();
	itemList.removeAll(mItem);
	mParent->addChildren(itemList);


	if(mItem ->type() == ConfigUserValue)
	{ 

		graphicProp->updateDisplay(graphicProp->getSelectedItem());
	 }
	else
	{ 

		tree->setCurrentItem(mParent);


		if (mGraphicItem->getTypeElement() == gLRU)
			mGraphicDesign->updateContext("Context: System");


		mGraphicDesign->updateComponents();

		mGraphicItem->hide();
		mGraphicItem->setSelected(false);
		mGraphicDesign->getList()->removeAll(mGraphicItem);

		for(int i=0; i<mGraphicDesign->getList()->size(); i++)
		{ 
			if (mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i)->isSelected())
			{ 
				graphicProp->updateDisplay(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i));
				break;
			 }
		 }
		if (i == mGraphicDesign->getList()->size())
			for(int j=0; j<mGraphicDesign->getList()->size(); j++)
				if (mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(j)->getProperties() == mGraphicItem->getParentItem())
					graphicProp->updateDisplay(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(j));

		mGraphicDesign->update();
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:3 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:1 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:1 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:1 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/project/configcmd.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:12 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:295 L_END:300 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:CConfigCmd NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:4 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
redo
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QList<QTreeWidgetItem*> itemList;
	CGraphicProperties* graphicProp = CGraphicProperties::getInstance();
	QTreeWidget* tree = mItem->treeWidget();


	itemList = mParent->takeChildren();
	itemList.removeAll(mItem);
	mParent->addChildren(itemList);


	if(mItem->type() == ConfigUserValue)
	{ 

		graphicProp->updateDisplay(graphicProp->getSelectedItem());
	 }
	else
	{ 

		tree->setCurrentItem(mParent);


		mGraphicDesign->updateComponents();


		mGraphicItem->hide();
		mGraphicItem->setSelected(false);
		mGraphicDesign->getList()->removeAll(mGraphicItem);


		QPoint childPos(mGraphicItem->pos().x() + mGraphicItem->width() , 
			mGraphicItem->pos().y() + mGraphicItem->height() );
		bool Found = false;
		for(int i=0; i<mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->size(); i++)
		{ 
			if (mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->posStart() == childPos)
			{ 
				mHierarchicalDesign->slotDeleteMessage(mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->getElemStart()->getProperties(), 
					mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->getElemEnd()->getProperties()->text(1), 
					mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->getName());
				listMsg.append(mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->takeAt(i));
				i = -1;
			 }
			else if (mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->posEnd() == childPos)
			{ 
				for(int j=0; j<mGraphicDesign->getList()->size(); j++)
					if ((mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(j)->getProperties() != mGraphicItem->getProperties()) &&
						(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(j)->getProperties()->text(1) == mGraphicItem->getProperties()->text(1)) &&
						(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(j)->getParentItem() == mGraphicItem->getParentItem()))
						Found = true;
				if (Found == false)
				{ 
					mHierarchicalDesign->slotDeleteMessage(mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->getElemStart()->getProperties(), 
						mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->getElemEnd()->getProperties()->text(1), 
						mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->getName());
					listMsg.append(mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->takeAt(i));
					i = -1;
				 }
				Found = false;
			 }
		 }

		for(int i=0; i<mGraphicDesign->getList()->size(); i++)
		{ 
			if (mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i)->isSelected())
			{ 
				graphicProp->updateDisplay(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i));
				break;
			 }
		 }
		if (i == mGraphicDesign->getList()->size())
			for(int j=0; j<mGraphicDesign->getList()->size(); j++)
				if (mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(j)->getProperties() == mGraphicItem->getParentItem())
					graphicProp->updateDisplay(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(j));

		mGraphicDesign->update();
	 }

 }
__END_BODY__

ign::update

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:13 AUTO:0 BREAK:1 CALLS:97 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:13 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:5 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:2 ENUM:0 EQTEST:8 EXPRORCALL:112 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/project/configcmd.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:4 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:8 IN:0 INDR:91 INLINE:0 INT:4 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:79 LOCALS:112 LONG:0 LT:5 L_BEGIN:310 L_END:388 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:redo NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:4 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:34 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0

undo

()

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int graphicItemType;
	CGraphicProperties* graphicProp = CGraphicProperties::getInstance();


	mParent->insertChild(mIndex, mItem);


	if(mItem->type() == ConfigUserValue)
	{ 

		graphicProp->updateDisplay(graphicProp->getSelectedItem());
	 }
	else
	{ 

		mItem->treeWidget()->setCurrentItem(mItem);


		mGraphicDesign->updateComponents();

		mGraphicItem->show();
		graphicItemType = mGraphicItem->getTypeElement();
		if(mGraphicDesign->getMainWindow()->getContext() == "Context: System")
		{ 
			if( graphicItemType == gInterface ||
				graphicItemType == gParamTbl ||
				graphicItemType == gProcessor ||
				graphicItemType == gCOTS)
			{ 
				mGraphicItem->hide();
			 }
		 }
		else if(mGraphicDesign->getMainWindow()->getContext() == "Context: System->LRU")
		{ 
			if(graphicItemType == gLRU)
				mGraphicItem->hide();
		 }


		for(int i=0; i<listMsg.size(); i++)
		{ 
			mHierarchicalDesign->slotAddMessage(listMsg.at(i)->getElemEnd()->getProperties()->text(1), 
				listMsg.at(i), listMsg.at(i)->getElemStart()->getProperties());
			mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->append(listMsg.at(i));
		 }

		mGraphicDesign->getList()->append(mGraphicItem);
		for(int i=0; i<mGraphicDesign->getList()->size(); i++)
			if (mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i)->isSelected())
				CGraphicProperties::getInstance()->updateDisplay(mGraphicDesign->getList()->at(i));
		mGraphicDesign->update();
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

{ 
	mGraphicItem->move(mNewPos);


	QPoint oldPosMsg(mOldPos.x() + mGraphicItem->width() , mOldPos.y() + mGraphicItem->height() );
	for(int i=0; i<mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->size(); i++)
	{ 
		if (oldPosMsg == mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->posStart())
			mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->setPosStart(mNewPos, mGraphicItem->width(), mGraphicItem->height());
		else if (oldPosMsg == mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->posEnd())
			mGraphicDesign->getMsgList()->at(i)->setPosEnd(mNewPos, mGraphicItem->width(), mGraphicItem->height());
	 }

	mGraphicDesign->update();
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
CBasePropertyItem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(text, PropBool, parentWidget, row, col)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int index = -1;

	setFlags(Qt::ItemIsSelectable);
	mParentWidget->setItem(mRow, mCol, this);
	mComboBox = new QComboBox(parentWidget);


	mComboBox->insertItem("TRUE");
    mComboBox->insertItem("FALSE");


	index = mComboBox->findText(text, Qt::MatchExactly);
	if(index >=0)
	{ 
		mComboBox->setCurrentIndex(index);
	 }
	mParentWidget->setCellWidget(mRow, mCol, mComboBox);


	connect(mComboBox, SIGNAL(currentIndexChanged(int)), this, SLOT(slotTellTable()));
	connect(this, SIGNAL(comboModified(int, int)), mParentWidget, SIGNAL(cellChanged(int, int)));
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:0 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:1 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Model/CPropertyItem.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:2 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:306 L_END:308 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:getText NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:1 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
CBasePropertyItem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(text, PropFile, parentWidget, row, col)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	setFlags(Qt::ItemIsEditable);
	mParentWidget->setItem(row, col, this);


	mTable = new QTableWidget(1, 2, mParentWidget);
	mTable->horizontalHeader()->hide();
	mTable->verticalHeader()->hide();
	mTable->setRowHeight(0, mParentWidget->rowHeight(row)-3);
	mTable->setColumnWidth(0, (mParentWidget->columnWidth(col) - mParentWidget->rowHeight(row))-2);
	mTable->setColumnWidth(1, mParentWidget->rowHeight(row));
	mTable->setAutoScroll(false);
	mTable->setVerticalScrollBarPolicy(Qt::ScrollBarAlwaysOff);
	mTable->setHorizontalScrollBarPolicy(Qt::ScrollBarAlwaysOff);



	mTableItem = new QTableWidgetItem(text, PropString);
	mTableItem->setFlags(Qt::ItemIsEditable);
	mTable->setItem(0,0, mTableItem);


	mPushButton = new QPushButton(QString::QString("..."), mTable);
	mPushButton->setFixedWidth(mTable->columnWidth(1));
	mPushButton->setFixedHeight(mTable->rowHeight(0));
	mTable->setCellWidget(0, 1, mPushButton);

	mParentWidget->setCellWidget(mRow, mCol, mTable);



	connect(mTable, SIGNAL(cellChanged(int, int)), this, SLOT(slotTellTable(int, int)));
	connect(this, SIGNAL(tableModified(int, int)), mParentWidget, SIGNAL(cellChanged(int, int)));


	connect(mPushButton, SIGNAL(released()), this, SLOT(slotSelectFile()));
 }
__END_BODY__

QWidget

__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	sorte = sorteElem;
	imageEnabled = new QPixmap(*Image);
	imageNotEnabled = new QPixmap(*Image);
	image = imageEnabled;
	clrBoite = Qt::white;
	element = 0;
	setMinimumSize(image->width()+20, image->height()+20);
	setMaximumSize(image->width()+20, image->height()+20);


	QPainter painter;
    painter.begin(imageNotEnabled);
    painter.fillRect(Image->rect(), QColor(127, 127, 127, 127));
    painter.end();


	if (sorteElem == gLRU)
		txtType = "LRU";
	else if (sorteElem == gInterface)
		txtType = "Interface";
	else if (sorteElem == gParamTbl)
		txtType = "Param Table";
	else if (sorteElem == gProcessor)
		txtType = "Processor";
	else if (sorteElem == gCOTS)
		txtType = "COTS";
 }

		txtName = elem->child(0)->text(2);

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
paintEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPaintEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QString tmpName = txtName;
	QString tmpType = txtType;
	if (txtName.length() > 15)
		tmpName = txtName.mid(0, 12) + "...";
	if (txtType.length() > 15)
		tmpType = txtType.mid(0, 12) + "...";
	QPainter p;
	p.begin(this);
	p.drawPixmap( 0, 0, *image );
	p.setFont(QFont("Arial", 7));
	p.drawText(5, this->height()-11, tmpName);
	p.drawText(5, this->height()-2, tmpType);
	p.setPen( clrBoite );
	p.drawRect( 0, 0, image->width()-1, image->height()-1 );
	p.end();
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
addCots
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString selectedCots, QTreeWidgetItem *selected, QTreeWidgetItem *last, CConfigCots *component)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	QString cname = selectedCots;
	
	CConfigCots *cots = component;
	cots->setText(1, cname);

    CConfigValue *value = 0;
	value = new CConfigValue(cots, 0);
    value->setText(0, "Name");
    value->setText(1, "string");
    value->setText(2, "theCOTS");

    value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
    value->setText(0, "Band");
    value->setText(1, "band");
    value->setText(2, "UNLINK");



	if ( cname == "acs_PowerSupply" )
	{ 

    value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
    value->setText(0, "Public");
    value->setText(1, "bool");
    value->setText(2, "FALSE");

    value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
    value->setText(0, "Long Term Power Off");
    value->setText(1, "double");
    value->setText(2, "3.0");

    value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
    value->setText(0, "Power Up Delay");
    value->setText(1, "double");
    value->setText(2, "5.0");

    value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
    value->setText(0, "Glitch Isolation");
    value->setText(1, "double");
    value->setText(2, "1.0");

    value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
    value->setText(0, "CB Name");
    value->setText(1, "string");
    value->setText(2, "");


	 }
	else
	{ 
		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Public");
		value->setText(1, "bool");
		value->setText(2, "TRUE");

		if ( cname == "acs_WidgetDriver" )
		{ 
		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Part Number");
		value->setText(1, "string");
		value->setText(2, "");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Link Type");
		value->setText(1, "string");
		value->setText(2, "acs_LinkResolver");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Link File");
		value->setText(1, "file");
		value->setText(2, "link.xml");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Run-Time File");
		value->setText(1, "file");
		value->setText(2, "ua.wgd");
		 }
		else if ( cname == "acs_ProtocolEmulator" )
		{ 
		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Arinc 702 Used");
		value->setText(1, "bool");
		value->setText(2, "FALSE");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Arinc 739 Used");
		value->setText(1, "bool");
		value->setText(2, "FALSE");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Arinc 740 Used");
		value->setText(1, "bool");
		value->setText(2, "FALSE");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Williamsburg Used");
		value->setText(1, "bool");
		value->setText(2, "FALSE");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Dual CDU Driver Enabled");
		value->setText(1, "bool");
		value->setText(2, "FALSE");
		 }
		else if ( cname == "acs_TextControlDriver" )
		{ 
		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Cross-Side Info");
		value->setText(1, "xside");
		value->setText(2, "ONSIDE");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Pages Definition File");
		value->setText(1, "file");
		value->setText(2, "page.xml");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Number of Lines");
		value->setText(1, "int");
		value->setText(2, "8");

		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Number of Columns");
		value->setText(1, "int");
		value->setText(2, "24");
		 }
		else if ( cname == "acs_CautionsAdvisoriesManager" )
		{ 
		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Advisories Definition File");
		value->setText(1, "file");
		value->setText(2, "page.xml");
		 }
		else if ( cname == "acs_GraphicController" )
		{ 
		value = new CConfigValue(cots, value);
		value->setText(0, "Adapter");
		value->setText(1, "string");
		value->setText(2, "acs_RaveAdapter");
		 }
	

	 }




 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
QWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	elemStart = start;
	elemEnd = end;

	ptStart.setX(start->pos().x() + start->width() );
	ptStart.setY(start->pos().y() + start->height() );
	ptEnd.setX(end->pos().x() + end->width() );
	ptEnd.setY(end->pos().y() + end->height() );

	propName = "";
	propId = -1;
	propType = "";
	propPeriodicity = -1;
	propFilter = false;
 }

slotUpdateDialog

__BEGIN_SIG__
(int state)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 							

	if(state == Qt::Checked)
	{ 
		typeEdit->setEnabled(false);
		custTypeEdit->setEnabled(true);

	 }
	else if(state == Qt::Unchecked)
	{ 
		custTypeEdit->setEnabled(false);
		typeEdit->setEnabled(true);
	 }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotUpdateOkButton
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	bool activateButton = false;

	if(!nameEdit->text().isEmpty() &&
		!valueEdit->text().isEmpty())
	{ 

		if(custTypeChk->checkState() == Qt::Checked)
		{ 

			if(!custTypeEdit->text().isEmpty())
			{ 
				activateButton = true;
			 }
			else
			{ 
				activateButton = false;
			 }
		 }
		else
		{ 
				activateButton = true;
		 }

	 }

	addButton->setEnabled(activateButton);
 }
__END_BODY__

(int state)

	if (!txtName->text().isEmpty() && !txtId->text().isEmpty())
	{ 
		if (((state == 0) && !txtPeriodicity->text().isEmpty()) || (state > 0))
		{ 
			okButton->setEnabled(true);

	 }
	okButton->setEnabled(false);
 }

QFrame

(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	setObjectName("theCDesign");
	setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_16.png"));
	setMinimumSize(200, 200);



	mMainWindow = mw;
	mGraphicProperties = gp;
	mHierarchy = tree;
	itemTemp = 0;
	itemParent = mHierarchy->topLevelItem(0);
	mode = Normal;
	startLine = 0;

	setFrameStyle(QFrame::Sunken | QFrame::StyledPanel);
	setAcceptDrops(true);




	mLineEnterAct = new QAction(tr("Enter the message mode"), this);
	mLineEnterAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage ink_add_24.png"));
	mLineEnterAct->setStatusTip(tr("View, add and delete messages"));
	connect(mLineEnterAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEnterMsgMode()));

	mLineExitAct = new QAction(tr("Exit the message mode"), this);
	mLineExitAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage ink_delete_24.png"));
	mLineExitAct->setStatusTip(tr("Hides all the messages"));
	connect(mLineExitAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotExitMsgMode()));

	mLineAct = new QAction(tr("Add a &message"), this);
	mLineAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+L"));
	mLineAct->setStatusTip(tr("Add a message"));
	connect(mLineAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotLine()));

	mLineDelAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete a message"), this);
	mLineDelAct->setStatusTip(tr("Delete a message"));
	connect(mLineDelAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDeleteLine()));
	
	mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
	mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
	mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
	mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
	connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDelete()));

	addElement(gSystem, itemParent, NULL, QPoint(20,20));




	connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mMainWindow, SLOT(slotUpdateModIndicator()));
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
addElement
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(typeElement typeElem, QTreeWidgetItem *item, QTreeWidgetItem *parent, QPoint position)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	CGraphicElement *element = NULL;


	int nb = 0;
	if ((position.x() == 0) && (position.y() == 0))
		for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
			if (list.at(i)->pos() == position)
			{ 
				if ((list.at(i)->pos().x() + 50) < this->width())
					position.rx() += 50;
				else if ((list.at(i)->pos().y() + 50) < this->height())
				{ 
					position.setX(0);
					position.ry() += 50;
				 }
				else
				{ 
					nb++;
					position.setX(nb);
					position.setY(nb);
				 }
				i = -1;
			 }


	if (typeElem == gSystem)
	{ 
		CGraphicElement *icnSystem = new CGraphicElement(gSystem, new QPixmap(": mage ocument_gear_48.png"), this);
		icnSystem->move(position);
		icnSystem->setToolTip("System");
		icnSystem->hide();
		icnSystem->setAttribute(Qt::WA_DeleteOnClose);
		icnSystem->setProperties(item);
		icnSystem->setParentItem(parent);
		list.append(icnSystem);
		element = icnSystem;
	 }

	else if (typeElem == gLRU)
	{ 
		CGraphicElement *icnLRU = new CGraphicElement(gLRU, new QPixmap(": mage ocument_gear_48.png"), this);
		icnLRU->move(position);
		icnLRU->setToolTip("LRU");
		icnLRU->setAttribute(Qt::WA_DeleteOnClose);
		icnLRU->setProperties(item);
		icnLRU->setParentItem(parent);
		element = icnLRU;
	 }

	else if (typeElem == gInterface)
	{ 
		CGraphicElement *icnInterface = new CGraphicElement(gInterface, new QPixmap(": mage ocument_plain_48.png"), this);
		icnInterface->move(position);
		icnInterface->setToolTip("Interface");
		icnInterface->setAttribute(Qt::WA_DeleteOnClose);
		icnInterface->setProperties(item);
		icnInterface->setParentItem(parent);
		element = icnInterface;
	 }

	else if (typeElem == gParamTbl)
	{ 
		CGraphicElement *icnParamTbl = new CGraphicElement(gParamTbl, new QPixmap(": mage ocument_table_48.png"), this);
		icnParamTbl->move(position);
		icnParamTbl->setToolTip("Parameters Table");
		icnParamTbl->setAttribute(Qt::WA_DeleteOnClose);
		icnParamTbl->setProperties(item);
		icnParamTbl->setParentItem(parent);
		element = icnParamTbl;
	 }

	else if (typeElem == gProcessor)
	{ 
		CGraphicElement *icnProcessor = new CGraphicElement(gProcessor, new QPixmap(": mage ocument_48.png"), this);
		icnProcessor->move(position);
		icnProcessor->setToolTip("Processor");
		icnProcessor->setAttribute(Qt::WA_DeleteOnClose);
		icnProcessor->setProperties(item);
		icnProcessor->setParentItem(parent);
		element = icnProcessor;
	 }

	else if (typeElem == gCOTS)
	{ 
		CGraphicElement *icnCots = new CGraphicElement(gCOTS, new QPixmap(": mage nformation_48.png"), this);
		icnCots->move(position);
		icnCots->setToolTip("COTS");
		icnCots->setAttribute(Qt::WA_DeleteOnClose);
		icnCots->setProperties(item);
		icnCots->setParentItem(parent);
		element = icnCots;
	 }

	return element;
 }

{ 
	QList<CGraphicElement *>::iterator listIt;
	CGraphicElement* graphicItem = NULL;

	for(listIt = list.begin(); listIt != list.end(); listIt++)
	{ 
		if((*listIt)->getProperties() == treeItem)

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:4 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:3 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:6 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicDesign.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:2 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:13 LOCALS:32 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:245 L_END:257 MAXNEST:3 MMINUS:0 NAME:getGraphicElement NONLCALS:1 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:1 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:6 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
dropEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDropEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	if (event->mimeData()->hasFormat("applicatio -dnditemdata")) { 
        QByteArray itemData = event->mimeData()->data("applicatio -dnditemdata");
        QDataStream dataStream(&itemData, QIODevice::ReadOnly);


		QString type;
		QPixmap image;
		QPoint offset;
		dataStream >> type >> image >> offset;


		QPoint posMouse = event->pos() - offset;
		QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> listTreeItems;

		if(itemTemp == 0)
		{ 
			if (type.compare("LRU") == 0)
			{ 
				mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(mHierarchy->topLevelItem(0));
				bool Rep = mHierarchy->slotAddLRU();
				if (Rep == false)
					return;
				listTreeItems = mHierarchy->selectedItems();
				list.last()->move(posMouse);
			 }
			else if (type.compare("Processor") == 0)
			{ 
				mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(itemParent);
				mHierarchy->slotAddProcess();
				listTreeItems = mHierarchy->selectedItems();
				list.last()->move(posMouse);
			 }
			else if (type.compare("Interface") == 0)
			{ 
				mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(itemParent);
				mHierarchy->slotAddInterface();
				listTreeItems = mHierarchy->selectedItems();
				list.last()->move(posMouse);
			 }
			else if (type.compare("Parameters Table") == 0)
			{ 
				mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(itemParent);
				mHierarchy->slotAddParamTbl();
				listTreeItems = mHierarchy->selectedItems();
				list.last()->move(posMouse);

			 }
			else if (type.compare("COTS") == 0)
			{ 
				mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(itemParent);
				bool rep = mHierarchy->slotAddCots();
				if(rep == false)
					return;

				listTreeItems = mHierarchy->selectedItems();
				list.last()->move(posMouse);
			 }

			for(int i=0; i<list.size()-1; i++)
			{ 
				list.at(i)->setColor(Qt::white);
				list.at(i)->setSelected(false);
			 }
			list.last()->setColor(Qt::black);
			list.last()->setSelected(true);
			mGraphicProperties->updateDisplay(list.last());
			mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(list.last()->getProperties());
		 }
		else
		{ 
			mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdMove("move project item", itemTemp->getProperties(),	itemTemp, this, itemTemp->pos(), posMouse));
			itemTemp = 0;
		 }

		setMinWindowSize();
		update();
		

		updateComponents();
		
        if (event->source() == this) { 
            event->setDropAction(Qt::MoveAction);
            event->accept();
         } else { 
            event->acceptProposedAction();
         }
		emit modified();
     } else { 
        event->ignore();
     }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

mousePressEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QMouseEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	CGraphicElement *child = static_cast<CGraphicElement*>(childAt(event->pos()));
	

	if (!child)
	{ 

		mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(itemParent);
		if (mMainWindow->getContext().compare("Context: System") == 0)
			mGraphicProperties->updateDisplay(list.at(0));
		else
			for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
				if (list.at(i)->getProperties() == itemParent)
					mGraphicProperties->updateDisplay(list.at(i));
	 }
	
	for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
	{ 

		if (child == list.at(i))
		{ 

			list.at(i)->setSelected(true);
			mGraphicProperties->updateDisplay(child);
			mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(list.at(i)->getProperties());
		 }
		else
		{ 

			list.at(i)->setSelected(false);
		 }
	 }


	if ((mode == Message) && (event->button() == Qt::LeftButton) && (startLine != 0))
	{ 

		if ((!child) || (child->getTypeElement() != gProcessor))
		{ 
			if (startLine != 0)
				startLine = 0;
		 }

		else
		{ 
			QString typeProcess = child->getProperties()->text(1);
			CAddMsgDialog dialog(this);
			if (dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted)
			{ 
				bool Found = false;
				for(int i=0; i<listMsg.size(); i++)
					if ((listMsg.at(i)->getID() == dialog.txtId->text().toInt()) &&
						(listMsg.at(i)->getTypeMsg() == dialog.boxType->currentText()) &&
						(listMsg.at(i)->getName() == dialog.txtName->text().ascii()) &&
						(startLine == listMsg.at(i)->getElemStart()))
						Found = true;
				if (Found == false)
				{ 

					CGraphicMessage *msg = new CGraphicMessage(startLine, child, this);
					msg->setName(dialog.txtName->text());
					msg->setID(dialog.txtId->text().toInt());
					msg->setTypeMsg(dialog.boxType->currentText());
					msg->setPeriodicity(dialog.txtPeriodicity->text().toInt());
					if (dialog.chboxFilter->isChecked())
						msg->setFilter(true);
					else
						msg->setFilter(false);

					mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdAddMsg("add a message", startLine->getProperties(), 
						msg, this, mHierarchy, typeProcess));
					emit modified();
				 }
				else
					QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error!", "This message already exists.  It has not been added", 
						QMessageBox::Ok, QMessageBox::NoButton);
			 }

			startLine = 0;
			update();
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

		CGraphicComponents::getInstance()->setComponentsEnabled(mMainWindow->getContext(),

	else

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
updateContext
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString context, CGraphicElement *elem)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	if (context == "Context: System")
	{ 

		if (mMainWindow->getContext().compare("Context: System->LRU") == 0)
		{ 
			if (mode == Message)
				mMainWindow->slotMsgMode();
			itemParent = mHierarchy->topLevelItem(0);
			mMainWindow->setContext("Context: System");
			mGraphicProperties->updateDisplay(list.at(0));
			updateComponents();
		 }
	 }
	else
	{ 

		if (mMainWindow->getContext().compare("Context: System") == 0)
		{ 
			itemParent = elem->getProperties();
			mMainWindow->setContext("Context: System->LRU");

			for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
			{ 
				if (list.at(i) == elem)
				{ 
					mGraphicProperties->updateDisplay(list.at(i));
					updateComponents();
				 }
			 }
		 }
	 }


	for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
	{ 
		if (list.at(i)->getParentItem() == itemParent)
			list.at(i)->show();
		else
			list.at(i)->hide();
	 }
	update();
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
updateSelection
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> listElem = mHierarchy->selectedItems();
	for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
	{ 
		if (list.at(i)->getProperties() == listElem.at(0))
		{ 
			if ((list.at(i)->getTypeElement() == gSystem) || (list.at(i)->getTypeElement() == gLRU))
				updateContext("Context: System", list.at(i));
			else
			{ 
				for(int j=0; j<list.size(); j++)
					if (list.at(j)->getProperties() == list.at(i)->getParentItem())
						updateContext("Context: System->LRU", list.at(j));
			 }
			list.at(i)->setSelected(true);
			CGraphicProperties::getInstance()->updateDisplay(list.at(i));
		 }
		else
			list.at(i)->setSelected(false);
	 }
	update();
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
mouseMoveEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QMouseEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	CGraphicElement *child = static_cast<CGraphicElement*>(childAt(event->pos()));
    if (!child)
        return;


	QPixmap Image = child->pixmap();


	QByteArray itemData;
    QDataStream dataStream(&itemData, QIODevice::WriteOnly);
	dataStream << child->toolTip() << Image << QPoint(event->pos() - child->pos());
	itemTemp = child;

    QMimeData *mimeData = new QMimeData;
    mimeData->setData("applicatio -dnditemdata", itemData);


	QDrag *drag = new QDrag(this);
    drag->setMimeData(mimeData);
    drag->setPixmap(Image);
    drag->setHotSpot(event->pos() - child->pos());

	drag->start(Qt::MoveAction | Qt::CopyAction);
 }
__END_BODY__

setMinWindowSize

__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	int wx=200;
	int hy=200;
	for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
	{ 
		if (list.at(i)->pos().x() > wx)
			wx = list.at(i)->pos().x() + list.at(i)->width();
		if (list.at(i)->pos().y() > hy)
			hy = list.at(i)->pos().y() + list.at(i)->height();
	 }
	setMinimumSize(wx, hy);
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:5 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:18 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:11 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:21 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicDesign.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:1 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:7 INLINE:0 INT:3 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:14 LOCALS:29 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:651 L_END:664 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:setMinWindowSize NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:7 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
paintEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QPaintEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QFrame::paintEvent(event);

	if (mode == Normal)
		return;

	int xStart, xEnd, yStart, yEnd;

	for(int i=0; i<listMsg.size(); i++)
	{ 
		for(int j=0; j<list.size(); j++)
		{ 
			if ((listMsg.at(i)->getElemEnd()->getProperties()->text(1) == list.at(j)->getProperties()->text(1)) && 
				(listMsg.at(i)->getElemStart() != list.at(j)) && 
				(listMsg.at(i)->getElemEnd()->getParentItem() == list.at(j)->getParentItem()) &&
				(listMsg.at(i)->getElemEnd()->getParentItem() == itemParent) &&
				(mMainWindow->getContext() == "Context: System->LRU"))
			{ 
				xStart = listMsg.at(i)->posStart().x();
				xEnd = list.at(j)->pos().x() + list.at(j)->width() ;
				yStart = listMsg.at(i)->posStart().y();
				yEnd = list.at(j)->pos().y() + list.at(j)->height() ;


				QPainter painter(this);
				painter.setPen(QPen(Qt::black, 2));
				painter.drawLine(QLine(listMsg.at(i)->posStart(), QPoint(xEnd, yEnd)));


				painter.save();
				painter.translate((xEnd-xStart)*0.5+xStart, (yEnd-yStart)*0.5+yStart);
				double angle = atan2((double)(yEnd-yStart), (double)(xEnd-xStart))/(2*3.1416)*360;
				painter.rotate(angle);
				QPoint pts[3] = {  QPoint(0, 10), QPoint(0, -10), QPoint(10, 0)  };
				painter.drawPolygon(pts, 3);
				painter.restore();
			 }
		 }
	 }

 }
__END_BODY__

		event->accept();
	else
		event->ignore();
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotDeleteLine
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int i = 0;
	for(i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
		if (list.at(i)->isSelected())
			break;


	QList<CGraphicMessage*> listTmp;
	QPoint childPos(list.at(i)->pos().x() + list.at(i)->width() , list.at(i)->pos().y() + list.at(i)->height() );
	for(int j=0; j<listMsg.size(); j++)
		if (listMsg.at(j)->posStart() == childPos)
			listTmp.append(listMsg.at(j));


	QStringList listMsgDel;
	QString rep;
	bool ok;
	for(int j=0; j<listTmp.size(); j++)
	{ 
		rep = listTmp.at(j)->getTypeMsg();
		rep.append(" : ");
		rep.append(listTmp.at(j)->getName());
		listMsgDel << rep;
	 }
	rep = QInputDialog::getItem(this, "Delete a message", "Select the message to be deleted", listMsgDel, 0, false, &ok);
	

	if (ok && !rep.isEmpty())
	{ 
		listMsgDel = rep.split(" : ");
		for(int j=0; j<listMsg.size(); j++)
		{ 
			if ((listMsg.at(j)->getTypeMsg() == listMsgDel.at(0).ascii()) && 
				(listMsg.at(j)->getName() == listMsgDel.at(1).ascii()))
			{ 

				mCmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdDelMsg("delete a message", list.at(i)->getProperties(), 
					listMsg.at(j), this, mHierarchy));
				emit modified();
				break;
			 }
		 }
	 }
	CGraphicProperties::getInstance()->updateDisplay(list.at(i));
	update();
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:2 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicDesign.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:2 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:888 L_END:893 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:editDelete NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
printComponents
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QPrinter printer;
	QPrintDialog printDialog(&printer, this);
	printer.setDocName("ACS Design");


	double ratioWidth, ratioHeight;
	if (width() > printer.pageRect().width())
	{ 
		ratioWidth = (double)printer.pageRect().width() / (double)this->width();
		ratioHeight = (double)printer.pageRect().height() / (double)this->height();
	 }
	else
	{ 
		ratioWidth = 1.0;
		ratioHeight = 1.0;
	 }
	int noPage = 1;

	if (printDialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted)
	{ 

		QPainter painter(&printer);
		painter.setViewport(printer.pageRect());
		painter.setWindow(printer.pageRect());
		painter.setPen(QPen(Qt::black, 1));

		for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
		{ 
			if (list.at(i)->getTypeElement() == gLRU)
			{ 
				if (noPage > 1)
					printer.newPage();

				painter.drawText(40, 40, QString("LRU - %1").arg(list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(0)->text(2)));
				for(int j=0; j<list.size(); j++)
				{ 
					if (list.at(j)->getParentItem() == list.at(i)->getProperties())
					{ 

						painter.drawRect(ratioWidth*list.at(j)->x(), ratioHeight*list.at(j)->y(), 48, 48);
						painter.drawText(ratioWidth*list.at(j)->x(), ratioHeight*list.at(j)->y()+60, 
							QString("%1").arg(list.at(j)->getProperties()->text(0)));
						painter.drawText(ratioWidth*list.at(j)->x(), ratioHeight*list.at(j)->y()+70, 
							QString("%1").arg(list.at(j)->getProperties()->text(1)));
					 }
				 }


				for(int k=0; k<listMsg.size(); k++)
				{ 
					for(int j=0; j<list.size(); j++)
					{ 
						if ((listMsg.at(k)->getElemEnd()->getProperties()->text(1) == list.at(j)->getProperties()->text(1)) && 
							(listMsg.at(k)->getElemStart() != list.at(j)) && 
							(listMsg.at(k)->getElemEnd()->getParentItem() == list.at(j)->getParentItem()) &&
							(listMsg.at(k)->getElemEnd()->getParentItem() == list.at(i)->getProperties()))
						{ 
							double xStart = listMsg.at(k)->posStart().x()*ratioWidth;
							double xEnd = (list.at(j)->pos().x() + list.at(j)->width() )*ratioWidth;
							double yStart = listMsg.at(k)->posStart().y()*ratioHeight;
							double yEnd = (list.at(j)->pos().y() + list.at(j)->height() )*ratioHeight;
							painter.setPen(QPen(Qt::black, 2));
							painter.drawLine(xStart, yStart, xEnd, yEnd);
							painter.setPen(QPen(Qt::black, 1));


							painter.save();
							painter.translate((xEnd-xStart)*0.5+xStart, (yEnd-yStart)*0.5+yStart);
							double angle = atan2((double)(yEnd-yStart), (double)(xEnd-xStart))/(2*3.1416)*360;
							painter.rotate(angle);
							QPoint pts[3] = {  QPoint(0, 10), QPoint(0, -10), QPoint(10, 0)  };
							painter.drawPolygon(pts, 3);
							painter.restore();
						 }
					 }
				 }

				painter.drawText(40, printer.pageRect().height() - 40, QString("Page %1").arg(noPage++));
			 }
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

menu
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const Menu &item)

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	switch ( item )
	{ 
		case EditUndo :
			return mCmdStack->canUndo();
		case EditRedo :
			return mCmdStack->canRedo();
		case EditCut :
			return true;
		case EditCopy :
			return true;
		case EditPaste :
			return true;
		case EditDelete :
			return true;
		case EditFind :
			return false;
		default:
			return false;
	 }
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:7 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:10 DEFAULT:1 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicDesign.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:3 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:21 LOCALS:26 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:1031 L_END:1051 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:menu NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:8 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:8 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:1 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenuEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QContextMenuEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	bool Found = false;
	CGraphicElement *child = static_cast<CGraphicElement*>(childAt(event->pos()));
	if (child)
	{ 


		QPoint childPos(child->pos().x() + child->width() , child->pos().y() + child->height() );
		for(int i=0; i<listMsg.size(); i++)
			if (listMsg.at(i)->posStart() == childPos)
				Found = true;
	 }

	QMenu menu(this);
	if (mode == Normal)
	{ 
		if (!child)
		{ 
			if (mMainWindow->getContext() == "Context: System->LRU")
				menu.addAction(mLineEnterAct);
		 }
		else
			menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
	 }
	else
	{ 
		if (!child)
		{ 
			if (mMainWindow->getContext() == "Context: System->LRU")
				menu.addAction(mLineExitAct);
		 }
		else
		{ 

			if (child->getTypeElement() == gProcessor)
			{ 
				menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
				menu.addAction(mLineAct);
				if (Found)
					menu.addAction(mLineDelAct);
			 }
		 }
	 }
	menu.exec(event->globalPos());
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:1 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:4 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicDesign.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:3 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:4 LOCALS:10 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:1128 L_END:1131 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:removeProperties NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:3 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readProperty
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QTreeWidgetItem *item)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	typeElement sorte;
	CGraphicElement *elem;
	QStack<int> pile;


	list.clear();
	sorte = gSystem;
	mHierarchy->setCurrentItem(mHierarchy->topLevelItem(0));

	do
	{ 
		for(int i=0; i<item->childCount(); i++)
		{ 


			if (item->child(i)->childCount() > 0)
			{ 
				pile.push(i);
				item = item->child(i);
				i = 0;

				if (item->type() == ConfigSystem)
					sorte = gSystem;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigLRU)
					sorte = gLRU;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigInterface)
					sorte = gInterface;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigTable)
					sorte = gParamTbl;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigProcess)
					sorte = gProcessor;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigPowerSupply)
					sorte = gCOTS;
			 }



			if (item->child(i)->text(0) == "posX")
			{ 
				int posX = item->child(i)->text(2).toInt();
				int posY = item->child(i+1)->text(2).toInt();
				elem = addElement(sorte, item, item->parent(), QPoint(posX, posY));
				if (sorte == gSystem)
				{ 
					list.removeLast();
					list.prepend(elem);
				 }
				else
					list.append(elem);
				elem->hide();
				if (sorte == gLRU)
					elem->show();
			 }




			if ((i == item->childCount() - 1) && (pile.size() > 0))
			{ 
				i = pile.pop();
				item = item->parent();

				if (item->type() == ConfigSystem)
					sorte = gSystem;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigLRU)
					sorte = gLRU;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigInterface)
					sorte = gInterface;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigTable)
					sorte = gParamTbl;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigProcess)
					sorte = gProcessor;
				else if (item->type() == ConfigPowerSupply)
					sorte = gCOTS;
			 }
		 }
	 } while(pile.size() > 0);

	itemParent = list.first()->getProperties();



	for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
	{ 
		for(int j=0; j<list.at(i)->getProperties()->childCount(); j++)
		{ 
			if (list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(j)->text(0) == "msgTypeProc")
			{ 
				QString typeProcess = list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(j)->text(2);
				for(int k=0; k<list.size(); k++)
				{ 
					if ((list.at(k)->getProperties()->text(1) == typeProcess) && (i != k) &&
						(list.at(i)->getParentItem() == list.at(k)->getParentItem()))
					{ 
						CGraphicMessage *msg = new CGraphicMessage(list.at(i), list.at(k), this);
						msg->setName(list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(j+1)->text(2));
						msg->setID(list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(j+2)->text(2).toInt());
						msg->setTypeMsg(list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(j+3)->text(2));
						msg->setPeriodicity(list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(j+4)->text(2).toInt());
						if (list.at(i)->getProperties()->child(j+5)->text(2) == "1")
							msg->setFilter(true);
						else
							msg->setFilter(false);
						msg->hide();
						listMsg.append(msg);
						break;
					 }
				 }
			 }
		 }
	 }

	setMinWindowSize();
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:5 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:37 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:10 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:37 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicComponents.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:21 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:46 LOCALS:62 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:50 L_END:95 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:QFrame NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:7 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:32 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
setComponentsEnabled
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString Context, bool Interface, bool ParamTbl, bool Normal)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

	for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
		list.at(i)->setSelected(false);

	if (Normal == true)
	{ 
		if (Context.compare("Context: System") == 0)
		{ 

			icnLRU->setElemEnabled(true);
			icnProcessor->setElemEnabled(false);
			icnInterface->setElemEnabled(false);
			icnParamTbl->setElemEnabled(false);
			icnCots->setElemEnabled(false);
		 }
		else if (Context.compare("Context: System->LRU") == 0)
		{ 


			icnLRU->setElemEnabled(false);
			icnProcessor->setElemEnabled(true);
			if (Interface == true)
				icnInterface->setElemEnabled(true);
			else
				icnInterface->setElemEnabled(false);
			if (ParamTbl == true)
				icnParamTbl->setElemEnabled(true);
			else
				icnParamTbl->setElemEnabled(false);
			icnCots->setElemEnabled(true);
		 }
	 }
	else
	{ 

		icnLRU->setElemEnabled(false);
		icnProcessor->setElemEnabled(false);
		icnInterface->setElemEnabled(false);
		icnParamTbl->setElemEnabled(false);
		icnCots->setElemEnabled(false);
	 }
 }

{ 
	CGraphicElement *child = static_cast<CGraphicElement*>(childAt(event->pos()));
	

	for(int i=0; i<list.size(); i++)
	{ 
		if ((child == list.at(i)) && (list.at(i)->isEnabled()))

		else

				list.at(i)->setElemEnabled(false);
		 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
mouseMoveEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QMouseEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	CGraphicElement *child = static_cast<CGraphicElement*>(childAt(event->pos()));
    if (!child)
        return;


	if ((child->isEnabled() == false) || (child->isSelected() == false))
		return;

    QPixmap Image = child->pixmap();


	QByteArray itemData;
    QDataStream dataStream(&itemData, QIODevice::WriteOnly);
	dataStream << child->toolTip() << Image << QPoint(event->pos() - child->pos());

    QMimeData *mimeData = new QMimeData;
    mimeData->setData("applicatio -dnditemdata", itemData);


	QDrag *drag = new QDrag(this);
    drag->setMimeData(mimeData);
    drag->setPixmap(Image);
    drag->setHotSpot(event->pos() - child->pos());


	if (drag->start() == Qt::CopyAction)
	{ 
        child->show();
        child->setPixmap(Image);
     }
 }
__END_BODY__

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:0 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:0 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/hierarchyDialog.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:79 L_END:81 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:hierarchyDialog NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:0 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0

__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDragEnterEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	dragItem =  this->itemAt(event->pos());

	if(dragItem != rootItem)
	{ 
		event->setAccepted(true);
		QList<QTreeWidgetItem*> selectedList = this->selectedItems();
			
		for(int i = 0; i<selectedList.size(); i++)
		{ 
			if(selectedList[i]!= rootItem)
			{ 
				dragBeginItem.push_back(static_cast<itemModel*>(selectedList[i]));
			 }
		 }
	 }
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:2 ASM:0 ASS:5 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:4 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:10 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/hierarchyDialog.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:1 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:1 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:5 INLINE:0 INT:1 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:17 LOCALS:41 LONG:0 LT:3 L_BEGIN:92 L_END:108 MAXNEST:4 MMINUS:0 NAME:dragEnterEvent NONLCALS:2 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:1 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:6 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
dropEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDropEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QTreeWidgetItem *dropItem ;	
	QTreeWidgetItem *dragParent, *dropParent;
	QTreeWidgetItem *child;
	int index = 0;
	
	itemModel *iMDragParent;
	itemModel *iMDropParent;
	itemModel *iMItemBeingDropped;

	QString beginPath ; 
	QString endPath;
	QString itemText;

	QString beginFolderPath, endFolderPath;

	QDir *dropDirParent;

	dropItem = this->itemAt(event->pos());

	if((dropItem!= NULL))
	{ 
		event->setAccepted(true);
	
		dragEndItem = static_cast<itemModel*>(dropItem);
	

		if (dragEndItem->getType() == fo)
		{ 		
		
			dropParent = dragEndItem;

			for(int i = 0; i<dragBeginItem.size(); i++)
			{ 
				dragParent = dragBeginItem[i]->parent();				

				if((dropItem!=dragBeginItem[i])&&(dropParent!= dragParent))
				{ 								
					index = dragParent->indexOfChild(dragBeginItem[i]);
					itemText =dragBeginItem[i]->text(0) ;

					if(itemText!= "Config")
					if(itemText!= "Default")
					if(!itemText.endsWith(".acs"))
					{ 
						child = dragParent->takeChild(index);

						iMDragParent = static_cast<itemModel*>(dragParent);

						iMDropParent = static_cast<itemModel*>(dropParent);

						iMItemBeingDropped= static_cast<itemModel*>(child);

						iMItemBeingDropped->setIsModified(true);

						dragEndItem->addChild(child);	

						if(dragBeginItem[i]->getType() == fi)
						{ 
							
							beginPath = iMDragParent->getDir()->absoluteFilePath(dragBeginItem[i]->text(0));
							endPath = iMDropParent->getDir()->absolutePath()+"/"+dragBeginItem[i]->text(0);
										
							iMItemBeingDropped->setNewPath(endPath);						
							
							moveFile(beginPath,  endPath);
						 }

						else
						{ 
							endPath = iMDropParent->getDir()->absolutePath()+"/"+dragBeginItem[i]->text(0);
							iMItemBeingDropped->setDir(endPath);
										
							iMItemBeingDropped->setNewPath(endPath);

							dropDirParent = iMDropParent->getDir();
							recursiveMove(iMDragParent->getDir(), dragBeginItem[i]->text(0), dropDirParent);
							recursiveDelete(*iMDragParent->getDir(),dragBeginItem[i]->text(0));
						
						 }
				 }
				else
				{ 
					QMessageBox::warning(0,"Acs Move Error", " Acs file is open - Cannot Move");
				 }
				else
				{ 
					QMessageBox::warning(0,"Default Move Error", " Acs file is open - Cannot Move");
				 }
				else
				{ 
					QMessageBox::warning(0,"Config Move Error", " Acs file is open - Cannot Move");

				 }

				 }
				
			 }
			dragBeginItem.clear();			
		
		
		 }

		else if(dragEndItem->getType() == fi)
		{ 	
			
			dropParent = dragEndItem->parent() ;
				
			for(int i = 0; i<dragBeginItem.size(); i++)
			{ 
				dragParent = dragBeginItem[i]->parent();
				if((dropItem!=dragBeginItem[i])&&(dropParent!=dragParent))
				{ 
					itemText =dragBeginItem[i]->text(0) ;

					if(itemText!= "Config")
					if(itemText!= "Default")
					if(!itemText.endsWith(".acs"))
					{ 
						index = dragParent->indexOfChild(dragBeginItem[i]);
						child = dragParent->takeChild(index);
						
						iMDragParent = static_cast<itemModel*>(dragParent);

						iMDropParent = static_cast<itemModel*>(dropParent);
						
						iMItemBeingDropped = static_cast<itemModel*>(child);
						
						iMItemBeingDropped->setIsModified(true);
					
						dropParent->addChild(child);

						if(dragBeginItem[i]->getType() == fi)
						{ 							
							beginPath = iMDragParent->getDir()->absoluteFilePath(dragBeginItem[i]->text(0));
							endPath = iMDropParent->getDir()->absolutePath()+"/"+dragBeginItem[i]->text(0);	
							iMItemBeingDropped->setNewPath(endPath);
							moveFile(beginPath,  endPath);
						 }

						else
						{ 
								
							endPath = iMDropParent->getDir()->absolutePath()+"/"+dragBeginItem[i]->text(0);
											
							iMItemBeingDropped->setNewPath(endPath);
							iMItemBeingDropped->setDir(endPath);
							
							dropDirParent = iMDropParent->getDir();
							recursiveMove(iMDragParent->getDir(), dragBeginItem[i]->text(0), dropDirParent);
							recursiveDelete(*iMDragParent->getDir(), dragBeginItem[i]->text(0));
							
						 }
					 }
					else
					{ 
						QMessageBox::warning(0,"Acs Move Error", " Acs file is open - Cannot Move");
					 }
					else
					{ 
						QMessageBox::warning(0,"Default Move Error", " Acs file is open - Cannot Move");
					 }
					else
					{ 
						QMessageBox::warning(0,"Config Move Error", " Acs file is open - Cannot Move");

					 }

				 }
				
			 }
			dragBeginItem.clear();

		 }
	 }
 }

Parent::itemText::dragBeginItem::i::text::itemText::Config::itemText::Default::itemText::endsWith::acs::index::dragParent::indexOfChild::dragBeginItem::i::child::dragParent::takeChild::index::iMDragParent::static_cast::itemModel::dragParent::iMDropParent::static_cast::itemModel::dropParent::iMItemBeingDropped::static_cast::itemModel::child::iMItemBeingDropped::setIsModified::true::dropParent::addChild::child::dragBeginItem::i::getType::fi::beginPath::iMDragParent::getDir::absoluteFilePath::dragBeginItem::i::text::endPath::iMDropParent::getDir::absolutePath::dragBeginItem::i::text::iMItemBeingDropped::setNewPath::endPath::moveFile::beginPath::endPath::endPath::iMDropParent::getDir::absolutePath::dragBeginItem::i::text::iMItemBeingDropped::setNewPath::endPath::iMItemBeingDropped::setDir::endPath::dropDirParent::iMDropParent::getDir::recursiveMove::iMDragParent::getDir::dragBeginItem::i::text::dropDirParent::recursiveDelete::iMDragParent::getDir::dragBeginItem::i::text::QMessageBox::warning::Acs::Move::Error::Acs::file::is::open::Cannot::Move::QMessageBox::warning::Default::Move::Error::Acs::file::is::open::Cannot::Move::QMessageBox::warning::Config::Move::Error::Acs::file::is::open::Cannot::Move::dragBeginItem::clear

#METRICS ARRAYOP:20 ASM:0 ASS:38 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:71 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:16 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:8 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:9 ENUM:0 EQTEST:4 EXPRORCALL:99 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/hierarchyDialog.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:2 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:6 IF:13 IN:0 INDR:55 INLINE:0 INT:3 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:176 LOCALS:308 LONG:0 LT:9 L_BEGIN:121 L_END:296 MAXNEST:7 MMINUS:0 NAME:dropEvent NONLCALS:2 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:2 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:6 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:67 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotRenameFolder
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QString empty = "";
	QDir *Dir;
	QTreeWidgetItem *parent;
	itemModel *iMParent, *iMContextItem;
	QString oldName;
	bool ok;
	
	parent = contextItem->parent();

	if(parent)
	{ 
		QString text = QInputDialog::getText(this, tr("Rename folder"),
                                          empty , QLineEdit::Normal,
                                             contextItem->text(0), &ok);

		if (ok && !text.isEmpty())
		{   	
		

			iMParent = static_cast<itemModel*>(parent);

			Dir = iMParent->getDir();
			
			oldName = contextItem->text(0);
			
			contextItem->setText(0,text);
			
			Dir->rename(oldName,text);
			
			iMContextItem = static_cast<itemModel*>(contextItem);

			iMContextItem->setIsModified(true);

			iMContextItem->setNewPath(Dir->absFilePath(text));

			iMContextItem->setDir(Dir->absFilePath(text));
			
						
					
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

{ 	 
	QTreeWidgetItem *parent;
	itemModel *child;
	itemModel *iMParent;
	QDir *newDir;

	 bool ok; 
	 QString text, empty= "";

	 if ( contextItem->getType() == fi )
	 { 
			
				 text = QInputDialog::getText(this, tr("Enter folder name"),
                                             tr(""), QLineEdit::Normal,
                                             empty, &ok);
				if (ok && !text.isEmpty())
				{   	
					parent = contextItem->parent();
					iMParent = static_cast<itemModel*>(parent);
					newDir = iMParent->getDir();
					child = new itemModel(fo, parent);
					child->setText(0,text);		
					newDir->mkdir(text);
					child->setIcon(0, QIcon(": mage older_16.png"));
					child->setDir(newDir->absoluteFilePath(text));
					child->setOldPath(newDir->absFilePath(text));
				
				 }
					
	  }

	 else
	 { 
		 
			 text = QInputDialog::getText(this, tr("Enter folder name"),
                                             tr(""), QLineEdit::Normal,
                                             empty, &ok);
				if (ok && !text.isEmpty())
				{   	
					
					child = new itemModel(fo, contextItem);
					child->setText(0,text);
					child->setIcon(0, QIcon(": mage older_16.png"));
					iMParent = static_cast<itemModel*>(contextItem);
					newDir = iMParent->getDir();
					newDir->mkdir(text);
					child->setDir(newDir->absoluteFilePath(text));
					child->setOldPath(newDir->absFilePath(text));				
	 		
				
				 }				
				
	  }
 }

addElement

__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDir pere, QString fils,  itemModel *childItem)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QStringList fileList , dirList;
	itemModel  *filsItem, *pereItem;
	QString filePath;

		
	pere.cd(fils);
	fileList  = pere.entryList(QDir::Files);
	for(int i = 0; i<fileList.size(); i++)
	{ 
		
		filsItem = new itemModel(fi, childItem);
		filsItem->setText(0,fileList[i]);		
		filsItem->setIcon(0, QIcon(": mage ocument_plain_16.png"));
		mapItemPath[filsItem] =  pere.absoluteFilePath(fileList[i]);
	
	 }
	dirList = pere.entryList(QDir::Dirs);
	for(int j = 0; j< dirList.size(); j++)
	{ 
		if(dirList[j] != "." && dirList[j] != "..")
		{ 
			pereItem = new itemModel(fo, childItem);
			pereItem->setDir(pere.absoluteFilePath(dirList[j]));
			pereItem->setText(0,dirList[j]);
			pereItem->setIcon(0, QIcon(": mage older_16.png"));
			addElement(pere, dirList[j],pereItem);
			mapItemPath[filsItem] =  pere.absoluteFilePath(dirList[j]);
		 }
	
	 }

	pere.cdUp();

 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenuEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QContextMenuEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *qwItem = currentItem();
  contextItem= static_cast<itemModel*>(qwItem);

   if ( contextItem == 0 )
    return;

  if ( contextItem->getType() == fi )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddAct);
	menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }

  else 
	if ( contextItem->getType() == fo)
	{ 
		QMenu menu(this);
		menu.addAction(mAddAct);
		if(contextItem!= rootItem)
		{ 
			
			if(contextItem->parent()!=rootItem)
				menu.addAction(mRenameAct);
			if(contextItem->childCount() ==0)
				menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);   
		 }
		menu.exec(event->globalPos());
	 }
 
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
moveFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString beginPath, QString endPath)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QFile fileBegin(beginPath);	
    QFile fileEnd(endPath);

	QByteArray content;
    if (!fileBegin.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text))
	{ 
		QMessageBox::warning(0, "", "Move Error");
		return false;
	
	 }
	else
		content = fileBegin.readAll();
	

    if (!fileEnd.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text))
	{  
		QMessageBox::warning(0, "", "Move Error");
		return false;
	 }
	else
	{ 
		
		fileEnd.write(content);
		fileEnd.close();
		fileBegin.close();
		fileBegin.remove();
		return true;

	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
recursiveMove
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDir *beginFolder, QString childFolder,  QDir *copyFolder)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QStringList fileList , dirList;
	QString filePath;
	QString beginFilePath, endFilePath;

		
	beginFolder->cd(childFolder);
	copyFolder->mkdir(childFolder);
	copyFolder->cd(childFolder);
	fileList  = beginFolder->entryList(QDir::Files);
	for(int i = 0; i<fileList.size(); i++)
	{ 
		
		beginFilePath = beginFolder->absoluteFilePath(fileList[i]);
		endFilePath = copyFolder->absolutePath()+"/"+fileList[i];

		moveFile(beginFilePath, endFilePath);
		
	
	 }
	dirList = beginFolder->entryList(QDir::Dirs);
	for(int j = 0; j< dirList.size(); j++)
	{ 
		if(dirList[j] != "." && dirList[j] != "..")
			recursiveMove(beginFolder, dirList[j], copyFolder );
		
	 }

	beginFolder->cdUp();	
	copyFolder->cdUp();
	
 }
__END_BODY__

recursiveDelete
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDir pere, QString fils)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QStringList fileList , dirList;
	pere.cd(fils);
	fileList  = pere.entryList(QDir::Files);
	for(int i = 0; i<fileList.size(); i++)
	{ 
		pere.remove(fileList[i]);
	 }
	dirList = pere.entryList(QDir::Dirs);
	for(int j = 0; j< dirList.size(); j++)
	{ 
		if(dirList[j] != "." && dirList[j] != "..")
		{ 				
			recursiveDelete(pere, dirList[j]);
			pere.rmdir(dirList[j]);
		 }
	
	 }

	pere.cdUp();
	pere.rmdir(fils);
 }

__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int widgetWidth;
	QStringList horizHeaderList;
	mMainWindow = (CMainWindow*)parent;
	mpSelectedItem = NULL;

	setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);


	setColumnCount(3);
	setRowCount(0);
	horizHeaderList = (QStringList() << tr("Attribute") << tr("Type") << tr("Value"));
	setHorizontalHeaderLabels(horizHeaderList);


	widgetWidth = parent->width();
	setColumnWidth(0, widgetWidt -1);
	setColumnWidth(1, widgetWidt -1);
	setColumnWidth(2, widgetWidt -1);



	mAddProperty = new QAction(tr("&Add property"), this);
	mAddProperty->setStatusTip(tr("Adds a custom property"));
	mAddProperty->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
	connect(mAddProperty, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddCustProperty()));

	mEditCustProperty = new QAction(tr("&Edit custom property"), this);
	mEditCustProperty->setStatusTip(tr("Adds a custom property"));
	mEditCustProperty->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
	connect(mEditCustProperty, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditCustProperty()));

	mDeleteValueAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete custom property"), this);
	mDeleteValueAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
	mDeleteValueAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
	mDeleteValueAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
	connect(mDeleteValueAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDeleteCustProperty()));



 }

CGraphicProperties
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int rowCount, rowIndex;


	disconnect(mDeleteValueAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDeleteCustProperty()));
	disconnect(mEditCustProperty, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditCustProperty()));
	disconnect(mAddProperty, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddCustProperty()));


	delete mDeleteValueAct;
	delete mEditCustProperty;
	delete mAddProperty;


	rowCount = this->rowCount();
	for(rowIndex = rowCount - 1; rowIndex >= 0; rowIndex--)
	{ 
		removeRow(rowIndex);
	 }
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:5 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:5 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicProperties.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:4 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:183 L_END:185 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:enableTableConnection NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:1 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
updateDisplay
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CGraphicElement *pGraphicElement)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int type, i, rowCount;
	int nextItem = 1;
	QTableWidgetItem* newTblItem;
	QTreeWidgetItem* pTreeWidgetItem;
	bool bExit = false;


	disableTableConnection();


	mpSelectedItem = pGraphicElement;


	mTreeItemPtrLst.clear();
	rowCount = this->rowCount();
	for(i = rowCount - 1; i >= 0; i--)
	{ 
		removeRow(i);
	 }


	if (mpSelectedItem == NULL)
		bExit = true;

	if(!bExit)
	{ 
		pTreeWidgetItem = mpSelectedItem->getProperties();
		if (pTreeWidgetItem == NULL)
		{ 
			QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
											"No TreeWidgetItem is defined.\n\n",
											"OK");
			bExit = true;
		 }
	 }


	if(!bExit)
	{ 

		this->setRowCount(this->rowCount() + 1);

		newTblItem = new CPropertyConst(pTreeWidgetItem->text(0), this, 0, 0);
		newTblItem = new CPropertyString(pTreeWidgetItem->text(1), this, 0, 1);
		newTblItem = new CPropertyConst(pTreeWidgetItem->text(2), this, 0, 2);



		for(i = 0; i < pTreeWidgetItem->childCount(); i++)
		{ 

			if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->type() == ConfigValue || 
			pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->type() == ConfigUserValue)
			{ 

				this->setRowCount(this->rowCount() + 1);


				mTreeItemPtrLst.append(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i));

				if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->type() == ConfigUserValue)
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyString(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(0), this, nextItem, 0);
				 }
				else
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyConst(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(0), this, nextItem, 0);
				 }

				newTblItem = new CPropertyConst(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1), this, nextItem, 1);

				if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("int"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyInt(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("string"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyString(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("bool"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyBool(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("double"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyDouble(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("file"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyFile(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("path"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyPath(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("band"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyBand(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else if(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(1) == tr("side"))
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertySide(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }
				else
				{ 
					newTblItem = new CPropertyString(pTreeWidgetItem->child(i)->text(2), this, nextItem, 2);
				 }

				nextItem++;
			 }
		 }



		this->verticalHeader()->hide();
	 }


	enableTableConnection();

 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

r::side::newTblItem::new::CPropertySide::pTreeWidgetItem::child::i::text::nextItem::newTblItem::new::CPropertyString::pTreeWidgetItem::child::i::text::nextItem::nextItem::verticalHeader::hide::enableTableConnection

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotAddCustProperty
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	if(mConfig == NULL)
	{ 
		QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
										"No project is set as active project.\n\n",
										"OK");
		return;
	 }
	if(mpSelectedItem == NULL)
	{ 
		QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
										"Selected item is null.\n\n",
										"OK");
		return;
	 }

	mConfig->setItemSelected(mpSelectedItem->getProperties(), true);
	mConfig->slotAddProperty();
	updateDisplay(mpSelectedItem);

 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:6 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:3 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:2 EXPRORCALL:8 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CGraphicProperties.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:2 IN:0 INDR:4 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:21 LOCALS:47 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:328 L_END:348 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:slotAddCustProperty NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:2 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:7 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotEditProperty
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(int row, int col)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	CUndoStack* cmdStack = mGraphicDesign->getCmdStack();
	QTreeWidgetItem* item;


	if (mpSelectedItem == NULL)
	return;


	if(row == 0)
	{ 
		if(col == 1)
		{ 
			item = mpSelectedItem->getProperties();
			QString type = ((CBasePropertyItem*)this->item(row, col))->getText();

			switch(item->type())
			{ 
			case ConfigSystem:
				cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit system item", item, 1, type, true));
				emit modified();
				break;

			case ConfigLRU:
				cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit lru item", item, 1, type, true));
				emit modified();
				break;

			case ConfigTable:
				cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit parameter item item", item, 1, type, true));
				emit modified();
				break;

			case ConfigInterface:
				cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit interface item", item, 1, type, true));
				emit modified();
				break;

			case ConfigPowerSupply:
				cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit power supply item", item, 1, type, true));
				emit modified();
				break;

			case ConfigProcess:
				cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit processor item", item, 1, type, true));
				emit modified();
				break;

			default:
				break;
			 }
		 }

	 }

	else
	{ 
		item = mTreeItemPtrLst[row - 1];
		QString value = ((CBasePropertyItem*)this->item(row, col))->getText();

		if(col == 2)
		{ 
			if( item->type() == ConfigValue || 
				item->type() == ConfigUserValue)
			{ 
				cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit value item", item, col, value, true));
				emit modified();
			 }
		 }
		else if(col == 0)
		{ 
			if( item->type() == ConfigUserValue)
			{ 

				if(!mConfig->propertyExists(item->parent(), value))
				{ 
					cmdStack->push(new CConfigCmdEdit("edit value item", item, col, value, true));
					emit modified();
				 }
				else
				{ 
					QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
												"A property with this name already exists.\n\n",
												"OK");

					disableTableConnection();
					((CBasePropertyItem*)this->item(row, col))->setText(item->text(0));
					enableTableConnection();
				 }
			 }
		 }
	 }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotEditCustProperty
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int currentRow;


	currentRow = this->currentRow();
	if (currentRow > 0)
	{ 
		QTreeWidgetItem* treeItem;

		treeItem = mTreeItemPtrLst[currentRow - 1];
		mConfig->setCurrentItem(treeItem);
		mConfig->slotEditUserValue();
		if(mpSelectedItem == NULL)
		{ 
			QMessageBox::warning(this, "Application name",
				"Error : No graphic item is active!.\n\n",
                                    "OK");
			return;
		 }
		mConfig->setCurrentItem(mpSelectedItem->getProperties());
		updateDisplay(mpSelectedItem);
	 }

 }

{ 
	QMenu menu(this);
	QTableWidgetItem* item;
	int currentRow;

	if(mpSelectedItem != NULL)
	{ 
		menu.addAction(mAddProperty);

		item = this->currentItem();
		if (item != NULL)
		{ 
			currentRow = row(item);

			if( currentRow > 0 && mTreeItemPtrLst[currentRow - 1]->type() == ConfigUserValue)
			{ 
				menu.addAction(mEditCustProperty);
				menu.addAction(mDeleteValueAct);
			 }
		 }
		menu.exec(event->globalPos());
	 }

 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
resizeEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QResizeEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	int rowIndex, rowNumber;
	QTableWidgetItem* tableItem;
	int widgetWidth = mMainWindow->width();

	rowNumber = this->rowCount();
	QTableWidget::resizeEvent(event);

	this->setColumnWidth(0, widgetWidt -1);
	this->setColumnWidth(1, widgetWidt -1);
	this->setColumnWidth(2, widgetWidt -1);

	for(rowIndex = 0; rowIndex < rowNumber; rowIndex++)
	{ 
		tableItem = item(rowIndex, 2);
		if(tableItem->type() == PropFile)
		{ 
			((CPropertyFile*)tableItem)->ResizeColumns();
		 }
		else if(tableItem->type() == PropPath)
		{ 
			((CPropertyPath*)tableItem)->ResizeColumns();
		 }
	 }

 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
getFilePath
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString file, QDir Rep, QString PTBL)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	
	QMap<QString, QString>::const_iterator it; 
	QString temp = "";
	QString parTblDir; 
	QStringList nameExplode ; 
	it = mapDir.find(file);
		if(it!= mapDir.end())
		{ 	
			temp = mapDir[file];		
			
		 }
		else
		{ 
			if(PTBL == "")
			{ 
			mapDir[file] = Rep.absolutePath()+"/" + file;
			temp = Rep.absolutePath()+"/" + file;	
			 }
			else
			{ 


				Rep.mkdir(PTBL);
				Rep.cd(PTBL);
				mapDir[file] = Rep.absolutePath()+"/" + file;
				temp = Rep.absolutePath()+"/" + file;			
				Rep.cdUp();
			
			 }

		 }
	
		
	return temp;


 }
__END_BODY__

{

	QProgressDialog pd("Generating files...", 0, 0, 400, 0);

	pd.setValue(count);

	QFile sys_doc_main;

	templatePath = path.trimmed();

	QDir rep_templateStart(templatePath);
	QDir rep_template = rep_templateStart;
	

	

    QString  nom_sys = xml.getAttrib("cname").c_str();
	QFileInfo inf = QFileInfo(project_path);
	QDir RepStart = inf.dir();

	QDir Rep = RepStart;

	Rep.cdUp();
	Rep.cdUp();
	

	QDir rep_doc = rep_template;	

	

	if(messageInLru.size()!=0)
	{ 
		messageInLru.clear();
	 }
	if(procReceivingMessage.size()!=0)
	{ 
		procReceivingMessage.clear();
	 }
	
		
	
		Rep.cd("Src");		
		if(Rep.count()!=0)
		{ 
			
			if(mapDir.size()!=0)
			{ 
				mapDir.clear();
				parTableConfig.clear();
				processorConfig.clear();
				interfaceConfig.clear();
				lruConfig.clear();
				systemConfig.clear();
				
				
			 }
		
			Rep.cdUp();
			mapDirectory(Rep, "Src");


		 }
		else
		{ 
			Rep.cdUp();
		 }
		

	if(rep_template.exists("Res"))
	{ 
		Rep.cd("Res");
		rep_template.cd("Res");


		temp = Rep.absolutePath()+" esource.h";
		QFile sys_res(temp);
		sys_res.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text);


		temp = rep_template.absolutePath()+" esource.h";
		QFile sys_res_h_template(temp);
		sys_res_h_template.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);

		content_res_h = sys_res_h_template.readAll();
		
		if(content_res_h.size()==0)
		{ 
			if(!missingFiles.contains(temp))
			missingFiles.push_back(temp);
		 }
		content_res_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
		content_res_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys.toUpper());
		content_res_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
		sys_res.write(content_res_h);
		sys_res.close();


		temp = Rep.absolutePath()+"/"+nom_sys+".rc";
		QFile sys_rc(temp);

		sys_rc_h_template.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);
		
		content_rc_h = sys_rc_h_template.readAll();

		if(content_rc_h.size()==0)
		{ 
			if(!missingFiles.contains(temp))
			missingFiles.push_back(temp);
		 }

		content_rc_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
		content_rc_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys.toUpper());
		content_rc_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
		sys_rc.write(content_rc_h);
		sys_rc.close();


		Rep.cdUp();
		rep_template.cdUp();
	 }
	else
	{ 
		if(!missingFolders.contains(rep_template.absolutePath()+" es/"))
		missingFolders.push_back(rep_template.absolutePath()+" es/");
