	QFile sys_vcproj_template(temp);

    vcprojFilePath = Rep.absolutePath()+"/"+nom_sys+".vcproj";

	sys_vcproj_template.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);



	content_vcproj = sys_vcproj_template.readAll();

	if(content_vcproj.size() ==0)
	{ 
		if(!missingFiles.contains(temp))
		missingFiles.push_back(temp);
	 }

	content_vcproj.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);	
	
	sys_vcproj_template.close();


	if(rep_doc.exists("Doc"))
	{ 
		rep_doc.cd("Doc");
		Rep.cd("Doc");


		temp = rep_doc.absolutePath()+" ainPage_template.txt";
		QFile sys_doc_main_template(temp);
		temp = Rep.absolutePath()+" ainPage.txt";
		sys_doc_main.setFileName(temp);

		sys_doc_main_template.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);
		sys_doc_main.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text);
		
		content_mainPage = sys_doc_main_template.readAll();
		if(content_mainPage.size() ==0)
		{ 
			if(!missingFiles.contains(temp))
			missingFiles.push_back(temp);
		 }
		content_mainPage.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
	
		



		temp = rep_doc.absolutePath()+" RU_template.txt";
		QFile sys_doc_LRU_template(temp);
		sys_doc_LRU_template.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);
		
		content_LRU_template = sys_doc_LRU_template.readAll();
		if(content_LRU_template.size() ==0)

			if(!missingFiles.contains(temp))
			missingFiles.push_back(temp);
		 }
		content_LRU_template.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);		



		temp = rep_doc.absolutePath()+" ySystem_template.dox";

		{

		 }

		Rep.cdUp();
		Rep.cd("Src");	
		content_dox.replace("SRC", Rep.absolutePath()+"/");

		Rep.cdUp();
		Rep.cd("Doc");
		content_dox.replace("OUTPUTDIR", Rep.absolutePath());	
		content_dox.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
		content_dox.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys.toUpper());
		content_dox.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);

		sys_doc_dox.close();
		Rep.cdUp();

	else
	{

		missingFolders.push_back(rep_doc.absolutePath()+" oc/");
		
	 }



	

	
	
	Rep.cd("Src");

	systemConfig[nom_sys]->setParentType("Source Files");
	
	tempFileName = nom_sys+"_"+nom_sys+".cpp";
	filename  = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);
	systemConfig[nom_sys]->addToFileList(filename);
	QFile sys_cpp(filename);	
	sys_cpp.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text);

	QFile sys_cpp_temp(temp);
	sys_cpp_temp.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);

	content = sys_cpp_temp.readAll();
	if(content.size()==0)
	{

		missingFiles.push_back(temp);
	 }

	tempFileName = nom_sys+"_"+nom_sys+".h";
	filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);
	systemConfig[nom_sys]->addToFileList(filename);
	QFile sys_h(filename);

	sys_h.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text);



	temp = rep_template.absolutePath()+" ySystem_mySystem.h";	
	QFile sys_h_temp(temp);
	sys_h_temp.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);

	content_h = sys_h_temp.readAll();
	if(content_h.size()==0)
	{ 
		if(!missingFiles.contains(temp))
		missingFiles.push_back(temp);
	 }
	content_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);

	 }

				xml.intoElem();
				
				while ( xml.findElem() )
    			{ 

						count++;
						count %=100;
						pd.setValue(count);
		
					if(xml.getTagName() == "value")
					{ 	
						if(QString(xml.getAttrib("name").c_str()) == "Param File Name")
						{ 
								if(QString(xml.getAttrib("value").c_str()) != "lru.par")
								{ 
										
									tempParam = new CParam(0,0);
									tempParam->readFile(QString(xml.getAttrib("value").c_str()));
									tempFileName = tempParam->getTypeName();
									if(tempFileName != "")
									{ 
										temp = tempFileName;
										tempFileName = nom_sys+"_"+tempFileName+".h";
										filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep, temp);
					
										tempParam->setSourcePath(filename);		

										tempParam->generate();
										parTblGenFolder = QFileInfo(filename).absoluteDir();
										parTblGenFiles = parTblGenFolder.entryInfoList(QDir::Files);
										parTblGenSectionFolder = parTblGenFolder.entryList(QDir::AllDirs) ;
										  for ( i = 0; i < parTblGenSectionFolder.size(); ++i)
										  {   
											if((parTblGenSectionFolder.at(i)!= ".")&&(parTblGenSectionFolder.at(i)!= ".."))
											{ 	
												parTblGenFolder.cd(parTblGenSectionFolder.at(i));
												parTblGenFiles+= parTblGenFolder.entryInfoList(QDir::Files);
												parTblGenFolder.cdUp();
											 }
										   }
										

										

										if(parTableConfig.size()>0)
											{ 
												if(parTableConfig.find(temp)==parTableConfig.end())
												{ 
													parTableConfig[temp] = new genProject();
													genPtbl = true;
												 }
												else
													genPtbl = false;


											 }
											else
											{ 
												genPtbl = true;
												parTableConfig[temp] = new genProject();
											 }

											parTableConfig[temp]->setParentType(n_LRU);
											if(genPtbl)
											{ 
												for(i = 0; i<parTblGenFiles.size(); i++)
													parTableConfig[temp]->addToFileList(parTblGenFiles.at(i).absoluteFilePath());

											 }
								
									 }
									else
									{ 
										QString message = "Please specify type name of "+QString(xml.getAttrib("value").c_str());
										
									 }				

								 }				

						 }	
						
					 }

					else if ( xml.getTagName() == "INTERFACE" )
				
					{

						content_Interface_cpp.replace("<ACSLRUTYPE>",n_LRU);

						content_Interface_cpp.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
						content_Interface_cpp.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys.toUpper());
						content_Interface_cpp.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
						temp_file->write(content_Interface_cpp);
						temp_file->close();				

						
						tempFileName = nom_sys+"_"+temp+".h";
						filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);
						interfaceConfig[temp]->addToFileList(filename);

						temp_file = new QFile(filename);	
						temp_file->open(QIODevice::WriteOnly | QIODevice::Text);
						

						nom_Interface = rep_template.absolutePath()+" ySystem_myInterface.h";
						QFile sys_Interface_h_temp(nom_Interface);
						sys_Interface_h_temp.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);
						
						content_Interface_h = sys_Interface_h_temp.readAll();
						if(content_Interface_h.size()==0)
						{ 
							if(!missingFiles.contains(nom_Interface))
							missingFiles.push_back(nom_Interface);
						 }
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSINTERFACETYPE>",temp);
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSINTERFACETYPE>",temp);
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSINTERFACETYPE>",temp.toUpper());
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSLRUTYPE>",n_LRU);
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSLRUTYPE>",n_LRU);
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSLRUTYPE>",n_LRU.toUpper());
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys.toUpper());
						content_Interface_h.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
						temp_file->write(content_Interface_h);
						temp_file->close();

					 }
					else if ( xml.getTagName() == "POWERSUPPLY" )					
					{ 
					 }
					else if ( xml.getTagName() == "PROCESSOR" )
					{ 
						messageIntercepted = false;
						temp = xml.getAttrib("cname").c_str();
						QString nom_Proc = temp;

						if(processorConfig.size()>0)
						{

						{

							missingFiles.push_back(nom_Proc);
						 }
						content_Proc_h.replace("<ACSPROCESSORTYPE>",temp);

						QFile sys_Proc_fct_temp(nom_Proc);
						sys_Proc_fct_temp.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly | QIODevice::Text);
						
						content_Proc_fct = sys_Proc_fct_temp.readAll();
						if(content_Proc_fct.size()==0)
						{ 
							if(!missingFiles.contains(nom_Proc))
							missingFiles.push_back(nom_Proc);
						 }
						content_Proc_fct.replace("<ACSPROCESSORTYPE>",temp);
						content_Proc_fct.replace("<ACSPROCESSORTYPE>",temp);
						content_Proc_fct.replace("<ACSPROCESSORTYPE>",temp);

						content_Proc_fct.replace("<ACSLRUTYPE>",n_LRU);

						content_Proc_fct.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
						content_Proc_fct.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys.toUpper());
						content_Proc_fct.replace("<ACSSYSTEMTYPE>",nom_sys);
						temp_file->write(content_Proc_fct);
						temp_file->close();
							xml.intoElem();
							 while (xml.findElem())
								{ 
								
									if(xml.getTagName() == "value")
									{ 	
										if(QString(xml.getAttrib("name").c_str()) == "msgTypeProc")
										{ 
											messageIntercepted = true;
											messageInterceptedInLru = true;
											receivingProcName = xml.getAttrib("value").c_str();
																						
											tempMsgModel = new messageModel();
											tempMsgModel->setValidity(true);

										 }									
										else if(QString(xml.getAttrib("name").c_str()) == "msgName")
										{ 
											messagePropertyValue = xml.getAttrib("value").c_str();
										
											tempMsgModel->setName(messagePropertyValue);
										
										 }
										else if(QString(xml.getAttrib("name").c_str()) == "msgID")
										{ 	
											messagePropertyValue = xml.getAttrib("value").c_str();
											
											tempMsgModel->setID(messagePropertyValue);
								
										 }
										else if(QString(xml.getAttrib("name").c_str()) == "msgTypeMsg")
										{ 
											messagePropertyValue = xml.getAttrib("value").c_str();
											
											tempMsgModel->setTypeMsg(messagePropertyValue);

								
										 }
										else if(QString(xml.getAttrib("name").c_str()) == "msgPeriodicity")
										{ 
											messagePropertyValue = xml.getAttrib("value").c_str();
											
											tempMsgModel->setPeriodicity(messagePropertyValue);
								
										 }
										else if(QString(xml.getAttrib("name").c_str()) == "msgFilter")
										{ 
											messagePropertyValue = xml.getAttrib("value").c_str();
											
											tempMsgModel->setFilter(messagePropertyValue);
											addOk = true;
										 }								
										
									 }
								if((tempMsgModel !=NULL)&&(addOk))
								{ 		
								tempMsgModel->setLruName(n_LRU);	
								procReceivingMessage[receivingProcName].push_back(tempMsgModel);
								messageInLru[n_LRU].push_back(tempMsgModel);
								tempMsgModel = NULL;
								addOk = false;
								 }

								 }
								if(!messageIntercepted)
								{ 									
								procReceivingMessage[temp].push_back(invalidModel);
								 }
								xml.outOfElem();
							
					 }
					else
					
					{ 
					 }

				 }
	
				xml.outOfElem();
		if(!messageInterceptedInLru)
		{ 
			messageInLru[n_LRU].push_back(invalidModel);
		
		 }	
				
		 }
		



 
   }
  xml.outOfElem();  

 
  if(!messageInLru.isEmpty()) 
  addMessagesToLruFiles(nom_sys, Rep);
  if(!procReceivingMessage.isEmpty())
  addMessagesToProcFiles(nom_sys, Rep);

  sys_doc_main.write(content_mainPage);
  sys_doc_main.close();

  if(content_vcproj.size()!=0)
  { 
	generateMakefile(vcprojFilePath, content_vcproj); 
   
	QProcess vcprojConvert;
	QString appDir = QApplication::applicationDirPath();
	QDir prjConverterDir(appDir);

	if(prjConverterDir.exists("prjconverter.exe"))
	{ 
		appDir +=" rjconverter.exe ";
		vcprojConvert.setWorkingDirectory(QFileInfo(vcprojFilePath).absoluteDir().absolutePath());
		QString cmd= appDir +" "+vcprojFilePath;
		vcprojConvert.execute(cmd);
	 }
	else
	{ 
		if(!missingPrograms.contains("prjconverter"))
		missingPrograms.push_back("prjconverter");
	 }
   }

  Rep.cdUp();
  Rep.cd("Doc");


  QProcess docGen ;
  docGen.setWorkingDirectory(Rep.absolutePath());
  QString command =  "doxygen "+ Rep.absolutePath()+"/" + nom_sys+".dox";
  
  docGen.start(command);
 if(docGen.error()!= QProcess::FailedToStart)
 { 
	
	while(!docGen.waitForFinished(10))
	{   
		count++;
		if(count<pd.maximum())
		 pd.setValue(count);

	 } 


  }
 else
 { 

	 if(!missingPrograms.contains("Doxygen"))
	 missingPrograms.push_back("Doxygen");
  }

  pd.setValue(pd.maximum());



 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:30 ASM:0 ASS:158 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:569 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:88 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:478 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:19 ENUM:0 EQTEST:34 EXPRORCALL:660 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/GraphicalInterface/Controller/Event-Handler/CCodeDocGen.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:2 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:98 IF:81 IN:0 INDR:59 INLINE:0 INT:2 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:984 LOCALS:1373 LONG:0 LT:100 L_BEGIN:105 L_END:1114 MAXNEST:7 MMINUS:0 NAME:gen NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:2 PPLUS:5 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:79 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:480 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:4 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
addMessagesToLruFiles
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString nom_sys, QDir Rep)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	
	
	QString tempFileName ;
	QString filename ;
	int insertIndex = 0;

	QString msgName; 
	QString msgId;
	QString msgType;
	QString msgDelay;
	QString strToWrite; 


	
	QFile *modifyFile;
	
	QByteArray contents;

	QMap<QString, listModel>::iterator msgLruIter = messageInLru.begin();
	QList<messageModel*> msgModelList; 
	QList<messageModel*>::iterator msgModelIter; 


	if(messageInLru.empty())
		return;

	for(; msgLruIter!=messageInLru.end(); msgLruIter++ )
	{ 

		tempFileName= nom_sys+"_"+msgLruIter.key()+ "msg.h";
        filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);	
		modifyFile = new QFile(filename);
		modifyFile->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite|QIODevice::Text);
		contents = modifyFile->readAll();
		msgModelList = msgLruIter.value();

		if(contents.size()!=0)
		{ 

		for(msgModelIter = msgModelList.begin(); msgModelIter != msgModelList.end(); msgModelIter++)
		{ 
			
			if((*msgModelIter)->isValid())
			{ 
			msgName = (*msgModelIter)->getName();
			msgId = (*msgModelIter)->getID();
			msgType = (*msgModelIter)->getTypeMsg();
			msgDelay = (*msgModelIter)->getPeriodicity();
			
			insertIndex = contents.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_ID>", 0);			
			
			strToWrite = "const int "+msgName.toUpper()+" = "+msgId+";"+'\n';
			contents.insert(insertIndex, strToWrite);

			insertIndex = contents.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_TYPE>", 0);	

			if(msgType =="Periodic")
			{ 
					strToWrite =  "const int "+msgName+" = _ACS::eTIME_CRITICAL_MSG;"+'\n';
			 }
			else if(msgType =="Critical")
			{ 
				strToWrite =  "const int "+msgName+" = _ACS::eCRITICAL_MSG;"+'\n';

			 }
			else if(msgType =="Debug")
			{ 
				strToWrite =  "const int "+msgName+" = _ACS::eDEBUG_MSG;"+'\n';

			 }
			else if(msgType =="Normal")
			{ 
				strToWrite =  "const int "+msgName+" = _ACS::eNORMAL_MSG;"+'\n';

			 }
	
			contents.insert(insertIndex, strToWrite);

			insertIndex = contents.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_DELAY>", 0);
			if(msgType =="Periodic")
			{ 
					strToWrite =  "const double "+msgName+" = "+msgDelay+" ;"+'\n';
					contents.insert(insertIndex, strToWrite);
			 }
			 }
			
		
		
		 }
		insertIndex = contents.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_ID>", 0);	
		contents.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_MSG_ID>").size());

		insertIndex = contents.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_TYPE>", 0);	
		contents.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_MSG_TYPE>").size());

		insertIndex = contents.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_DELAY>", 0);
		contents.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_MSG_DELAY>").size());
		 }
		modifyFile->close();
		modifyFile->remove();

		modifyFile = new QFile(filename);
		modifyFile->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite|QIODevice::Text);
		modifyFile->write(contents);
		modifyFile->close();
		

	
	 }


	
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
addMessagesToProcFiles
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString nom_sys, QDir Rep)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  
	  
	int insertIndex = 0;
	int beginIndex = 0;
	int endIndex = 0;

	QString tempFileName ;
	QString filename ;
	QString msgName; 
	QString msgId;
	QString msgType;
	QString lruName;
	QString msgDelay;
	QString msgFilter;
	QString strToWrite;
	

	

	QByteArray staticFunctionName;
	QByteArray voidFunctionName;
	QByteArray processorType;
	QByteArray lruIdNamespace ;
	QByteArray lruTypeNamespace ;
	QByteArray messageName ;
	QByteArray lruDelayNamespace;


	
	QFile *modifyFileProcH;
	QFile *modifyFileProcCpp;
	QFile *modifyFileProcFct;

	QFile *templateFileH;
	QFile *templateFileCpp;
	QFile *templateFileFct;

	QByteArray templateContentH;
	QByteArray templateContentCpp;
	QByteArray templateContentFct;

	QByteArray fileContentH;
	QByteArray fileContentCpp;
	QByteArray fileContentFct;

	QByteArray strToInsert;
	QDir messageDir(templatePath);

	
	if(messageDir.exists("Messages"))
	{ 	messageDir.cd("Messages");


	

	QMap<QString, listModel>::iterator msgProcIter = procReceivingMessage.begin();
	QList<messageModel*> msgModelList; 
	QList<messageModel*>::iterator msgModelIter; 

	for(; msgProcIter!=procReceivingMessage.end(); msgProcIter++ )
	{ 
			msgModelList = msgProcIter.value();
		
			processorType = msgProcIter.key();
			tempFileName= nom_sys+"_"+msgProcIter.key()+ ".h";
			filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);	
			modifyFileProcH = new QFile(filename);
			modifyFileProcH->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite|QIODevice::Text);
			fileContentH = modifyFileProcH->readAll();

			templateFileH = new QFile(messageDir.absoluteFilePath("processor_h.txt"));
			if(templateFileH->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite))
			{ 
				templateContentH = templateFileH->readAll();
				if(templateContentH.size()==0)
				{ 
					if(!missingFiles.contains(messageDir.absolutePath()+" rocessor_h.txt"))
					missingFiles.push_back(messageDir.absolutePath()+" rocessor_h.txt");
				 }

				templateFileH->close();
			
				
			 }
		



			tempFileName= nom_sys+"_"+msgProcIter.key()+ ".cpp";
			filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);	
			modifyFileProcCpp = new QFile(filename);
			modifyFileProcCpp->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite|QIODevice::Text);
			fileContentCpp = modifyFileProcCpp->readAll();

			templateFileCpp = new QFile(messageDir.absoluteFilePath("processor_cpp.txt"));
			if(templateFileCpp->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite))
			{ 
				templateContentCpp = templateFileCpp->readAll();
				if(templateContentCpp.size()==0)
				{ 
					if(!missingFiles.contains(messageDir.absolutePath()+" rocessor_cpp.txt"))
					missingFiles.push_back(messageDir.absolutePath()+" rocessor_cpp.txt");
				 }
				templateFileCpp->close();
		
			 }
		



			tempFileName= nom_sys+"_"+msgProcIter.key()+ "_fct.cpp";
			filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);	
			modifyFileProcFct = new QFile(filename);
			modifyFileProcFct->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite);
			fileContentFct = modifyFileProcFct->readAll();

			templateFileFct = new QFile(messageDir.absoluteFilePath("processor_fct.txt"));
			if(templateFileFct->open(QIODevice::ReadWrite|QIODevice::Text))
			{ 
				templateContentFct = templateFileFct->readAll();
			
				if(templateContentFct.size()==0)
				{ 
					if(!missingFiles.contains(messageDir.absolutePath()+" rocessor_fct.txt"))
					missingFiles.push_back(messageDir.absolutePath()+" rocessor_fct.txt");
				 }

				templateFileFct->close();
		
			
			 }

			
			

	for(msgModelIter = msgModelList.begin(); msgModelIter != msgModelList.end(); msgModelIter++)
		{ 
			if((*msgModelIter)->isValid())
			{ 

				
			msgName = (*msgModelIter)->getName();
			msgId = (*msgModelIter)->getID();
			msgType = (*msgModelIter)->getTypeMsg();
			msgDelay = (*msgModelIter)->getPeriodicity();
			msgFilter = (*msgModelIter)->getFilter();
			lruName = (*msgModelIter)->getLruName();


			insertIndex = fileContentH.indexOf("<INSERT_STATIC_MSG_FUNCTION>", 0);	
			beginIndex = templateContentH.indexOf("<STATIC_FUNCTION>", 0);
			beginIndex += QString("<STATIC_FUNCTION>").size();
			endIndex = templateContentH.indexOf("< TATIC_FUNCTION>");

			strToInsert = templateContentH.mid(beginIndex, endIndex-beginIndex);
			staticFunctionName = "On"+msgName+"Message";
			strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<STATIC_FUNCTION_NAME>"), staticFunctionName);
            fileContentH.insert(insertIndex, strToInsert);


			insertIndex = fileContentH.indexOf("<INSERT_VOID_MSG_FUNCTION>", 0);	
			beginIndex = templateContentH.indexOf("<VOID_FUNCTION>", 0);
			beginIndex += QString("<VOID_FUNCTION>").size();
			endIndex = templateContentH.indexOf("< OID_FUNCTION>");

			strToInsert = templateContentH.mid(beginIndex, endIndex-beginIndex);
			voidFunctionName = "on"+msgName+"Message";
			strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<VOID_FUNCTION_NAME>"),voidFunctionName);
            fileContentH.insert(insertIndex, strToInsert);


			insertIndex = fileContentFct.indexOf("<INSERT_STATIC_MSG_FUNCTION>", 0);	
			messageName = msgName+"_MESSAGE";
			templateContentFct.replace(QByteArray("<PROCESSOR_TYPE>"), processorType);
			templateContentFct.replace(QByteArray("<MESSAGE_NAME>"), messageName);
			templateContentFct.replace(QByteArray("<STATIC_FUNCTION_NAME>"), staticFunctionName);
			templateContentFct.replace(QByteArray("<VOID_FUNCTION_NAME>"),voidFunctionName);
			fileContentFct.insert(insertIndex, templateContentFct);

			insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_HANDLER>", 0);
			beginIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("<INIT>", 0);
			beginIndex += QString("<INIT>").size();
			endIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("< NIT>");

			lruTypeNamespace = lruName+"MsgType";
			lruIdNamespace = lruName+"MsgID";
			lruDelayNamespace = lruName+"MsgDelay";
				

			strToInsert = templateContentCpp.mid(beginIndex, endIndex-beginIndex);
			strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<MESSAGE_NAME>"), messageName);
			strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<STATIC_FUNCTION_NAME>"), staticFunctionName);
			strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<LRU_TYPE_NAMESPACE>"), lruTypeNamespace);
			strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<LRU_ID_NAMESPACE>"), lruIdNamespace);

			fileContentCpp.insert(insertIndex, strToInsert);
		
			if(msgFilter =="0")
			{ 
				insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_FILTER_CODE>", 0);
				beginIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("<FILTER>", 0);
				beginIndex += QString("<FILTER>").size();
				endIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("< ILTER>");
				
				strToInsert = templateContentCpp.mid(beginIndex, endIndex-beginIndex);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<MESSAGE_NAME>"), messageName);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<LRU_ID_NAMESPACE>"), lruIdNamespace);

				fileContentCpp.insert(insertIndex, strToInsert);
			
			 }
            

			if(msgType =="Periodic")
			{ 
				
				insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_PERIODIC_POWER_UP>", 0);
				beginIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("<COLD_POWER_UP>", 0);
				beginIndex += QString("<COLD_POWER_UP>").size();
				endIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("< OLD_POWER_UP>");
				
				strToInsert = templateContentCpp.mid(beginIndex, endIndex-beginIndex);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<MESSAGE_NAME>"), messageName);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<LRU_ID_NAMESPACE>"), lruIdNamespace);

				fileContentCpp.insert(insertIndex, strToInsert);
			
				insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_VOID_FUNCTIONS>", 0);
				beginIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("<PERIODIC_MESSAGE>", 0);
				beginIndex += QString("<PERIODIC_MESSAGE>").size();
				endIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("< ERIODIC_MESSAGE>");
				
				strToInsert = templateContentCpp.mid(beginIndex, endIndex-beginIndex);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<MESSAGE_NAME>"), messageName);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<LRU_ID_NAMESPACE>"), lruIdNamespace);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<VOID_FUNCTION_NAME>"), voidFunctionName);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<PROCESSOR_TYPE>"), processorType);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<LRU_DELAY_NAMESPACE>"), lruDelayNamespace);

				fileContentCpp.insert(insertIndex, strToInsert);
				
		


			 }
			else 
			{ 
		
				insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_VOID_FUNCTIONS>", 0);
				beginIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("<NON_PERIODIC_MESSAGE>", 0);
				beginIndex += QString("<NON_PERIODIC_MESSAGE>").size();
				endIndex = templateContentCpp.indexOf("< ON_PERIODIC_MESSAGE>");
			
				strToInsert = templateContentCpp.mid(beginIndex, endIndex-beginIndex);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<MESSAGE_NAME>"), messageName);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<VOID_FUNCTION_NAME>"), voidFunctionName);
				strToInsert.replace(QByteArray("<PROCESSOR_TYPE>"), processorType);
				
				fileContentCpp.insert(insertIndex, strToInsert);		
	
			 }
			 }
			else
			{ 
				break;
			 }
		
		
		 }

		insertIndex = fileContentH.indexOf("<INSERT_STATIC_MSG_FUNCTION>", 0);	
		fileContentH.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_STATIC_MSG_FUNCTION>").size());

		insertIndex = fileContentH.indexOf("<INSERT_VOID_MSG_FUNCTION>", 0);	
		fileContentH.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_VOID_MSG_FUNCTION>").size());
		
		modifyFileProcH->remove();
		modifyFileProcH->close();
			
		tempFileName= nom_sys+"_"+msgProcIter.key()+ ".h";
		filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);	
		modifyFileProcH = new QFile(filename);
		modifyFileProcH->open(QIODevice::WriteOnly|QIODevice::Text);
		modifyFileProcH->write(fileContentH);
		modifyFileProcH->close();
		


		insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_MSG_HANDLER>", 0);	
		fileContentCpp.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_MSG_HANDLER>").size());

		insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_FILTER_CODE>", 0);	
		fileContentCpp.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_FILTER_CODE>").size());

		insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_PERIODIC_POWER_UP>", 0);	
		fileContentCpp.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_PERIODIC_POWER_UP>").size());

		insertIndex = fileContentCpp.indexOf("<INSERT_VOID_FUNCTIONS>", 0);	
		fileContentCpp.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_VOID_FUNCTIONS>").size());

		modifyFileProcCpp->close();

		tempFileName= nom_sys+"_"+msgProcIter.key()+ ".cpp";
		filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);	
		modifyFileProcCpp = new QFile(filename);
		modifyFileProcCpp->open(QIODevice::WriteOnly|QIODevice::Text);
		modifyFileProcCpp->write(fileContentCpp);
		modifyFileProcCpp->close();


		insertIndex = fileContentFct.indexOf("<INSERT_STATIC_MSG_FUNCTION>", 0);	
		fileContentFct.remove(insertIndex,QString("<INSERT_STATIC_MSG_FUNCTION>").size());


		modifyFileProcFct->close();

		tempFileName= nom_sys+"_"+msgProcIter.key()+ "_fct.cpp";
		filename = getFilePath(tempFileName, Rep);	
		modifyFileProcFct = new QFile(filename);
		modifyFileProcFct->open(QIODevice::WriteOnly|QIODevice::Text);
		modifyFileProcFct->write(fileContentFct);
		modifyFileProcFct->close();


	
	 }

   }
  else
  { 
	  if(!missingFolders.contains(messageDir.absolutePath()+" essages/"))
	  missingFolders.push_back(messageDir.absolutePath()+" essages/");

	  	
   }
  
  
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
generateMakefile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString projectFilePath, QByteArray contents)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


	QDomDocument doc; 
    
	doc.setContent(contents,true);
	
	QDomNodeList childNodes = doc.childNodes();	

	QDomNode nodeVisualStudio = childNodes.item(childNodes.size()-1);

	QDomNode fileNode = nodeVisualStudio.namedItem("Files");
	
	QDomElement sourceFile ;
	
	
	sourceFile = fileNode.toDocument().createElement("Filter");
	sourceFile.setAttribute("Name", "Source Files");
	sourceFile.setAttribute("Filter", "");

	addSystem(sourceFile,projectFilePath );
	addLru(sourceFile,projectFilePath);
	addProcessor(sourceFile, projectFilePath);
	addParameterTable(sourceFile, projectFilePath);


	fileNode.appendChild(sourceFile);

	int begin = contents.indexOf("<Files>");
	int endOfFiles = contents.indexOf("<Globals>");

	contents.remove(begin, endOfFiles-begin);
	
	QDomDocument testdoc;
	QDomElement myelem= testdoc.createElement("myelem");
	QDomNode mynode = testdoc.importNode(fileNode, true);
	myelem = mynode.toElement();
	testdoc.appendChild(myelem);

	
	QFile file(projectFilePath);
	file.open(QIODevice::WriteOnly);

	
	QByteArray ba = testdoc.toByteArray();
	QByteArray removed = "" ;
	begin = 0;
	int crochet = 0;
	int end = 0;

	QByteArray mid = "";


	begin = ba.indexOf("Filter=", 0);
	while(begin>0)
	{ 
	
		end = ba.indexOf("Name", begin);
		
		if(end>0)
		{ 
			mid = ba.mid(begin,end-begin );
			ba.remove(begin, end-begin);			
			crochet = ba.indexOf(">", begin);
			ba.insert(crochet,mid);
			mid.clear();
			crochet = ba.indexOf(">", begin);		
			begin = ba.indexOf("Filter=", crochet);
			
		 }
			
	 }


	endOfFiles = contents.indexOf("<Globals>");
	contents.insert(endOfFiles, ba);

	file.write(contents);
	
	file.close();
		 


 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
addSystem
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDomNode  & sourceFile, QString vcprojPath)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QDomElement systemElem ;
	QStringList temp ;
	QString relativeTempPath = ""; 
	
	QDir   vcprojDir = QFileInfo(vcprojPath).absoluteDir();
	

	int i = 0;

	QMap<QString, genProject*>::iterator sysIter = systemConfig.begin();
	for(; sysIter!=systemConfig.end(); sysIter++)
	{ 
		temp = sysIter.value()->getFileList();	

		for(i = 0; i<temp.size(); i++)
		{ 
			systemElem  = sourceFile.toDocument().createElement("File");
			relativeTempPath = vcprojDir.relativeFilePath(temp[i]);
			
			systemElem.setAttribute("RelativePath",relativeTempPath );
			sourceFile.appendChild(systemElem);
		 }

	 }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
addProcessor
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDomNode  &sourceFile, QString vcprojPath)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
    QDomNodeList sourceChildren = sourceFile.childNodes();
	int correctNodeIndex = 0;
	QDomNode parentNode; 
	QString parentType;

	QDomElement systemElem , sysProc;
	QStringList temp ;
	QString relativeTempPath = ""; 

	QDir   vcprojDir = QFileInfo(vcprojPath).absoluteDir();

	int i = 0;

	QMap<QString, genProject*>::iterator procIter = processorConfig.begin();
		QMap<QString, genProject*>::iterator procIterEnd = processorConfig.end();
		


	while(procIter!=procIterEnd)
	{ 

		parentType = procIter.value()->getParentType();
		
		if(parentType =="Source Files")
			parentNode = sourceFile;
		else
		{ 
			for(i = 0; i<sourceChildren.size(); i++)
			{ 
				if(sourceChildren.item(i).toElement().attribute("Name")==parentType)
				{  correctNodeIndex = i;
					break;
				 }
			 }
			parentNode = sourceChildren.item(correctNodeIndex);
			
		 }

		temp = procIter.value()->getFileList();	
		sysProc = parentNode.toDocument().createElement("Filter");
		sysProc.setAttribute("Name", procIter.key());
		sysProc.setAttribute("Filter", "");
	

		for(i = 0; i<temp.size(); i++)
		{ 
			systemElem  = sysProc.toDocument().createElement("File");
			relativeTempPath = vcprojDir.relativeFilePath(temp[i]);
			systemElem.setAttribute("RelativePath",relativeTempPath );
			sysProc.appendChild(systemElem);
		 }
		parentNode.appendChild(sysProc);
		if(parentNode!=sourceFile)
			sourceFile.appendChild(parentNode);

		procIter++;
	
	 }
	
	

 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
addParameterTable
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDomNode & sourceFile, QString vcprojPath)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QDomNodeList sourceChildren = sourceFile.childNodes();
	int correctNodeIndex = 0;
	QDomNode parentNode; 
	QString parentType;

	QDomElement systemElem , sysProc;
	QStringList temp ;
	QString relativeTempPath = ""; 

	QDir   vcprojDir = QFileInfo(vcprojPath).absoluteDir();

	int i = 0;
	
	QMap<QString, genProject*>::iterator parTblIter = parTableConfig.begin();
	QMap<QString, genProject*>::iterator parTblIterEnd = parTableConfig.end();
		


	while(parTblIter!=parTblIterEnd)
	{ 

		parentType = parTblIter.value()->getParentType();
		
		if(parentType =="Source Files")
			parentNode = sourceFile;
		else
		{ 
			for(i = 0; i<sourceChildren.size(); i++)
			{ 
				if(sourceChildren.item(i).toElement().attribute("Name")==parentType)
				{  correctNodeIndex = i;
					break;
				 }
			 }
			parentNode = sourceChildren.item(correctNodeIndex);
			
		 }

		temp = parTblIter.value()->getFileList();	
		sysProc = parentNode.toDocument().createElement("Filter");
		sysProc.setAttribute("Name", parTblIter.key());
		sysProc.setAttribute("Filter", "");
	

		for(i = 0; i<temp.size(); i++)
		{ 
			systemElem  = sysProc.toDocument().createElement("File");
			
			relativeTempPath = vcprojDir.relativeFilePath(temp[i]);
			systemElem.setAttribute("RelativePath",relativeTempPath );
			sysProc.appendChild(systemElem);
		 }
		parentNode.appendChild(sysProc);
		if(parentNode!=sourceFile)
			sourceFile.appendChild(parentNode);

		parTblIter++;
	
	 }

 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
mapDirectory
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QDir pere, QString fils)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QStringList fileList , dirList;
	pere.cd(fils);
	
		fileList  = pere.entryList(QDir::Files);
	
		for(int i = 0; i<fileList.size(); i++)
		{ 
			
			mapDir[fileList[i]] = pere.absoluteFilePath(fileList[i]);
			pere.remove(pere.absoluteFilePath(fileList[i]));

			
		 }
		dirList = pere.entryList(QDir::Dirs);
			for(int j = 0; j< dirList.size(); j++)
			{ 
				if(dirList[j] != "." && dirList[j] != "..")
				{ 
					mapDir[dirList[j]] = pere.absoluteFilePath(dirList[j]);
					mapDirectory(pere, dirList[j]);
					
				 }
			
			 }
	pere.cdUp();
	
 }
__END_BODY__

  addTab(mFormats, "Formats");

  mPages = new CPage(this);
  mPages->setObjectName("Pages");

  addTab(mPages, "Pages");





  mProperties = new CProperties(this);

  QMap<QString, QVariant> extra;
  extra["minimum"] = 1;
  extra["maximum"] = 99;
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Number of lines");
  mProperties->setProperty("Lines", 1, extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["minimum"] = 1;
  extra["maximum"] = 99;
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Number of columns");
  mProperties->setProperty("Columns", 1, extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Line Select key. This list specify the LS key position. Space is used as separator.");
  mProperties->setProperty("LS_Keys", "", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Default page name.");
  mProperties->setProperty("Default_Page", QStringList(), extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Scratchpad type.");
  QStringList type;
  type << "acs_Scratchpad" << "acs_ScratchNZ";
  mProperties->setProperty("Type", type, extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["minimum"] = 1;
  extra["maximum"] = 99;
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Scratchpad line position.");
  mProperties->setProperty("Position", 0, extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Scratchpad delete annunciation.");
  mProperties->setProperty("Delete_Annunc", "", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Text for Invalid Entry generic page.");
  mProperties->setProperty("Invalid_Entry", "INVALID ENTRY", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Text for Not Suported generic page.");
  mProperties->setProperty("Not_Suported", "NOT SUPORTED", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Text for In Development generic page.");
  mProperties->setProperty("In_Development", "IN DEVELOPMENT", extra);

  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Enter text control document comment");
  mProperties->setProperty("comment", "", extra);





  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mMainWindow, SLOT(slotUpdateModIndicator()));

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



  CMarkup xml;
  if ( !xml.load(fn) )
  { 
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "XML document error.");
    return false;
   }



  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  xml.findElem();
  xml.intoElem();


  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("int");
  mProperties->setProperty("Lines", atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str()));


  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("int");
  mProperties->setProperty("Columns", atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str()));


  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("string");
  mProperties->setProperty("Invalid_Entry", xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str());


  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("string");
  mProperties->setProperty("Not_Suported", xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str());


  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("string");
  mProperties->setProperty("In_Development", xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str());


  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("int");




  xml.findElem("collection");
  mKeys->load(xml);


  xml.findElem("object");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findElem("class");
  mProperties->setProperty("Type", xml.getData().c_str());
  xml.findElem("contents");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("int");
  mProperties->setProperty("Position", atoi(xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str()));
  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findElem("value");
  xml.findChildElem("string");
  mProperties->setProperty("Delete_Annunc", xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str());
  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();


  xml.findElem("object");


  xml.findElem("collection");
  mFormats->load(xml);


  xml.findElem("collection");
  mPages->load(xml);





  xml.findElem("properties");
  xml.findChildElem();
  mProperties->setProperty("LS_Keys", xml.getChildData().c_str());
  xml.findChildElem();
  mProperties->setProperty("Comment", xml.getChildData().c_str());

  xml.outOfElem();


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
writeFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( fn.isEmpty() )
  { 
    fn = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(".", filter(), 0);

    if ( fn.isEmpty() )
      return false;
    else if ( QFileInfo(fn).extension(false).isEmpty() )
      fn += ".wgd";
   }

  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  CMarkup xml;
  xml.setDoc("<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n");
  xml.addElem("ACS");
  xml.addAttrib("type", "textcontrol");
  xml.addAttrib("version", glb::version);

  xml.intoElem();






  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "lines");
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("int");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("Lines").toInt());


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "columns");
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("int");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("Columns").toInt());


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "invalid entry");
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("string");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("Invalid_Entry").toString().toAscii().data());


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "not suported");
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("string");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("Not_Suported").toString().toAscii().data());


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "in development");
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("string");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("In_Development").toString().toAscii().data());


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "default page");
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("int");


  xml.addChildAttrib("val", 0);


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "keys");
  mKeys->save(xml);


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "scratchpad");
  xml.addElem("object");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("class");
  xml.addAttrib("schema", 0);
  xml.setData(mProperties->value("Type").toString().toAscii().data());
  xml.addElem("contents");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("int");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("Position").toInt());
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("int");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("Columns").toInt());
  xml.addElem("value");
  xml.addChildElem("string");
  xml.addChildAttrib("val", mProperties->value("Delete_Annunc").toString().toAscii().data());
  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "message stack");
  xml.addElem("object");
  xml.addChildElem("class");
  xml.addChildAttrib("schema", 0);
  xml.setChildData("acs_MsgStack");
  xml.addChildElem("contents");


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "formats");
  mFormats->save(xml);


  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "pages");
  mPages->save(xml);





  xml.addNode(CMarkup::MNT_COMMENT, "properties");
  xml.addElem("properties");
  xml.addChildElem("line_select");
  xml.setChildData(mProperties->value("LS_Keys").toString().toAscii().data());
  xml.addChildElem("comment");
  xml.setChildData(mProperties->value("Comment").toString().toAscii().data());

  xml.outOfElem();





  if ( !xml.save(fn) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(fn);
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "FMS Editor", message);

    QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
    return false;
   }


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

{

    list << QString("%1L").arg(i + 1);

  return list;

__BEGIN_NAME__
maybeSave
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( isModified() )
  { 
    QString fn = QFileInfo(filename()).fileName();
    int ret = QMessageBox::warning( 0,
                                    "Editor",
                                    QString("File %1 has been modified.\n"
                                            "Do you want to save your changes?").arg(fn),
                                    QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::Default,
                                    QMessageBox::No,
                                    QMessageBox::Cancel | QMessageBox::Escape );
    if ( ret == QMessageBox::Yes )
      return writeFile(filename());
    else if ( ret == QMessageBox::Cancel )
      return false;
   }
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

  mAddAct = new QAction(tr("&Add"), this);
  mAddAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage lement_add_24.png"));
  mAddAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds format"));
  connect(mAddAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), mPage, SLOT(slotAddPage()));

  mEditAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits format"));
  connect(mEditAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), mPage, SLOT(slotEditPage()));

  mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
  mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
  mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
  mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
  connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), mPage, SLOT(slotDeletePage()));





  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mPage, SIGNAL(modified()));
 }

  setObjectName("thePageList");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_16.png"));

  mPage = qobject_cast<CPage *>(parent);





  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
  setHorizontalScrollBarPolicy(Qt::ScrollBarAlwaysOff);
  setMinimumSize(250, 0);





  mAddAct = new QAction(tr("&Add"), this);
  mAddAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage lement_add_24.png"));
  mAddAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds format"));
  connect(mAddAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), mPage, SLOT(slotAddPage()));

  mEditAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits format"));
  connect(mEditAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), mPage, SLOT(slotEditPage()));

  mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
  mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
  mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
  mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
  connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), mPage, SLOT(slotDeletePage()));
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 

  for ( int i = 0; i < mPageStack->count(); ++i )
    mPageStack->removeWidget(mPageStack->widget(i));
  mPageList->clear();

  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findElem("vector");
  xml.intoElem();

  while ( xml.findElem("collection") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.findElem("pair");
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.findElem("collection");

    CPageView *page = new CPageView(this);
    page->load(xml);
    mPageStack->addWidget(page);

    xml.findElem("value");
    xml.findChildElem("string");
    QString name = xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str();

    CPageItem *item = new CPageItem(mPageList);
    item->setText(name);
    item->setPage(page);

    xml.outOfElem();
    xml.outOfElem();
   }

  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
save
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.addElem("collection");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("vector");
  xml.addAttrib("size", mPageList->count());
  xml.intoElem();

  for ( int i = 0; i < mPageList->count(); ++i )
  { 
    CPageItem *item = static_cast<CPageItem *>(mPageList->item(i));

    xml.addElem("collection");
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.addElem("pair");
    xml.intoElem();

    item->page()->save(xml);

    xml.addElem("value");
    xml.addChildElem("string");
    xml.addChildAttrib("val", item->text().toAscii().data());

    xml.outOfElem();
    xml.outOfElem();
    xml.outOfElem();
   }

  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__

{ 
  if ( typeEdit->currentText() == "acs_CharKey" )
    return charEdit->text();
  else if ( typeEdit->currentText() == "acs_ModeKey" )
    return QString::number(modeEdit->currentIndex());
  else if ( typeEdit->currentText() == "acs_LSKey" )
    return QString::number(lsEdit->currentIndex());

    return QString();

__BEGIN_NAME__
QTreeWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setObjectName("theKey");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_16.png"));

  mTextControl = qobject_cast<CTextControl *>(parent);
  mBase = Dec;





  setColumnCount(4);
  QStringList headers;
  headers << tr("ID") << tr("Type") << tr("Value") << tr("paging");
  setHeaderLabels(headers);
  header()->setSortIndicatorShown(false);
  header()->setClickable(false);
  header()->resizeSection(0, 100);
  header()->resizeSection(1, 150);
  header()->setResizeMode(2, QHeaderView::Stretch);
  hideColumn(3);

  setRootIsDecorated(false);
  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);





  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemDoubleClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotDoubleClick()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mTextControl, SIGNAL(modified()));





  CKeyItem *prev = 0;
  for ( int i = 0; i < 128; ++i )
  { 
    CKeyItem *item = new CKeyItem(this, prev);

    if ( isupper(i) || isdigit(i) )
    { 
      item->setText(1, "acs_CharKey");
      item->setText(2, QString(i));
     }
    else
      item->setText(1, "acs_NullKey");

    prev = item;
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  clear();

  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findElem("vector");
  xml.intoElem();

  CKeyItem *prev = 0;
  while ( xml.findElem("object") )
  { 
    CKeyItem *item = new CKeyItem(this, prev);
    item->load(xml);
    prev = item;
   }

  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__

save

__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.addElem("collection");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("vector");
  xml.addAttrib("size", 128);
  xml.intoElem();
  for ( int i = 0; i < topLevelItemCount(); ++i )
    static_cast<CKeyItem *>(topLevelItem(i))->save(xml);
  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotEdit
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CKeyItem *item = static_cast<CKeyItem *>(currentItem());

  CKeyEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.typeEdit->setCurrentText(item->text(1));
  dialog.modeEdit->addItems(mTextControl->pageList());
  dialog.lsEdit->addItems(mTextControl->lsList());
  dialog.setValue(item->text(2));
  dialog.pagingEdit->setChecked(item->text(3) == "true");
  dialog.refresh();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
    QString value = dialog.value();
    QString paging = dialog.pagingEdit->isChecked() ? "true" : "false";

    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "edit key"));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CKeyCmdEdit("", item, 1, type));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CKeyCmdEdit("", item, 2, value));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CKeyCmdEdit("", item, 3, paging));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "edit key"));
    emit modified();
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

(CMarkup &xml)

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findElem("class");
  setText(1, xml.getData().c_str());

  if ( text(1) == "acs_CharKey" ||  text(1) == "acs_LSKey" )
  { 
    xml.findElem("contents");
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.findElem("value");
    xml.findChildElem("int");
    setText(2, xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str());
    xml.outOfElem();
   }
  else if ( text(1) == "acs_ModeKey" )
  { 
    xml.findElem("contents");
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.findElem("value");
    xml.findChildElem("int");
    setText(2, xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str());
    xml.findElem("value");
    xml.findChildElem("bool");
    setText(3, xml.getChildAttrib("val").c_str());
    xml.outOfElem();
   }

  xml.outOfElem();
 }

{ 
  xml.addElem("object");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("class");
  xml.addAttrib("schema", 0);
  xml.setData(text(1).toAscii().data());
  xml.addElem("contents");

  if ( text(1) == "acs_CharKey" || text(1) == "acs_LSKey" )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.addElem("value");
    xml.addChildElem("int");
    xml.addChildAttrib("val", text(2).toAscii().data());
    xml.outOfElem();
   }
  else if ( text(1) == "acs_ModeKey" )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();

    xml.addChildAttrib("val", text(2).toAscii().data());
    xml.addElem("value");
    xml.addChildElem("bool");
    xml.addChildAttrib("val", text(3).toAscii().data());
    xml.outOfElem();
   }
  xml.outOfElem();
 }

{ 
  QListWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

  for ( int i = 0; i < mParent->count(); ++i )
    if ( mParent->widget(i)->objectName() == item->text() )
      mParent->setCurrentIndex(i);

{ 
  QString name = typeEdit->currentText();

  if ( name == "acs_StringFormat" )
  { 
    bandLabel->hide();
    bandEdit->hide();
    minLabel->hide();
    minEdit->hide();
    maxLabel->hide();
    maxEdit->hide();
    scaleLabel->hide();
    scaleEdit->hide();
    fmtEdit->setEnabled(true);
   }
  else if ( name == "acs_ValueFormat" )
  { 
    bandLabel->hide();
    bandEdit->hide();
    minLabel->show();
    minEdit->show();
    maxLabel->show();
    maxEdit->show();
    scaleLabel->show();
    scaleEdit->show();
    fmtEdit->setEnabled(true);
   }
  else if ( name == "acs_AngleFormat" )
  { 
    bandLabel->hide();
    bandEdit->hide();
    minLabel->show();
    minEdit->show();
    maxLabel->show();
    maxEdit->show();
    scaleLabel->show();
    scaleEdit->show();
    fmtEdit->setEnabled(true);
   }
  else if ( name == "acs_TimeFormat" )
  { 
    bandLabel->hide();
    bandEdit->hide();
    minLabel->hide();
    minEdit->hide();
    maxLabel->hide();
    maxEdit->hide();
    scaleLabel->hide();
    scaleEdit->hide();
    fmtEdit->setEnabled(true);
   }
  else if ( name == "acs_FreqFormat" )
  { 
    bandLabel->show();
    bandEdit->show();
    minLabel->hide();
    minEdit->hide();
    maxLabel->hide();
    maxEdit->hide();
    scaleLabel->hide();
    scaleEdit->hide();
    fmtEdit->setEnabled(true);
   }
  else if ( name == "acs_AltitudeFormat" )
  { 
    bandLabel->hide();
    bandEdit->hide();
    minLabel->show();
    minEdit->show();
    maxLabel->show();
    maxEdit->show();
    scaleLabel->hide();
    scaleEdit->hide();
    fmtEdit->setText("");
    fmtEdit->setEnabled(false);
   }

  { 
    bandLabel->hide();

    minLabel->hide();
    minEdit->hide();
    maxLabel->hide();

  adjustSize();

{ 
  setObjectName("theFormat");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_16.png"));

  mTextControl = qobject_cast<CTextControl *>(parent);





  setColumnCount(11);
  QStringList headers;
  headers << tr("Format") << tr("Type");
  setHeaderLabels(headers);
  header()->setSortIndicatorShown(false);
  header()->setClickable(false);
  header()->resizeSection(0, 200);
  header()->setResizeMode(1, QHeaderView::Stretch);
  hideColumn(2);
  hideColumn(3);
  hideColumn(4);
  hideColumn(5);
  hideColumn(6);
  hideColumn(7);
  hideColumn(8);
  hideColumn(9);
  hideColumn(10);

  setRootIsDecorated(false);
  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);





  mAddAct = new QAction(tr("&Add"), this);
  mAddAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage lement_add_24.png"));
  mAddAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds format"));
  connect(mAddAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAdd()));

  mEditAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits format"));
  connect(mEditAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEdit()));

  mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
  mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
  mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
  mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
  connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDelete()));





  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemDoubleClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotDoubleClick()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mTextControl, SIGNAL(modified()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), this, SLOT(slotSort()));
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:0 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:0 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/textcontrol/format/format.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:4 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:121 L_END:123 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:CFormat NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:0 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  clear();

  xml.intoElem();
  xml.findElem("vector");
  xml.intoElem();

  while ( xml.findElem("object") )
  { 
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.findElem("class");
    QString type = xml.getData().c_str();
    xml.findElem("contents");
    xml.intoElem();

    CFormatItem *item = 0;

    if ( type == "acs_StringFormat" )
      item = new CStringFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_ValueFormat" )
      item = new CValueFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_AngleFormat" )
      item = new CAngleFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_TimeFormat" )
      item = new CTimeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_FreqFormat" )
      item = new CFreqFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_AltitudeFormat" )
      item = new CAltitudeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_LatitudeFormat" )
      item = new CLatitudeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_LongitudeFormat" )
      item = new CLongitudeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_FixedWidthFormat" )
      item = new CFixedWidthFormatItem(this);

    if ( item )
      item->load(xml);

    xml.outOfElem();
    xml.outOfElem();
   }

  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
save
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.addElem("collection");
  xml.intoElem();
  xml.addElem("vector");
  xml.addAttrib("size", topLevelItemCount());
  xml.intoElem();
  for ( int i = 0; i < topLevelItemCount(); ++i )
  { 
    CFormatItem *item = static_cast<CFormatItem *>(topLevelItem(i));

    xml.addElem("object");
    xml.intoElem();
    xml.addElem("class");
    xml.addAttrib("schema", 0);
    xml.setData(item->text(1).toAscii().data());
    xml.addElem("contents");
    xml.intoElem();
    item->save(xml);
    xml.outOfElem();
    xml.outOfElem();
   }
  xml.outOfElem();
  xml.outOfElem();
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotAdd
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CFormatEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.setWindowTitle("Add Format");

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
    QString type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
    QString color = QString::number(dialog.colorEdit->currentIndex());
    QString separator = dialog.sepEdit->text();
    QString invalid = dialog.invEdit->text();
    QString regExp = dialog.regExpEdit->text();
    QString format = dialog.fmtEdit->text();
    QString min = dialog.minEdit->text();
    QString max = dialog.maxEdit->text();
    QString scale = dialog.scaleEdit->text();
    QString band = QString::number(dialog.bandEdit->currentIndex());

    QTreeWidgetItem *item = 0;
    if ( type == "acs_StringFormat" )
      item = new CStringFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_ValueFormat" )
      item = new CValueFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_AngleFormat" )
      item = new CAngleFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_TimeFormat" )
      item = new CTimeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_FreqFormat" )
      item = new CFreqFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_AltitudeFormat" )
      item = new CAltitudeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_LatitudeFormat" )
      item = new CLatitudeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_LongitudeFormat" )
      item = new CLongitudeFormatItem(this);
    else if ( type == "acs_FixedWidthFormat" )
      item = new CFixedWidthFormatItem(this);

    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "add format"));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdAdd("", item));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 0, name));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 1, type));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 2, color));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 3, separator));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 4, invalid));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 5, regExp));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 6, format));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 7, min));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 8, max));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 9, scale));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 10, band));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "add format"));
    emit modified();
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
slotEdit
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CFormatItem *item = static_cast<CFormatItem *>(currentItem());

  CFormatEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.setWindowTitle("Edit Format");
  dialog.nameEdit->setText(item->text(0));
  dialog.typeEdit->setCurrentIndex(dialog.typeEdit->findText(item->text(1)));
  dialog.typeEdit->setEnabled(false);
  dialog.colorEdit->setCurrentIndex(item->text(2).toInt());
  dialog.sepEdit->setText(item->text(3));
  dialog.invEdit->setText(item->text(4));
  dialog.invEdit->setMaxLength(mTextControl->prop().value("Columns").toInt());
  dialog.regExpEdit->setText(item->text(5));
  dialog.fmtEdit->setText(item->text(6));
  dialog.minEdit->setText(item->text(7));
  dialog.maxEdit->setText(item->text(8));
  dialog.scaleEdit->setText(item->text(9));
  dialog.bandEdit->setCurrentIndex(item->text(10).toInt());
  dialog.refresh();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
    QString type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
    QString color = QString::number(dialog.colorEdit->currentIndex());
    QString separator = dialog.sepEdit->text();
    QString invalid = dialog.invEdit->text();
    QString regExp = dialog.regExpEdit->text();
    QString format = dialog.fmtEdit->text();
    QString min = dialog.minEdit->text();
    QString max = dialog.maxEdit->text();
    QString scale = dialog.scaleEdit->text();
    QString band = QString::number(dialog.bandEdit->currentIndex());

    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "edit format"));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 0, name));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 1, type));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 2, color));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 3, separator));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 4, invalid));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 5, regExp));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 6, format));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 7, min));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 8, max));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 9, scale));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CFormatCmdEdit("", item, 10, band));
    mTextControl->undoStack().push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "edit format"));
    emit modified();
   }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenuEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QContextMenuEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

  if ( item == 0 )
    return;

  QMenu menu(this);
  menu.addAction(mAddAct);
  menu.addAction(mEditAct);
  menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
  menu.exec(event->globalPos());

()

{ 
  QWidgetList list = windowList(CreationOrder);
  int h = height() / list.count();
  int y = 0;
  for ( QWidgetList::iterator it = list.begin(); it != list.end(); ++it )
  { 
    (*it)->parentWidget()->resize(width(), h);
    (*it)->parentWidget()->move(0, y);
    y += h;
   }
 }

filename

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( list->currentItem()->text() == "Project File" )
    return QFileInfo(QDir(dirEdit->text()), fileEdit->text() + ".acs").absFilePath();

  else if ( list->currentItem()->text() == "Parameter File" )
    return QFileInfo(QDir(dirEdit->text()), fileEdit->text() + ".par").absFilePath();

  else if ( list->currentItem()->text() == "Option File" )
    return QFileInfo(QDir(dirEdit->text()), fileEdit->text() + ".opt").absFilePath();

  else if ( list->currentItem()->text() == "Widget File" )
    return QFileInfo(QDir(dirEdit->text()), fileEdit->text() + ".wgd").absFilePath();

  else if ( list->currentItem()->text() == "Text Control File" )
    return QFileInfo(QDir(dirEdit->text()), fileEdit->text() + ".tcd").absFilePath();

  else if ( list->currentItem()->text() == "Text File" )
    return QFileInfo(QDir(dirEdit->text()), fileEdit->text() + ".txt").absFilePath();

  return QString();
 }

{ 
	if (list->currentRow() > 0)
		systemEdit->setEnabled(false);
	else
		systemEdit->setEnabled(true);

	{ 
		if ((list->currentRow() == 0) && !systemEdit->text().isEmpty())
		{ 
			okButton->setEnabled(true);
			return;
		 }
		else if(list->currentRow() > 0)
		{ 
			okButton->setEnabled(true);
			return;
		 }
	 }
	okButton->setEnabled(false);

__BEGIN_NAME__
on_okButton_clicked
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
	QString path;
	if (list->currentRow() == 0)
		path = dirEdit->text() + "/" + systemEdit->text() + " onfi efault/" + fileEdit->text() + ".acs";
	else
		path = filename();
	QFileInfo file(path);
	if (file.exists())
	{ 
		int res = QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "The file already exists.  Do you want to overwrite it?", 
			QMessageBox::Yes, QMessageBox::No, QMessageBox::NoButton);
		if (res == QMessageBox::Yes)
			setResult(QDialog::Accepted);
		else
			setResult(QDialog::Rejected);
		return;
	 }

	QDir dir(dirEdit->text() + "/" + systemEdit->text());
	if ((list->currentRow() == 0) && (dir.exists()))
	{ 
		int res = QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "The system already exists.  Choose another system name.", 
			QMessageBox::Ok, QMessageBox::NoButton, QMessageBox::NoButton);
		setResult(QDialog::Rejected);
		return;
	 }
	setResult(QDialog::Accepted);
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
QDialog
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent, "CConfigEditDialog")
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  mDialog = type;

  if ( type == System )
    setCaption("System Edit");
  else if ( type == LRU )
    setCaption("LRU Edit");
  else if ( type == Table )
    setCaption("Parameter Table Edit");
  else if ( type == Interface )
    setCaption("Interface Edit");
  else if ( type == PowerSupply )
    setCaption("Power Supply Edit");
  else if ( type == Processor )
    setCaption("Processor Edit");
  else
    setCaption("Value Edit");

  mLayout = new QGridLayout(this, 1, 1, 11, 6);
  mLayout->setObjectName("Layout");





  mNameLabel = new QLabel(this);
  mNameLabel->setObjectName("NameLabel");
  mNameLabel->setText(tr("Name:"));
  QToolTip::add(mNameLabel, tr("Value name"));
  Q3WhatsThis::add(mNameLabel, tr("This entry defines the value name."));
  mLayout->addWidget(mNameLabel, 0, 0);

  mName = new QLineEdit(this);
  mName->setObjectName("Name");
  mLayout->addWidget(mName, 0, 1);
  connect(mName, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotEnableButton()));

  if ( mDialog != Value )
  { 
    mNameLabel->hide();
    mName->hide();
   }





  mTypeLabel = new QLabel(this);
  mTypeLabel->setObjectName("TypeLabel");
  mTypeLabel->setText(tr( "Type:"));
  QToolTip::add(mTypeLabel, tr("Value Type"));
  Q3WhatsThis::add(mTypeLabel, tr("This entry defines the value type."));
  mLayout->addWidget(mTypeLabel, 1, 0);

  if ( mDialog == System )
  { 
    QLineEdit *temp = new QLineEdit(this);
    temp->setMinimumSize(QSize(225, 0));
    temp->setText("acs_System");
    connect(temp, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotEnableButton()));

    mType = temp;
   }
  else if ( mDialog == LRU )
  { 
    QLineEdit *temp = new QLineEdit(this);
    temp->setMinimumSize(QSize(225, 0));
    temp->setText("acs_LRU");
    connect(temp, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotEnableButton()));

    mType = temp;
   }
  else if ( mDialog == Table )
  { 
    QLineEdit *temp = new QLineEdit(this);
    temp->setMinimumSize(QSize(225, 0));
    temp->setText("ParTbl");
    connect(temp, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotEnableButton()));

    mType = temp;
   }
  else if ( mDialog == Interface )
  { 
    QLineEdit *temp = new QLineEdit(this);
    temp->setMinimumSize(QSize(225, 0));
    temp->setText("acs_Interface");
    connect(temp, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotEnableButton()));

    mType = temp;
   }
  else if ( mDialog == PowerSupply )
  { 
    QLineEdit *temp = new QLineEdit(this);
    temp->setMinimumSize(QSize(225, 0));
    temp->setText("acs_PowerSupply");
    connect(temp, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotEnableButton()));

    mType = temp;
   }
  else if ( mDialog == Processor )
  { 
    QComboBox *temp = new QComboBox(this);
    temp->setMinimumSize(QSize(225, 0));
    temp->setEditable(true);
    temp->insertItem(tr("acs_Processor"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("acs_WidgetDriver"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("acs_ProtocolEmulator"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("acs_TextControlDriver"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("acs_CautionsAdvisoriesManager"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("acs_GraphicController"));
    connect(temp, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotEnableButton()));

    mType = temp;
   }
  else
  { 
    QComboBox *temp = new QComboBox(this);
    temp->setMinimumSize(QSize(225, 0));
    temp->insertItem(tr("bool"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("int"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("double"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("string"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("band"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("side"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("xside"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("file"));
    temp->insertItem(tr("path"));
    connect(temp, SIGNAL(textChanged(const QString &)), this, SLOT(slotReresh()));

    mType = temp;
   }
  mLayout->addWidget(mType, 1, 1);





  mValueLabel = new QLabel(this);
  mValueLabel->setObjectName("ValueLabel");
  mValueLabel->setText(tr("Value:"));
  QToolTip::add(mValueLabel, tr("Value"));
  Q3WhatsThis::add(mValueLabel, tr("This entry defines the value data."));
  mLayout->addWidget(mValueLabel, 2, 0);

  QLineEdit *temp = new QLineEdit(this);
  mLayout->addWidget(temp, 2, 1);
  mValue = temp;

  mBrowse = new QToolButton(this);
  mBrowse->setObjectName("Browse");
  mBrowse->setMinimumSize(20, 20);
  mBrowse->setText("...");
  mBrowse->hide();
  QToolTip::add(mBrowse, "Browses file");
  mLayout->addWidget(mBrowse, 2, 2);
  connect(mBrowse, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(slotBrowse()));

  QSpacerItem *spacer = new QSpacerItem(20, 20, QSizePolicy::Minimum, QSizePolicy::Expanding);
  mLayout->addItem(spacer, 3, 1);

  if ( mDialog != Value )
  { 
    mValueLabel->hide();
    mValue->hide();
   }





  QVBoxLayout *buttonLayout = new QVBoxLayout(0, 0, 6);

  mOkButton = new QPushButton(this);
  mOkButton->setObjectName("OkButton");
  mOkButton->setEnabled(false);
  mOkButton->setText(tr("OK"));
  mOkButton->setAccel(QKeySequence(tr("Return")));
  buttonLayout->addWidget(mOkButton);
  connect(mOkButton, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(accept()));

  mCancelButton = new QPushButton(this);
  mCancelButton->setObjectName("CancelButon");
  mCancelButton->setText(tr("Cancel"));
  mCancelButton->setAccel(QKeySequence(tr("Esc")));
  buttonLayout->addWidget(mCancelButton);
  connect(mCancelButton, SIGNAL(clicked()), this, SLOT(reject()));

  spacer = new QSpacerItem(20, 20, QSizePolicy::Minimum, QSizePolicy::Expanding);
  buttonLayout->addItem(spacer);

  mLayout->addMultiCellLayout(buttonLayout, 0, 3, 3, 3);


  resize(QSize(401, 127).expandedTo(minimumSizeHint()));
  slotEnableButton();
 }

{

  if ( type() == "file" )
    name = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName(".", glb::acsfile, this);
  else if ( type() == "path" )
    name = QFileDialog::getExistingDirectory(".", this);

  if ( !name.isEmpty() )
    value(name);
 }
__END_BODY__

{ 
  QMap<int, QString> dict;

  if ( type == "bool" )
  {

    dict.insert(0, "FALSE");
   }
  else if ( type == "side" )
  { 
    dict.insert(0, "LEFT");
    dict.insert(1, "RIGHT");
    dict.insert(2, "CENTER");
   }
  else if ( type == "xside" )

    dict.insert(1, "OFFSIDE");
   }
  else if ( type == "band" )
  { 
    dict.insert(0x0000, "UNLINK");
    dict.insert(0xffff, "BAND 1_1");
    dict.insert(0x5555, "BAND 2_1");
    dict.insert(0xaaaa, "BAND 2_2");

__BEGIN_NAME__
on_typeEdit_activated
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( typeEdit->currentText() == "int")
  { 
    valueEdit->setValidator(new QIntValidator(valueEdit));
    valueEdit->setText(QString::number(valueEdit->text().toInt()));
   }
  else if ( typeEdit->currentText() == "double")
  { 
    valueEdit->setValidator(new QDoubleValidator(valueEdit));
    valueEdit->setText(QString::number(valueEdit->text().toDouble()));
   }
  else if ( typeEdit->currentText() == "string" )
  { 
    QRegExp exp("^[a-zA-Z].*$");
    valueEdit->setValidator(new QRegExpValidator(exp, valueEdit));
   }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setText(0, xml.getAttrib("name").c_str());

  xml.intoElem();
  while ( xml.findElem() )
  { 
    CBaseOptionItem *item = 0;

    if ( xml.getTagName() == "group" )
      item = new COptionGroup(this);
    else
      item = new COptionItem(this);

    item->load(xml);
   }
  xml.outOfElem();
 }

(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  xml.addElem("group");
  xml.addAttrib("name", text(0).toAscii().data());

  xml.intoElem();
  for ( int i = 0; i < childCount(); ++i )
    static_cast<CBaseOptionItem *>(child(i))->save(xml);
  xml.outOfElem();      
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
load
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CMarkup &xml)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QString name = xml.getAttrib("name").c_str();
  setText(0, name);

  xml.intoElem();
  while ( xml.findElem() )
  { 
    CBaseOptionItem *item = 0;

    if ( xml.getTagName() == "group" )
      item = new COptionGroup(this);
    else
      item = new COptionItem(this);

    item->load(xml);
   }
  xml.outOfElem();
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
QTreeWidget
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(parent)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  setObjectName("theOption");
  setWindowIcon(QIcon(": mage ocument_gear_16.png"));

  mMainWindow = mw;





  setColumnCount(4);
  QStringList headers;
  headers << tr("Option") << tr("Type") << tr("Value") << tr("Comment");
  setHeaderLabels(headers);
  header()->resizeSection(0, 150);
  header()->resizeSection(1, 100);
  header()->resizeSection(2, 150);
  header()->setResizeMode(3, QHeaderView::Stretch);

  setSortingEnabled(false);
  setRootIsDecorated(true);
  setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);





  mProperties = new CProperties(this);

  QMap<QString, QVariant> extra;
  extra.clear();
  extra["helptext"] = QString("Enter option document comment");
  mProperties->setProperty("comment", "", extra);





  mAddOptionAct = new QAction(tr("&Add Option"), this);
  mAddOptionAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage lement_add_24.png"));
  mAddOptionAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+A"));
  mAddOptionAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds option"));
  connect(mAddOptionAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddOption()));

  mAddGroupAct = new QAction(tr("Add &Group"), this);
  mAddGroupAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage older_add_24.png"));
  mAddGroupAct->setStatusTip(tr("Adds option group"));
  connect(mAddGroupAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotAddGroup()));

  mEditOptionAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditOptionAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditOptionAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditOptionAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits option"));
  connect(mEditOptionAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditOption()));

  mEditGroupAct = new QAction(tr("&Edit"), this);
  mEditGroupAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage dit_24.png"));
  mEditGroupAct->setShortcut(tr("Ctrl+E"));
  mEditGroupAct->setStatusTip(tr("Edits option group"));
  connect(mEditGroupAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotEditGroup()));

  mDeleteAct = new QAction(tr("&Delete"), this);
  mDeleteAct->setIcon(QIcon(": mage elete2_24.png"));
  mDeleteAct->setShortcut(tr("Del"));
  mDeleteAct->setStatusTip(tr("Deletes the selection"));
  connect(mDeleteAct, SIGNAL(triggered()), this, SLOT(slotDelete()));





  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemDoubleClicked(QTreeWidgetItem *, int)), this, SLOT(slotDoubleClick()));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemExpanded(QTreeWidgetItem *)), this, SLOT(expandItem(QTreeWidgetItem *)));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(itemCollapsed(QTreeWidgetItem *)), this, SLOT(collapseItem(QTreeWidgetItem *)));
  connect(this, SIGNAL(modified()), mMainWindow, SLOT(slotUpdateModIndicator()));





  COptionRoot *item = new COptionRoot(this);
  item->setText(0, "AMI");
  item = new COptionRoot(this);
  item->setText(0, "CNF");
  item = new COptionRoot(this);
  item->setText(0, "OPC");
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:9 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:5 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:10 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/option/option.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:3 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:9 LOCALS:13 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:297 L_END:305 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:editCopy NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:1 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:6 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
editPaste
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 


  CMarkup xml;
  xml.setDoc(QApplication::clipboard()->text().toAscii().data());


  QTreeWidgetItem *parent = selectedItems().value(0);
  if ( parent->type() == OptionItem )
    parent = parent->parent();


  if ( !xml.findElem("options") )
  { 
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "Unable to paste the clipboard information.");
    return;
   }



  QList<CBaseOptionItem *> items;
  try
  { 
    xml.intoElem();
    while ( xml.findElem() )
    { 
      if ( xml.getTagName() == "group" )
        items.append(new COptionGroup(parent));
      else
        items.append(new COptionItem(parent));
      items.last()->load(xml);
     }
    xml.outOfElem();

    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "paste option"));
    for ( QList<CBaseOptionItem *>::iterator it = items.begin(); it != items.end(); ++it )
      mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdAdd("", *it));
    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "paste option"));
   }
  catch ( ... )
  { 
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "Unable to paste the clipboard information.");

    for ( QList<CBaseOptionItem *>::iterator it = items.begin(); it != items.end(); ++it )
      delete *it;
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
editFind
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  CFindDialog dialog;
  dialog.caseCheck->hide();
  dialog.startCheck->hide();

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString text = dialog.findEdit->text();

    Qt::MatchFlags flags = Qt::MatchRecursive;
    if ( dialog.exactCheck->isChecked() )
      flags |= Qt::MatchCaseSensitive;

    QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> found = findItems(text, flags, 0);
    if ( found.count() )
      scrollToItem(found[0]);
   }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__

__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:4 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:8 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:4 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:6 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:1 EXPRORCALL:11 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/option/option.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:3 IN:0 INDR:5 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:18 LOCALS:32 LONG:0 LT:1 L_BEGIN:387 L_END:404 MAXNEST:2 MMINUS:0 NAME:editFind NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:4 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:8 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
readFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 



  CMarkup xml;
  if ( !xml.load(fn) )
  { 
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "ACS Editor", "XML document error.");
    return false;
   }



  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  clear();

  xml.findElem();
  xml.intoElem();

  xml.findElem("group");
  COptionRoot *item = new COptionRoot(this);
  item->load(xml);

  xml.findElem("group");
  item = new COptionRoot(this);
  item->load(xml);

  xml.findElem("group");
  item = new COptionRoot(this);
  item->load(xml);





  xml.findElem("properties");
  while ( xml.findChildElem() )
  { 
    QString name = xml.getChildTagName().c_str();
    QString value = xml.getChildData().c_str();
    mProperties->setProperty(name, value);
   }
  xml.outOfElem();


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
