__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
writeFile
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QString fn)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( fn.isEmpty() )
  { 
    fn = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(".", filter(), 0);

    if ( fn.isEmpty() )
      return false;
    else if ( QFileInfo(fn).extension(false).isEmpty() )
      fn += ".opt";
   }

  QApplication::setOverrideCursor(QCursor(Qt::WaitCursor));





  CMarkup xml;
  xml.setDoc("<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n");
  xml.addElem("ACS");
  xml.addAttrib("type", "option");
  xml.addAttrib("version", glb::version);

  xml.intoElem();

  



  for ( int i = 0; i < topLevelItemCount(); ++i )
    static_cast<CBaseOptionItem *>(topLevelItem(i))->save(xml);





  xml.addElem("properties");
  QStringList list = mProperties->names();
  for ( int i = 0; i < list.count(); ++i )
  { 
    xml.addChildElem(list[i].toAscii().data());
    xml.setChildData(mProperties->value(list[i]).toString().toAscii().data());
   }

  xml.outOfElem();





  if ( !xml.save(fn) )
  { 
    QString message = QString("Unable to write the <B>%1< > file.").arg(fn);
    QMessageBox::warning(0, "FMS Editor", message);

    QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
    return false;
   }


  setWindowTitle(fn);
  mCmdStack.clear();
  emit modified();

  QApplication::restoreOverrideCursor();
  return true;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
slotAddOption
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  COptionEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.setCaption("Add Option");
  dialog.nameEdit->setFocus();

  QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> find = findItems("*", Qt::MatchWildcard | Qt::MatchRecursive, 0);
  for ( QList<QTreeWidgetItem *>::iterator it = find.begin(); it != find.end(); ++it )
    if ( (*it)->type() == OptionItem )
      dialog.optionList << (*it)->text(0);

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
    QString type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
    QString value = dialog.valueEdit->text();
    QString comment = dialog.cmtEdit->text();

    QTreeWidgetItem *parent = selectedItems().value(0);
    if ( parent->type() == OptionItem )
      parent = parent->parent();

    QTreeWidgetItem *item = new COptionItem(parent);
    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "add option"));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdAdd("", item));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 0, name));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 1, type));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 2, value));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 3, comment));
    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "add option"));
    emit modified();
   }
 }
__END_BODY__

{ 
  COptionEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.setCaption("Add Option Group");
  dialog.typeEdit->hide();
  dialog.typeLabel->hide();
  dialog.valueEdit->hide();
  dialog.valueLabel->hide();
  dialog.cmtEdit->hide();
  dialog.cmtLabel->hide();
  dialog.nameEdit->setFocus();

  QTreeWidgetItem *parent = selectedItems().value(0);
  if ( parent->type() == OptionItem )
    parent = parent->parent();

  for ( int i = 0; i < parent->childCount(); ++i )
    if ( parent->child(i)->type() == OptionGroup )
      dialog.optionList << parent->child(i)->text(0);

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();

    QTreeWidgetItem *item = new COptionGroup(parent);
    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "add option group"));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdAdd("", item));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 0, name));
    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "add option group"));
    emit modified();
   }
 }

()

__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

  COptionEditDialog dialog;
  dialog.setCaption("Edit Option");
  dialog.nameEdit->setText(item->text(0));
  dialog.typeEdit->setCurrentText(item->text(1));
  dialog.valueEdit->setText(item->text(2));
  dialog.cmtEdit->setText(item->text(3));
  dialog.refresh();
  dialog.valueEdit->setFocus();

  QList<QTreeWidgetItem *> find = findItems("*", Qt::MatchWildcard | Qt::MatchRecursive, 0);
  for ( QList<QTreeWidgetItem *>::iterator it = find.begin(); it != find.end(); ++it )
    if ( (*it)->type() == OptionItem )
      dialog.optionList << (*it)->text(0);
  dialog.optionList.remove(item->text(0));

  if ( dialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    QString name = dialog.nameEdit->text();
    QString type = dialog.typeEdit->currentText();
    QString value = dialog.valueEdit->text();
    QString comment = dialog.cmtEdit->text();

    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroBegin, "edit option"));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 0, name));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 1, type));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 2, value));
    mCmdStack.push(new COptionCmdEdit("", item, 3, comment));
    mCmdStack.push(new CCommand(CCommand::MacroEnd, "edit option"));
    emit modified();
   }
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
contextMenuEvent
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QContextMenuEvent *event)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QTreeWidgetItem *item = currentItem();

  if ( item == 0 )
    return;

  if ( item->type() == OptionRoot )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddOptionAct);
    menu.addAction(mAddGroupAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == OptionGroup )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddOptionAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditGroupAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
  else if ( item->type() == OptionItem )
  { 
    QMenu menu(this);
    menu.addAction(mAddOptionAct);
    menu.addAction(mEditOptionAct);
    menu.addAction(mDeleteAct);
    menu.exec(event->globalPos());
   }
 }

__BEGIN_NAME__
maybeSave
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( isModified() )
  { 
    QString fn = QFileInfo(filename()).fileName();
    int ret = QMessageBox::warning( 0,
                                    "Editor",
                                    QString("File %1 has been modified.\n"
                                            "Do you want to save your changes?").arg(fn),
                                    QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::Default,
                                    QMessageBox::No,
                                    QMessageBox::Cancel | QMessageBox::Escape );
    if ( ret == QMessageBox::Yes )
      return writeFile(filename());
    else if ( ret == QMessageBox::Cancel )
      return false;
   }
  return true;
 }

names
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  QMap<int, QString> order;
  for ( QMap<QString, Property>::const_iterator i = mProperties.constBegin(); i != mProperties.constEnd(); ++i )
    order[i.data().index] = i.key();

  QStringList list;
  for ( QMap<int, QString>::iterator j = order.begin(); j != order.end(); ++j )
    list << j.data();

  return list;
 }

  if ( mProperties.contains(name) )

    const Property &attr = mProperties[name];

    if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::StringList )
      return attr.value.toStringList()[attr.extra["selected"].toInt()];

#METRICS ARRAYOP:1 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:2 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:2 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:2 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:3 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/properties.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:1 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:6 LOCALS:8 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:192 L_END:197 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:extra NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:2 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:2 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
setProperty
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QString &name, QVariant value, StringVariantMap extra)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( value.type() == QVariant::CString )
    value.asString();


  if ( mProperties.contains(name) )
  { 
    Property &attr = mProperties[name];
    attr.value = value;
    if ( extra.count() )
      for ( StringVariantMap::iterator it = extra.begin(); it != extra.end(); ++it )
        attr.extra[it.key()] = it.data();
   }
  else
  { 
    switch ( value.type() )
    { 
      case QVariant::Bool:
        break;

      case QVariant::Int:
        break;

      case QVariant::UInt:
        if ( !extra.contains("minimum") )
          extra["minimum"] = 0;
        break;

      case QVariant::Double:
        break;

      case QVariant::String:
        break;

      case QVariant::StringList:
        if ( !extra.contains("selected") )
          extra["selected"] = 0;
        break;

      default:
        qDebug("Properies::setProperty() internal error");
        return;
     }
    mProperties[name] = Property(name, mIndex++, value, extra);
   }
 }
__END_BODY__
__BEGIN_IDS__
setProperty::value::type::QVariant::CString::value::asString::mProperties::contains::name::Property::attr::mProperties::name::attr::value::value::extra::count::StringVariantMap::iterator::it::extra::begin::it::extra::end::it::attr::extra::it::key::it::data::value::type::QVariant::Bool::QVariant::Int::QVariant::UInt::extra::contains::minimum::extra::minimum::QVariant::Double::QVariant::QVariant::StringList::extra::contains::selected::extra::selected::qDebug::Properies::setProperty::internal::error::mProperties::name::Property::name::mIndex::value::extra
__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__

(const QString &name, QVariant value)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( value.type() == QVariant::CString )
    value.asString();

  if ( mProperties.contains(name) )
    mProperties[name].value = value;
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:1 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:1 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:1 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/properties.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:7 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:291 L_END:293 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:removeProperty NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:1 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:1 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:1 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:1 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/properties.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:3 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:302 L_END:304 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:clear NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:1 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0 
__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
dialog
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(QWidget *parent, const QString &caption)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  mDlg = new QDialog(parent);
  mDlg->setWindowTitle(caption);


  QVBoxLayout *vbox = new QVBoxLayout(mDlg, 12, 6);
  QHBoxLayout *hbox = 0;





  int width = 0;
  QMap<int, QString> order;
  for ( QMap<QString, Property>::iterator i = mProperties.begin(); i != mProperties.end(); ++i )
  { 
    if ( i.key().length() > width )
      width = i.key().length();
    order[i.data().index] = i.key();
   }





  int row = 0;
  for ( QMap<int, QString>::iterator j = order.begin(); j != order.end(); ++j )
  { 
    Property &attr = mProperties[j.data()];

    if ( attr.extra.contains("hidden") && attr.extra["hidden"].toBool() )
      continue;

    bool readonly = attr.extra.contains("readonly") && attr.extra["readonly"].toBool();

    QString helpText = attr.extra.contains("helptext") ? attr.extra["helptext"].toString() : "";


    QLabel *label = new QLabel(QString().leftJustify(width , 'X'), mDlg);
    label->setMinimumSize(label->sizeHint());
    label->setText(attr.name.replace('_', " ") + ":");
    hbox = new QHBoxLayout(vbox);
    hbox->addWidget(label);



    QVariant value = attr.value;
    if ( value.type() == QVariant::Bool )
    { 
      if ( readonly ) 
      { 
        QLineEdit *lineEdit = new QLineEdit((value.toBool() ? "True" : "False"), mDlg);
        lineEdit->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        lineEdit->setEnabled(false);
        hbox->addWidget(lineEdit);
      }
      else
      { 
        QComboBox *comboBox = new QComboBox(mDlg);
        comboBox->insertItem(tr("False"));
        comboBox->insertItem(tr("True"));
        comboBox->setCurrentItem(value.toBool() ? 1 : 0);
        attr.widget = comboBox;
        label->setBuddy(comboBox);
        if ( !helpText.isEmpty() )
          QToolTip::add(comboBox, helpText);
        hbox->addWidget(comboBox);
       }
      hbox->addStretch(2);
     }

    else if ( value.type() == QVariant::Int )
    { 
      if ( readonly )
      { 
        QLineEdit *lineEdit = new QLineEdit(value.toString(), mDlg);
        lineEdit->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        lineEdit->setEnabled(false);
        hbox->addWidget(lineEdit);
       }
      else
      { 
        QSpinBox *spinBox = new QSpinBox(mDlg);
        spinBox->setValue(value.toInt());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("prefix") )
          spinBox->setPrefix(attr.extra["prefix"].toString());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("suffix") )
          spinBox->setSuffix(attr.extra["suffix"].toString());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("minimum") )
          spinBox->setMinValue(attr.extra["minimum"].toInt());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("maximum") )
          spinBox->setMaxValue(attr.extra["maximum"].toInt());
        attr.widget = spinBox;
        label->setBuddy(spinBox);
        if ( !helpText.isEmpty() )
          QToolTip::add(spinBox, helpText);
        hbox->addWidget(spinBox);
       }
      hbox->addStretch(2);
     }

    else if ( value.type() == QVariant::UInt )
    { 
      if ( readonly )
      { 
        QLineEdit *lineEdit = new QLineEdit(value.toString(), mDlg);
        lineEdit->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        lineEdit->setEnabled(false);
        hbox->addWidget(lineEdit);
       }
      else
      { 
        QSpinBox *spinBox = new QSpinBox(mDlg);
        spinBox->setValue(value.toInt());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("prefix") )
          spinBox->setPrefix(attr.extra["prefix"].toString());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("suffix") )
          spinBox->setSuffix(attr.extra["suffix"].toString());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("minimum") )
          spinBox->setMinValue(attr.extra["minimum"].toUInt());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("maximum") )
          spinBox->setMaxValue(attr.extra["maximum"].toUInt());
        attr.widget = spinBox;
        label->setBuddy(spinBox);
        if ( !helpText.isEmpty() )
          QToolTip::add(spinBox, helpText);
        hbox->addWidget(spinBox);
       }
      hbox->addStretch(2);
     }

    else if ( value.type() == QVariant::Double )
    { 
      if ( readonly )
      { 
        QLineEdit *lineEdit = new QLineEdit(value.toString(), mDlg);
        lineEdit->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        lineEdit->setEnabled(false);
        hbox->addWidget(lineEdit);
       }
      else
      { 
        QLineEdit *lineEdit = new QLineEdit(value.toString(), mDlg);
        lineEdit->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        QDoubleValidator *validator = new QDoubleValidator(mDlg);
        if ( attr.extra.contains("minimum") )
          validator->setBottom(attr.extra["minimum"].toDouble());
        if ( attr.extra.contains("maximum") )
          validator->setTop(attr.extra["maximum"].toDouble());
        lineEdit->setValidator(validator);
        lineEdit->setAlignment(Qt::AlignRight);
        attr.widget = lineEdit;
        label->setBuddy(lineEdit);
        if ( !helpText.isEmpty() )
          QToolTip::add(lineEdit, helpText);
        hbox->addWidget(lineEdit);
       }
      hbox->addStretch(2);
     }

    else if ( value.type() == QVariant::String )
    { 
      if ( readonly )
      { 
        QLineEdit *lineEdit = new QLineEdit(value.toString(), mDlg);
        lineEdit->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        lineEdit->setEnabled(false);
        hbox->addWidget(lineEdit);
       }
      else
      { 
        QLineEdit *lineEdit = new QLineEdit(value.toString(), mDlg);
        lineEdit->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        if ( attr.extra.contains("maximum") )
          lineEdit->setMaxLength(attr.extra["maximum"].toInt());
        attr.widget = lineEdit;
        label->setBuddy(lineEdit);
        if ( !helpText.isEmpty() )
          QToolTip::add(lineEdit, helpText);
        hbox->addWidget(lineEdit);

        if ( attr.extra.contains("filefilter") || attr.extra.contains("folder") )
        { 
          QToolButton *button = new QToolButton(mDlg);
          button->setIconSet(QIcon(":image older_16.png"));
          connect(button, SIGNAL(clicked()), mMapper, SLOT(map()));
          mMapper->setMapping(button, attr.name);
          hbox->addWidget(button);
         }
       }
     }

    else if ( value.type() == QVariant::StringList )
    { 
      if ( readonly )
      { 
        QComboBox *comboBox = new QComboBox(mDlg);
        comboBox->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        comboBox->insertItem(value.toStringList()[attr.extra["selected"].toInt()]);
        comboBox->setEnabled(false);
        hbox->addWidget(comboBox);
       }
      else
      { 
        QComboBox *comboBox = new QComboBox(mDlg);
        comboBox->setMinimumSize(225, 0);
        comboBox->insertStringList(value.toStringList());
        comboBox->setCurrentItem(attr.extra["selected"].toInt());
        comboBox->setEditable(attr.extra["edit"].toBool());
        attr.widget = comboBox;
        label->setBuddy(comboBox);
        if ( !helpText.isEmpty() )
          QToolTip::add(comboBox, helpText);
        hbox->addWidget(comboBox);
       }
      hbox->addStretch(2);
     }

    row++;
   }

  connect(mMapper, SIGNAL(mapped(const QString &)), this, SLOT(mapped(const QString &)));
 
  vbox->addStretch(2);
  hbox = new QHBoxLayout(vbox);
  hbox->addStretch(1);
  QPushButton *button = new QPushButton("OK", mDlg);
  button->setDefault(true);
  hbox->addWidget(button);
  connect(button, SIGNAL(clicked()), mDlg, SLOT(accept()));
  button = new QPushButton("Cancel", mDlg);
  hbox->addWidget(button);
  connect(button, SIGNAL(clicked()), mDlg, SLOT(reject()));

  mDlg->adjustSize();
  mDlg->setFixedHeight(mDlg->height());





  int result = mDlg->exec();
  if ( result == QDialog::Accepted )
  { 
    for ( QMap<QString, Property>::iterator i = mProperties.begin(); i != mProperties.end(); ++i )
    { 
      Property &attr = i.data();

      if ( (attr.extra.contains("hidden") && attr.extra["hidden"].toBool()) ||
           (attr.extra.contains("readonly") && attr.extra["readonly"].toBool()) )
        continue;

      if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::Bool )
        attr.value = QVariant(bool(((QComboBox*)i.data().widget)->currentItem()), 0);
      else if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::Int )
        attr.value = ((QSpinBox*)attr.widget)->value();
      else if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::UInt )
        attr.value = ((QSpinBox*)attr.widget)->value();
      else if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::Double )
        attr.value = ((QLineEdit*)attr.widget)->text().toDouble();
      else if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::String )
        attr.value = ((QLineEdit*)attr.widget)->text();
      else if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::StringList )
        attr.extra["selected"] = ((QComboBox*)attr.widget)->currentItem();

      attr.widget = 0;
     }
   }

  delete mDlg;
  mDlg = 0;
  return result;
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_NAME__
mapped
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(const QString &name)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  Property &attr = mProperties[name];


  if ( attr.value.type() == QVariant::String )
  { 
    if ( attr.extra.contains("filefilter") )
    { 
      QString filename = QFileDialog::getSaveFileName(".", attr.extra["filefilter"].toString(), mDlg, "", tr("Choose a file"));
      if ( !filename.isEmpty() )
        ((QLineEdit*)attr.widget)->setText(filename);
     }

    else if ( attr.extra.contains("folder") )
    { 
      QString filename = QFileDialog::getExistingDirectory(".", mDlg, "", tr("Choose a folder"));
      if ( !filename.isEmpty() )
        ((QLineEdit*)attr.widget)->setText(filename);
     }
   }
 }

#METRICS ARRAYOP:0 ASM:0 ASS:0 AUTO:0 BREAK:0 CALLS:0 CASE:0 CHAR:0 CLASS:0 CONST:0 CONTINUE:0 CYCLO:1 DEFAULT:0 DO:0 DOTS:0 DOUBLE:0 ELSE:0 ENUM:0 EQTEST:0 EXPRORCALL:0 EXTERN:0 FILE:/tmp/poly-class-code/undostack.cpp FLOAT:0 FOR:0 FORTRAN:0 GE:0 GOTO:0 GT:0 IF:0 IN:0 INDR:1 INLINE:0 INT:0 IS_BLK:0 IS_FUN:1 LE:0 LOC:4 LOCALS:6 LONG:0 LT:0 L_BEGIN:43 L_END:45 MAXNEST:1 MMINUS:0 NAME:mRedo NONLCALS:0 OPERATOR:0 OUT:0 PARNUM:1 PPLUS:0 REGISTER:0 RETURN:0 SCOPEOP:0 SHORT:0 SIGNED:0 SIZEOF:0 STATIC:0 STMNT:0 STRUCT:0 SWITCH:0 TERNINSTR:0 TYPEDEF:0 UNION:0 UNSIGNED:0 VOID:0 VOLATILE:0 WHILE:0 __ASM__:0 __INLINE__:0

__BEGIN_NAME__
CUndoStack
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  while ( !mUndo.isEmpty() )
    delete mUndo.takeFirst();

  while ( !mRedo.isEmpty() )
    delete mRedo.takeFirst();
 }

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
push
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
(CCommand *cmd)
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  mUndo.append(cmd);

  while ( !mRedo.isEmpty() )
    delete mRedo.takeFirst();

  cmd->redo();
 }
__END_BODY__

__BEGIN_FUNC__
__BEGIN_NAME__
undo
__END_NAME__
__BEGIN_SIG__
()
__END_SIG__
__BEGIN_BODY__
{ 
  if ( mUndo.last()->isMacroEnd() )
    while ( !mUndo.last()->isMacroBegin() )
    { 
      mUndo.last()->undo();
      mRedo.append(mUndo.takeLast());
     }

  mUndo.last()->undo();
  mRedo.append(mUndo.takeLast());
 }
__END_BODY__

__END_IDS__
__END_FUNC__
